(78, 'Ayako School of Ballet', 'Ayako School of Ballet offers classes for children ages 4 through Professional. Class types include: Classical and\r\nContemporary Ballet, Pointe Classes (Level V and up), Variation Classes (Level IV and up), Modern, Jazz, and Competition\r\nclasses (Level III and up audition in). Our classes are held Monday through Saturday year round, with a two-week August\r\nIntensive Workshop each summer.', 'Ballet', '517 Marine View Ave, Ste E\r\nBelmont, CA, US', 'at@ayakoschoolofballet.com', '+1 650-592-7272', '1', '+1 650-592-7272', 'US', 'https://www.ayakoschool.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/ayakoschool/about/?ref=page_internal', 'institutions/1614682041_ayako.jpg', '2021-03-02 17:47:21', '2021-03-02 17:47:21'),
(79, 'Ballet Academy of Texas', 'The GOAL of the Ballet Academy of Texas is to provide quality, professional dance Ballet Academy of Texas instruction for all ages. The primary focus is on classical ballet technique which provides a strong foundation for all other dance forms. Our goal for the recrecessary to prepare for a career in dance.', 'Ballet', 'Ballet Academy of Texas\r\n145 Fitness Court\r\nCoppell, TX 75019', 'balletoftexas@gmail.com', '972-745-0199', '1', '972-745-0199', 'US', 'www.balletacademyoftexas.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/Ballet-Academy-Of-Texas-149028668459406/', 'institutions/1614682305_bat.jpg', '2021-03-02 17:51:45', '2021-03-02 17:51:45'),
(80, 'Bayview School of Ballet', 'bayview School of Ballet is a world leader in professional ballet instruction, and a cultural institution for expressive art.', 'Ballet', '148 Willowdale, Avenue\r\n\r\nToronto, Ontario\r\n\r\nM2N 4Y4', 'bsbballet@gmail.com', '416 222 5111', '1', '416 222 5111', 'CA', 'https://www.bayviewballet.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/bayviewballet', 'institutions/1614682436_bayview.jpg', '2021-03-02 17:53:56', '2021-03-02 17:53:56'),
(81, 'Bonnie Haney Dance', 'Bonnie Haney School of Dance & Performing Co. has been serving the Fargo/Moorhead area for over 30 years.  We provide classes in nearly all types of dance with a strong emphasis on Ballet and the importance of technique in all styles.  Every year we put on The Nutcracker Ballet & Holiday Show, as well as a Spring Show.  We also offer summer intensive classes, including a guest teacher from Royal Winnipeg Ballet.  We have something to offer for all ages and abilities!', 'Ballet', '3051 25th Street South, Suite S (Family Fare Plaza strip mall)\r\nFargo, ND 58103', 'fargomoorhead@gmail.com', '701-232-9900', '1', '218-236-9900', 'US', 'http://www.bonniehaneydance.com/', '-', 'institutions/1614682835_bonnie.jpg', '2021-03-02 18:00:35', '2021-03-02 18:00:35'),
(82, 'Broadway Dance Academy', 'https://broadwaydanceacademy.net/', 'Ballet', 'Broadway Dance Academy\r\n5604 Merrick Road\r\nMassapequa, NY 11758', 'christine@broadwaydanceacademy.net', '51679572327232', '1', '51679572327232', 'US', 'adwaydanceacademy.net', 'https://www.facebook.com/broadwaydanceacademyandperformingarts/', 'institutions/1614688510_broadway.png', '2021-03-02 19:35:10', '2021-03-02 19:35:10'),
(83, 'California DanceArts', 'At CDA, we offer ballet training programs for young dancers up through professional levels. In addition, we have classes in Contemporary, Modern, Jazz, Pas de Duex (partnering), Aerial Ballet, AcroDance and Adult Classes.', 'Ballet', 'Foothill School Complex\r\n\r\n4490 Cornishon Ave. #6\r\n\r\nLa Canada, CA 91011', 'info@caldancearts.com', '818-790-7924', '1', '818-790-7924', 'CA', 'https://www.caldancearts.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CalBallet', 'institutions/1614688677_cdcb.jpg', '2021-03-02 19:37:57', '2021-03-02 19:37:57'),
(84, 'Colburn School', 'At Colburn, people with a passion for the performing arts get their chance to build a future in music or dance. Guiding them are faculty members that include internationally acclaimed musicians and dancers from the nation’s top ensembles and companies.', 'Ballet', 'Colburn School\r\n200 South Grand Avenue\r\nLos Angeles, CA 90012', 'musicacademy@colburnschool.edu', '213-621-2200', '1', '213-621-2200', 'US', 'https://www.colburnschool.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ColburnSchool/', 'institutions/1614690058_colburn.jpg', '2021-03-02 20:00:58', '2021-03-02 20:00:58'),
(85, 'Coronado Academy of Dance', 'Coronado Academy of Dance has been providing quality dance education to our community since 1998. Our studio represents a positive learning environment where dancers can have fun, be creative, and experience the incredible world of dance. CAD encourages dancers to take the disciplines of dance into their everyday lives, helping to build self-confidence, poise, and self-esteem.', 'Ballet', '952 Orange Ave. (alley entrance)\r\nCoronado, CA 92118', 'dawn@coronadodance.com', '(858) 230-1144', '1', '(858) 230-1144', 'US', 'http://coronadodance.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/coranadoacademyofdance/', 'institutions/1614690352_cad.png', '2021-03-02 20:05:52', '2021-03-02 20:05:52'),
(86, 'Dance Attitudes', 'Dance Attitudes is a great choice for those wishing to explore the art of dance. \r\n At Dance Attitudes, we believe that exposure to the arts opens many doors for the future & is important at any age. Our teaching philosophy is to create a fun, encouraging environment with memories to last a lifetime. Both Katie & Kelly knew from an early age that they wanted to become studio owners. Their dream has come true & today, they hope to inspire others to follow their own dreams.', 'Ballet', '95 Grand Avenue Pawtucket, RI 02861', 'kelly@danceattitudes.org', '401-727-1636', '1', '401-727-1636', 'US', 'http://danceattitudes.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/dance.attitudes.1', 'institutions/1614690821_danceattitudes.jpg', '2021-03-02 20:13:41', '2021-03-02 20:13:41'),
(87, 'Diane Matthews School of Dance Arts', 'West Chester Dance Works provides intensive training for dancers, facilitate community-based and dance festival performing opportunities, and engage community members with interactive presentations. Visit www.wcdw.org for more information and check back soon for our most recent opportunities.', 'Ballet', '315-9 Westtown Road, West Chester, PA 19382', 'director@wcdw.org', '(610) 692-3398', '1', '(610) 692-3398', 'US', 'http://www.dianematthewsdance.com/', 'www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1614691143_diana.jpg', '2021-03-02 20:19:03', '2021-03-02 20:19:03'),
(88, 'Edra Toth\'s Academy of Dance & Music', 'Edra Toth\'s Academy of Dance & Music and Northeastern Ballet Theatre reflects the artistic vision of its founder Edra Toth. And, her passion. Miss Edra (as she is affectionately known) has built a life teaching children and adults the joy of dance. She believes that anyone can dance...and should! She never turns a child away that cannot pay. She remembers those who helped her find her life through dance and vows to give that experience to as many children as possible.', 'Ballet', '26 Glendon Street\r\nWolfeboro, New Hampshire 03894', 'admin@ballethub.com', '-', '0', '-', 'US', 'https://ballethub.com/danceschool/edra-toths-academy-of-dance-music-wolfeboro-new-hampshire/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ballethub', 'institutions/1614691681_ballethub.png', '2021-03-02 20:28:01', '2021-03-02 20:28:01'),
(89, 'Hermitage Dance Academy', 'Find Yourself at HDA!\r\nDance can help you find many things, what will you find at HDA?', 'Ballet', '3441 Lebanon Pike, Suite 130\r\nHermitage, TN, US', 'hdaoffice@hdadance.com', '615-231-7100', '1', '615-231-7100', 'US', 'https://hermitagedance.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hdadance/', 'institutions/1614694070_hermitage.png', '2021-03-02 21:01:11', '2021-03-02 21:07:50'),
(90, 'McCaleb Dance', 'Nancy McCaleb’s dances have been performed in over 70 theaters on the West Coast, in New York City, Mexico, and Europe.  In venues ranging from an opera house in Poland to a bread factory in Germany, her provocative, powerfully athletic, and deeply moving dances bring audiences to their feet.', 'Ballet', '8070 La Jolla Shores Drive #404, La Jolla, CA  92037', 'mccalebdance@yahoo.com', '-', '0', '-', 'code', 'http://www.mccalebdance.org/', '-', 'institutions/1614694303_melani.jpg', '2021-03-02 21:11:43', '2021-03-02 21:11:43'),
(91, 'Butler University', 'Butler University is a nationally recognized university with six academic colleges: Arts, Business, Communication, Education, Liberal Arts and Sciences, and Pharmacy and Health Sciences. We’re known for providing small classes, opportunities to engage directly with faculty, and real-world experience through internships, co-ops, research with faculty mentors, performances, and community engagement offerings.', 'Ballet', '4600 Sunset Avenue, Indianapolis, Indiana', 'social@butler.edu', '46208 • 800-368-6852', '1', '46208 • 800-368-6852', 'US', 'https://www.butler.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/butleruniversity', 'institutions/1614694868_butler.jpg', '2021-03-02 21:21:08', '2021-03-02 21:21:08'),
(92, 'Juilliard School', 'Located at Lincoln Center in NYC, Juilliard is a top performing arts conservatory with programs in dance, drama, classical music, and jazz.', 'Ballet', 'The Juilliard School\r\n60 Lincoln Center Plaza\r\nNew York, NY 10023', 'socialmedia@juilliard.edu', '212-799-5000', '1', '212-799-5000', 'US', 'www.juilliard.edu', 'https://www.facebook.com/TheJuilliardSchool', 'institutions/1614695325_julia.png', '2021-03-02 21:28:45', '2021-03-02 21:28:45'),
(93, 'Kathleen Academy of Dance', 'ur goal in teaching dance is to expose our students to various styles in such a manner that they develop a passion for the arts, either as a dancer, or a patron of the arts. Dance is an art form, and not a competitive sport, and can be enjoyed on so many different levels.', 'Ballet', '411 US Highway 206\r\nHillsborough, NJ, US', 'kadstudio@gmail.com', '+1 908-359-8888', '1', '+1 908-359-8888', 'US', 'https://www.kathleenacademy.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/KathleenAcademy/', 'institutions/1614695559_kathleen.jpg', '2021-03-02 21:32:39', '2021-03-02 21:32:39'),
(94, 'Logrea Dance Academy', 'We are training students to become independent, respectful, self confident, young adults with a passion for the arts.', 'Ballet', '2 Dale Avenue Ossining, NY 10562', 'logreadance@gmail.com', '9149412939', '1', '9149412939', 'US', 'https://www.logreadance.com/contact.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/LogreaDanceAcademy', 'institutions/1614696070_longrea.jpg', '2021-03-02 21:41:10', '2021-03-02 21:41:10'),
(95, 'The Loudoun School of Ballet', 'The Loudoun School of Ballet in Leesburg, Virginia, has trained more than 16,000 dance students, fostering a tradition of excellence in dance instruction since 1977 – more than 40 years!', 'Ballet', '305-H E Market St, Leesburg, VA 20176', 'info@lsofballet.com', '703-771-3200', '1', '703-771-3200', 'US', 'https://www.lsofballet.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/loudounballetschool/', 'institutions/1615624612_Loundon.jpg', '2021-03-13 15:36:52', '2021-03-13 15:36:52'),
(96, 'M & M Dance Academy of Monroeville', 'Our mission is to teach dance in a nurturing, stress-free, compassionate, and positive atmosphere while giving each dancer a strong dance technique, poise, and sense of self-esteem. The confidence gained through classes and performances benefits students in all aspects of life. We promote teamwork and friendship as essential tools to build happy dancers and good people.', 'Ballet', '4314 Old William Penn Hwy, Monroeville, PA 15146', 'lori.mmdance@hotmail.com', '412-373-5020', '1', '412-373-5020', 'US', 'https://www.mmdanceacademy.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/MMDanceAcademy/', 'institutions/1615625061_m&m.jpg', '2021-03-13 15:44:21', '2021-03-13 15:44:21'),
(97, 'Mill Ballet School', 'The Mill Ballet School is dedicated to only the highest standards of classical and contemporary dance. It is open to career-orientated students, as well as those who wish to study classical and contemporary dance for pure enjoyment, for the inherent health benefits, or to develop a life long appreciation of the art.', 'Ballet', '243 N Union St #120, Lambertville, NJ', 'info@millballetschool.com', 'info@millballetschool.com', '1', 'info@millballetschool.com', 'US', 'https://www.millballetschool.com/home', 'https://www.facebook.com/themillballetschool/', 'institutions/1615627786_mbs.jpg', '2021-03-13 16:29:46', '2021-03-13 16:29:46'),
(98, 'New Albany School of Ballet and dance arts', 'The New Albany Ballet is a youth oriented organization that provides dancers with\r\nunique opportunities to study and dance with professional dancers from all over the U.S. and beyond. In fact, the company has sponsored six different guest artists since its inception in 2011.This gives us an avenue to build up a dance force that can support and sponsor professional companies and dancers to come to New Albany and augment our program.', 'Ballet', '216 South Denton Road New Albany MS 38652 (Close to the Movie Reel and the Mane Touch).', 'justine.stewart@newalbanyballetstudio.com', '662-266-0500', '1', '662-266-0500', 'US', 'http://www.newalbanyballetstudio.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/groups/126505936177/', 'institutions/1615628572_albany.jpg', '2021-03-13 16:42:52', '2021-03-13 16:42:52'),
(99, 'Nicole Cote School of Dance', 'Nicole Cote School of Dance began the Leadership Program in 2018. Dancers over the age of 13 are chosen through an application process into the Leadership Program with either a Gold, Silver, or Bronze title. This Leadership program enables the dancers to assist faculty members with weekly dance classes in return for tuition reimbursement. This program motivates, contributes, and creates dancers to help enrich the lives of other dancers through talent and skill.', 'Ballet', '5180 Minton Road\r\nPalm Bay, FL 32907', 'nicolecote@nicolecoteschoolofdance.com', '(321) 725-6710', '1', '(321) 725-6710', 'US', 'https://www.nicolecoteschoolofdance.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Nicole-Cote-School-of-Dance-150304775011079/', 'institutions/1615629170_nicole_cote.png', '2021-03-13 16:52:50', '2021-03-13 16:52:50'),
(100, 'North Central Ballet', 'Founded in 1993 by Leslie M. Jordan III, the ballet studio and North Central Ballet Company enrich the environment of our community through education, performance and dance related activities.', 'Ballet', '12077 KATY RD, SUITE 713 • KELLER, TEXAS 76248', 'lesjordan@northcentralballet.com', '817-428-8232', '1', '817-428-8232', 'US', 'https://www.northcentralballet.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/NorthCentralBallet/', 'institutions/1615629355_ncb.jpg', '2021-03-13 16:55:55', '2021-03-13 16:55:55'),
(101, 'Opus Performing Arts', 'Opus Performing Art boasts some of the best teachers in the Bellingham area, including Artistic Director Brooke Evans, Amy Guerra, and BRD co-founder Diane Williams. This video is an introduction to the faculty as they explain the core values and principles they apply to their teaching philosophy.', 'Ballet', '114 W Holly St\r\nBellingham, WA', 'opusperformingarts@gmail.com', '360-734-5300', '1', '360-734-5300', 'US', 'https://www.opusbellingham.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/opusperformingarts/', 'institutions/1615629596_opus.png', '2021-03-13 16:59:56', '2021-03-13 16:59:56'),
(102, 'Pacific Ballet Academy', 'Pacific Ballet Academy offers a full range of graded classes, from pre-ballet to pre-professional training. We provide a unique opportunity for students of all ages and abilities to study the traditions and discipline of Russian Ballet. Whether a student\'s goal is a career in dance or purely recreational exercise, our dedicated faculty offers personal attention and professional training to match each student\'s interests.', 'Ballet', '295 Polaris Avenue   •   Mountain View, CA', 'director@pacificballet.org', '(650) 969-4614', '1', '(650) 969-4614', 'US', 'http://www.pacificballet.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pacificballetacademy/', 'institutions/1615733124_pacificballet.jpg', '2021-03-14 20:45:24', '2021-03-14 20:45:24'),
(103, 'PZ Dance Academy', 'The PZDA opened its doors in September of 1976. We have met with continued success in training and nurturing our dancers. We have built our reputation on our ability to provide a quality dance education in a positive and encouraging environment, where lifelong friendships, bonds, and memories are made.', 'Ballet', '173 Grove St (6,543.61 mi)\r\nWorcester, MA, MA 01605', 'pzda.dancer@gmail.com', '508-757-9654', '1', '508-757-9654', 'US', 'http://www.pzdance.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pzdance/', 'institutions/1615733427_pz.png', '2021-03-14 20:50:27', '2021-03-14 20:50:27'),
(104, 'THE ROCK SCHOOL FOR DANCE EDUCATION', 'The Rock School for Dance Education is proud to be one of the nation’s top pre- professional training programs. The School has been producing classically trained and versatile dancers for over 50 years. Dancers from around the world are attracted to The School’s exceptional faculty, individual attention, nurturing environment, and the success of its alumni. In addition, The Rock School offers a unique in-house academic program and supervised residence.', 'Ballet', '1101 South Broad Street\r\nPhiladelphia, PA, 19147\r\nUnited States', 'info@therockschool.org', '(215) 551-7010', '1', '(215) 551-7010', 'US', 'therockschool.org', 'https://twitter.com/intent/follow?original_referer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.therockschool.org%2F&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&screen_name=therockschool&tw_p=followbutton', 'institutions/1615733566_RockWebLogo.png', '2021-03-14 20:52:46', '2021-03-14 20:52:46'),
(105, 'San Pedro Ballet School', 'At San Pedro Ballet School, we believe that we are not only training students in the art of dance, but we are training them in the lessons of life. We teach them how to be graceful and how to take care of their bodies. We teach them about responsibility, how to work well with others, and how to be a good team member.', 'Ballet', '1231 S. Pacific Avenue\r\nSan Pedro, CA 90731', 'info@sanpedroballetschool.com', '310.732.1861', '1', '310.732.1861', 'US', 'http://www.sanpedroballetschool.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/squarespace', 'institutions/1615738191_san.png', '2021-03-14 22:09:51', '2021-03-14 22:09:51'),
(106, 'Vladimir Issaev\'s School of Classical Ballet', 'Under the artistic direction of Ballet Master VLADIMIR ISSAEV, we offer classes in ballet, pointe, character, hip hop and contemporary with a focus in Vaganova style classical ballet. The school stresses to offer quality training from a highly qualified staff of professionals.', 'Ballet', '15939 Biscayne Boulevard\r\nNorth Miami Beach, FL 33160', 'school@classicalballetschool.com', '305 948 4777', '1', '305 948 4777', 'US', 'https://www.classicalballetschool.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/IdanceatVISCB/', 'institutions/1616417492_vladmir.PNG', '2021-03-22 18:51:32', '2021-03-22 18:51:32'),
(107, 'NJ Ballet\'s', 'New Jersey School of Ballet has provided top quality instruction for over 50 years. Classes are held in three locations; Livingston, Somerville and the Morristown area', 'Ballet', '7-9 VREELAND ROAD, FLORHAM PARK, NJ 07932', 'info@njballet.org', '(973) 597-9600', '1', '(973) 597-9600', 'US', 'http://www.njschoolofballet.com/index.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/NJSBallet/about/?ref=page_internal', 'institutions/1616417792_njsb.jpg', '2021-03-22 18:56:32', '2021-03-22 18:56:32'),
(108, 'Academy of Dance', 'The Academy of Dance is truly unique among the ballet schools in the Spokane area. Our program is geared toward the development of the whole child.', 'Ballet', 'The Academy of Dance\r\n14214 E Sprague Ave, Spokane Valley, 99216', 'spokaneacademyofdance@gmail.com', '509-922-3023', '1', '509-922-3023', 'US', 'https://www.spokaneacademyofdance.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/SpokaneAOD', 'institutions/1616483199_aod.jpg', '2021-03-23 13:06:39', '2021-03-23 13:06:39'),
(109, 'Stapleton School of the Performing Arts', 'Founded in Marin County California in 1988 by Virginia Stapleton, the school is distinguished by its commitment to inclusiveness and respect while providing top quality performing arts training.', 'Ballet', 'PO Box 331\r\nSan Anselmo, CA 94979', 'info@stapletonschool.org', '(415)454-5759', '1', '(415)454-5759', 'US', 'https://www.stapletonschool.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/stapletonschoolofpa/', 'institutions/1616483397_stapleton-logo.jpg', '2021-03-23 13:09:57', '2021-03-23 13:09:57'),
(110, 'Steffi Nossen School of Dance', 'Founded as a modern dance school in 1937 by dance legend Steffi Nossen, the Steffi Nossen School of Dance (SNSD) offers the highest quality, developmentally appropriate dance instruction and performance opportunities for all ages and abilities. From pre-schoolers through pre-professionals, students have the opportunity to learn a range of dance forms including modern, ballet, jazz, tap, hip hop, yoga and composition, workshops and short courses in world dance forms.', 'Ballet', '216 N Central Ave\r\nWhite Plains, NY 10606', 'info@steffinossen.org', '(914) 328-1900', '1', '(914) 328-1900', 'US', 'https://www.steffinossen.org/', 'https://www.instagram.com/steffinossendance/', 'institutions/1616484051_streffi.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:20:51', '2021-03-23 13:20:51'),
(111, 'Westlake School for the Performing Arts', 'WSPA was founded in the summer of 1991 by Malu Rivera-Peoples and Karen Dycaico. In a successful collaboration with the City of Daly City Parks and Recreation Department, a state-of-the art dance studio in the Larcombe Clubhouse was built to begin a summer dance program of 35 students and three instructors. Its first performance was at the Pacelli Gymnasium celebrating the new renovated park.', 'Ballet', '200 Northgate Ave #4, Daly City CA 94015', 'wspa1@sbcglobal.net', '(650) 757 - 1244', '1', '(650) 757 - 1244', 'US', 'https://www.wspadance.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/wspadalycity/photos/?ref=page_internal', 'institutions/1616484377_westlake.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:26:17', '2021-03-23 13:26:17'),
(112, 'Royal Ballet, London, ENGLAND', 'Our mission is to nurture, train and educate exceptional young dancers for The Royal Ballet, Birmingham Royal Ballet and other leading UK and international companies, and to inspire the future of classical ballet training.', 'Ballet', '46 Floral Street, Covent Garden, London, WC2E 9DA, UK', 'enquiries@royalballetschool.org.uk', '+44 (0)20 7836 8899', '1', '+44 (0)20 7836 8899', 'GB', 'https://royalballetschool.org.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/royal.ballet.school/', 'institutions/1616484664_rbs.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:31:04', '2021-03-23 13:31:04'),
(113, 'Vaganova Ballet Academy, Saint Petersburg, RUSSIA', 'Founded in 1738 by decree of Empress Anna I, of Russia, the Imperial Ballet School became Russia’s first educational establishment to provide professional ballet training. Now known as the Vaganova Ballet Academy, the school has just marked its 275th Anniversary. Over the years, the Academy has graduated a galaxy of legendary dancers and choreographers.', 'Ballet', 'Rossi Street, 2\r\nMuseum', 'academy@vaganovaacademy.com', '-', '0', '-', 'RU', 'http://vaganovaacademy.com/', '-', 'institutions/1616484950_vaganova.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:35:50', '2021-03-23 13:35:50'),
(114, 'Escuela Nacional de ballet de Cuba, Havana, CUBA', 'Established in 1959 by Betty Oliphant and Celia Franca, Canada’s National Ballet School (NBS) is one of the world’s foremost training institutions for aspiring young dancers and teachers. NBS is sharing dance through the Olympic-calibre training and holistic preparation of young dancers for careers on the world stage, and by successfully training teachers, ballet masters and artistic directors who hold posts in schools and companies across Canada and around globe.', 'Ballet', 'Canada\'s National Ballet School\r\n400 Jarvis St\r\nToronto ON  M4Y 2G6\r\nCanada', 'info@nbs-enb.ca', '416-964-3780', '1', '416-964-3780', 'CA', 'https://www.nbs-enb.ca/ai13/Schools/Cuban-National-Ballet-School.aspx', 'https://www.facebook.com/NBSENB', 'institutions/1616485532_cnbss.png', '2021-03-23 13:45:32', '2021-03-23 13:45:32'),
(115, 'John Cranko School, Stuttgart, GERMANY', 'The John Cranko Schule consists of the Ballet School of the State Theatre Stuttgart and the State Ballet Academy – a Vocational School. The school is financed by the State of Baden-Württemberg and the City of Stuttgart. The school year is the same as that of state schools. An admission is possible at any stage of the training. Condition for admission is a passed entrance examination.', 'Ballet', 'John Cranko Schule\r\nWerastraße 27\r\n70182 Stuttgart\r\nGermany', 'info@john-cranko-schule.de', '+49. (0)711. 28539 0', '1', '+49. (0)711. 28539 0', 'DE', 'http://www.john-cranko-schule.de/', '-', 'institutions/1616485763_johncranco.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:49:23', '2021-03-23 13:49:23'),
(116, 'Bolshoi Ballet Academy, Moscow, RUSSIA', 'The acclaimed Bolshoi Ballet Academy (BBA) has produced some of the most accomplished stars of the current generation, including Natalia Osipova, Alexei Ratmansky, Polina Semionova, Vladimir Malakhov, Maria Kochetkova, and many others.  \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nWith its nearly 250-year history, the Academy’s curriculum and pedagogy are recognized for their focus on strength, musicality, clarity of technique, and personal expression.', 'Ballet', 'Facebook Social Icon\r\nInstagram\r\nYouTube\r\nADDRESS\r\n​\r\nRussian American Foundation, Inc.\r\n\r\n1560 Broadway #500, New York, NY 10036', 'jdirenfeld@russianamericanfoundation.org', '212-687-6118', '1', '212-687-6118', 'RU', 'https://www.bolshoiballetacademy.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/BolshoiBalletAcademySI/', 'institutions/1616485898_bba.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:51:38', '2021-03-23 13:51:38'),
(117, 'Houston Ballet Academy, Houston, Texas', 'The Professional Program is designed for students who meet the artistic expectations set forth by the Artistic Director, Stanton Welch AM and for those students interested in a professional career in ballet. This does not exclude students who wish to enter college, however students must be prepared to focus on training as a priority along with meeting the artistic requirements set forth by the Artistic Director.', 'Ballet', 'Wortham Theater Center, located at 501 Texas Ave. at Smith Street in downtown Houston (zip 77002)', 'info@houstonballet.org', '713 523 6300', '1', '713 523 6300', 'US', 'https://www.houstonballet.org/about/academy1/professional-program/', 'https://www.facebook.com/houstonballet', 'institutions/1616486081_hba.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:54:41', '2021-03-23 13:54:41'),
(118, 'School of American Ballet, NYC, New York', 'We train talented dancers from diverse backgrounds for professional careers in ballet while enriching the life of every student.', 'Ballet', 'School of American Ballet\r\n70 Lincoln Center Plaza', 'info@sab.org', '212-769-6600', '1', '212-769-6600', 'US', 'https://sab.org/', '-', 'institutions/1616486210_sab.JPG', '2021-03-23 13:56:50', '2021-03-23 13:56:50'),
(119, 'Scuola di Ballo del Teatro alla Scala, Milan', 'The roots of the La Scala Academy date back to 1813, when La Scala opened the Ballet School, now recognized as one of the most prestigious institutions for international ballet training; in the 1950s, with the creation of the \"Cadetti della Scala\" school, Arturo Toscanini wanted to give historical continuity to the Italian lyric tradition, always with a view to promoting the growth of young talents, a true La Scala vocation.', 'Ballet', 'Via S. Marta, 18 - 20123 Milano', 'relazioni.esterne@accademialascala.it', '+39028545111', '1', '+39028545111', 'IT', 'https://www.accademialascala.it/en/home-en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/accademiascala/', 'institutions/1616486888_academiatetro.jpg', '2021-03-23 14:08:08', '2021-03-23 14:08:08'),
(120, 'Australian Ballet School', 'For almost 60 years, The Australian Ballet has been inspiring, delighting and challenging audiences through the power of its performances. A commitment to artistic vibrancy, a spirited style and a willingness to take risks have defined the company from its earliest days, both onstage and off.', 'Ballet', '2 Kavanagh St Level 6\r\nSouthbank, VIC, Australia', 'tickets@australianballet.com.au', '+611300369741', '1', '+611300369741', 'AU', 'https://australianballet.com.au/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/theaustralianballet', 'institutions/1616487183_theaustralianballet.JPG', '2021-03-23 14:13:03', '2021-03-23 14:13:03'),
(121, 'Royal Danish School', 'The next three academic years the Royal Danish Academy - Architecture, Design, Conservation will focus massively on the UN Global Goals - in our research, in our educations and in our graduation projects. Here you can explore a selection of projects, articles and photos connected to this effort.', 'Ballet', 'Philip de Langes Allé 10\r\nCopenhagen, Denmark', 'info@kglakademi.dk', '+4541701500', '1', '+4541701500', 'DK', 'https://royaldanishacademy.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/kglakademi', 'institutions/1616487672_rds.jpg', '2021-03-23 14:21:12', '2021-03-23 14:21:12'),
(122, 'Central Pennsylvania Youth Ballet', 'Central Pennsylvania Youth Ballet, founded in 1955 by Marcia Dale Weary, is known throughout the world for providing the finest in classical ballet training. CPYB’s exceptional faculty, individual attention, and nurturing environment train not just the dancer, but the whole person.', 'Ballet', '5 North Orange Street, Suite 3, Carlisle, PA 17013-2727', 'info@cpyb.org', '+1 717-601-2840', '1', '+1 717-601-2840', 'US', 'https://cpyb.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/centralpennsylvaniayouthballet', 'institutions/1616487921_cpyb.jpg', '2021-03-23 14:25:21', '2021-03-23 14:25:21'),
(123, 'Ballet Academy East, USA', 'Ballet Academy East offers comprehensive dance training for beginners through professionals. Led by world-class faculty in an environment that encourages professional and personal success, BAE is your home for quality dance education.', 'Ballet', '1651 3rd Ave suite 307\r\nNew York, NY', 'info@baenyc.com', '+1 212-410-9140', '1', '+1 212-410-9140', 'US', 'http://balletacademyeast.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/', 'institutions/1616488147_bae.jpg', '2021-03-23 14:29:07', '2021-03-23 14:29:07'),
(124, 'Sunhwa Arts Academy, South Korea', 'Sunhwa Arts School was launched in 1974 and has been supported by the Sunhwa Educational Foundation since 1977, when this foundation was created by Reverend Moon. It is considered to be among the most prominent visual arts, music and dance middle schools and high schools in South Korea.', 'Ballet', 'Gwangjin-gu, Seoul: 02-2204-1300', 'info@sunhwa.com', '02-2204-1300', '1', '02-2204-1300', 'KR', 'http://www.sunhwa.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sunhwa-Arts-School/282795668493606', 'institutions/1616489418_sunhwa.png', '2021-03-23 14:50:18', '2021-03-23 14:50:18'),
(125, 'Real Conservatorio Profesional de Danza Mariemma, Spain', 'Conservatorio de Danza que pertenece a la Comunidad de Madrid. Imparte Danza Clásica, Danza Española y Danza Contemporánea', 'Ballet', 'C/ Padre Amigó, 5\r\nMadrid, Spain', 'info@rcpdmariemma.com', '+34 914 68 06 51', '1', '+34 914 68 06 51', 'ES', 'Real Conservatorio Profesional de Danza Mariemma, Spain', 'https://www.facebook.com/RCPD-Mariemma-381500435751/', 'institutions/1616489874_rcpd.png', '2021-03-23 14:57:54', '2021-03-23 14:57:54'),
(126, 'Vienna State Opera Ballet School, Vienna', 'he virtuoso Vienna State Ballet dances at the Vienna State Opera and the Volksoper. The highlights of the 2020/21 season include works by George Balanchine, Jerome Robbins, Hans van Manen, and Martin Schläpfer.', 'Ballet', 'Tegetthoffstraße 7, 1010 Vienna, Austria', 'info@wien.info', '+43 1 21114', '1', '+43 1 21114', 'AT', 'https://www.wien.info/en/music-stage-shows/dance/vienna-state-ballet', 'https://www.facebook.com/ViennaTouristBoard', 'institutions/1616490087_vienna.png', '2021-03-23 15:01:27', '2021-03-23 15:01:27'),
(127, 'Paris Opera Ballet School, France', 'Since its creation under the reign of Louis XIV, the Ballet School of the Opéra national de Paris has built a worldwide reputation thanks to outstanding personalities and excellence in teaching.', 'Ballet', 'Place de la Bastille\r\nParis, France', 'resa.internet@operadeparis.fr', '+33 892 89 90 90', '1', '+33 892 89 90 90', 'FR', 'https://www.operadeparis.fr/en/artists/ballet-school', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/operadeparis/about/?ref=page_internal', 'institutions/1616493079_opera.jpg', '2021-03-23 15:51:19', '2021-03-23 15:51:19'),
(128, 'San Francisco Ballet School, USA', 'The dream of becoming a professional ballet dancer may begin with Nutcracker; however, the real work starts here.\r\n\r\nFrom intensive youth ballet training programs to classes for adults, and dance education partnerships with SFUSD schools and community organizations, SF Ballet seeks to share the joy of dance with the broadest audience possible. Our education programs and the SF Ballet School strive to provide equitable access to high quality dance education for students of all ages and abilities.', 'Ballet', '455 Franklin St\r\nSan Francisco, CA', 'tickets@sfballet.org', '415-861-5600', '1', '415-861-5600', 'US', 'https://www.sfballet.org/school-education/', 'https://www.facebook.com/sfballet', 'institutions/1616498344_SFB_Horizontal_Logo.png', '2021-03-23 17:19:04', '2021-03-23 17:19:04'),
(129, 'Master Ballet Academy, Arizona', 'Welcome to Master Ballet Academy® – Arizona’s premier Ballet Dance School.\r\n\r\nRanked #4 ballet school in the world!\r\n\r\nOur Artistic Director Slawomir Woźniak is well known throughout the professional ballet community all over the world.', 'Ballet', '15795 N 76th Street\r\nScottsdale, AZ 85260', 'masterballetnews@gmail.com', '6029968000', '1', '6029968000', 'US', 'http://www.masterballetacademy.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/masterballetacademy', 'institutions/1616498659_master ballet academy.jpg', '2021-03-23 17:24:19', '2021-03-23 17:24:19'),
(130, 'Abby Lee Dance Company', 'The Abby Lee Dance Company was once a not-for-profit organization, formed 35 years ago to afford promising and dedicated young dancers the opportunity to study with the dance community’s most distinguished dance educators and to compete against other talented young people across the country! The Abby Lee Dance Company was the resident competition team of The Maryen Lorrain Dance Studio in Pittsburgh, PA for 30 successful years.', 'Ballet', '7123 Saltsburg Road\r\nPittsburgh, PA 15235', 'mediamgmt@abbyleedancecompany.com', '4127956234', '1', '4127956234', 'US', 'https://abbyleedancecompany.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/OfficialAbbyLeeMiller', 'institutions/1616506018_aldc.JPG', '2021-03-23 19:26:58', '2021-03-23 19:26:58'),
(131, 'The English National Ballet', 'We’re a bold, ambitious, and creative touring ballet company, that reaches for innovative ways of honouring, and adding to ballet.', 'Ballet', 'English National Ballet\r\n41 Hopewell Square,\r\nLondon, E14 0SY', 'hello@ballet.org.uk', '+442075811245', '1', '+442075811245', 'GB', 'https://www.ballet.org.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/EnglishNationalBallet', 'institutions/1616506351_enb.jpg', '2021-03-23 19:32:31', '2021-03-23 19:32:31'),
(132, 'Royal Winnipeg Ballet Schoo', 'For almost 80 years, the Royal Winnipeg Ballet School has been inspiring young artists and supporting them in the pursuit of their goals. Under the direction of School Director Stéphane Léonard, the RWB School is well-known across Canada and around the world for providing excellence in dance education.', 'Ballet', '380 Graham Avenue\r\nR3C 4K2', 'customerservice@rwb.org', '2049560183', '1', '2049560183', 'CA', 'http://rwb.org/school', 'https://www.facebook.com/RWBallet', 'institutions/1616508185_rwb.jpg', '2021-03-23 20:03:05', '2021-03-23 20:03:05'),
(133, 'Kirov Academy of Ballet', '\"As one of the world’s elite ballet academies, Kirov Academy’s performances warrant attention. The school has produced ballet competition winners and placed its graduates in major companies worldwide.\"', 'Ballet', '4301 Harewood Rd NE\r\nWashington D.C., DC', 'info@kabdc.org', '+1 202-832-1087', '1', '+1 202-832-1087', 'US', 'http://kirovacademydc.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/kirovacademy/', 'institutions/1616510383_kirow.JPG', '2021-03-23 20:39:43', '2021-03-23 20:39:43'),
(134, 'Elmhurst', 'Located in a beautiful suburb minutes from Chicago, Elmhurst University combines the close-knit learning environment of a small school with the endless opportunities of a world-class city.', 'Ballet', '190 Prospect Avenue\r\nElmhurst, Illinois 60126', 'admit@elmhurst.edu', '(630) 617-3400', '1', '(630) 617-3400', 'US', 'https://www.elmhurst.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/elmhurstuniversity', 'institutions/1616510624_elmhurst.jpg', '2021-03-23 20:43:44', '2021-03-23 20:43:44'),
(135, 'Brent Street Schools', 'Brent Street is a place where incredible things happen for passionate and hard-working performers.  For over 35 years Brent Street has been a leader in performance arts, training countless working professionals across all genres of the industry.', 'Ballet', 'Box 261\r\nThe Entertainment Quarter\r\n122 Lang Road, Moore Park\r\nNSW 2021', 'info@brentstreet.com.au', '02 8323 6666', '1', '02 8323 6666', 'AU', 'https://brentstreet.com.au/', 'https://www.facebook.com/brentstreetstudios', 'institutions/1616511182_brent.JPG', '2021-03-23 20:53:02', '2021-03-23 20:53:02'),
(136, 'The School of Richmond Ballet', 's the official school of Richmond Ballet, The State Ballet of Virginia, we offer superior training for young people who aspire to have a professional ballet career as well as those students who wish simply to enrich their lives through dance. Together, with our world-class faculty, we work to ensure that every student has a valuable and positive experience with dance, from the tiniest dancer to the elite artists that graduate from our advanced programs.', 'Ballet', '407 East Canal Street\r\nRichmond, VA 23219', 'bbonda@richmondballet.com', '8043440906', '1', '8043440906', 'US', 'https://www.richmondballet.com/school/', 'https://www.facebook.com/RichmondBallet/', 'institutions/1616511751_richmond.png', '2021-03-23 21:02:31', '2021-03-23 21:02:31'),
(137, 'Rambert School of Ballet and Contemporary Dance', 'Currently celebrating its centenary year, Rambert School has flexed and moved with the times. Today the finely-tuned curriculum, inspirational teaching and the creative talent and individuality of students make us a world leading centre for dance training. The School prides itself on nurturing each individual throughout their training to ensure the School’s young adults prosper into healthy, balanced and ultimately successful professionals.', 'Ballet', 'Clifton Lodge, St. Margarets Drive Twickenham TW1 1QN', 'info@rambertschool.org.uk', '+44 (0) 208 892 9960', '1', '+44 (0) 208 892 9960', 'GB', 'https://www.rambertschool.org.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/rambertschool/', 'institutions/1616512229_rambert.png', '2021-03-23 21:10:29', '2021-03-23 21:10:29'),
(138, 'Salzburg International Ballet Academy', 'SIBA is The ONLY ballet workshop in which you experience what it means to be a professional dancer, Due to the structure of the curriculum and the special training of our international teachers.', 'Ballet', 'The school Address: Herz Jesu Gymnasium, Schoenleitenstr. 1,\r\n\r\n5020 Salzburg-Liefering, Austria', 'nili.glazer@gmail.com', '(+43) 676 939 7711', '1', '(+43) 676 939 7711', 'AT', 'https://www.siba-academy.com/contact/', 'https://www.facebook.com/sibanili', 'institutions/1616512794_EDAS-SIBA-LOGO.jpg', '2021-03-23 21:19:54', '2021-03-23 21:19:54'),
(139, 'Codarts', 'Codarts is a Rotterdam based international university providing high level professional arts education in music, dance and circus arts. The university has about 1,000 students, of 65 nationalities, and around 480 staff members.', 'Ballet', 'Kruisplein 26\r\n3012 CC Rotterdam\r\nThe Netherlands', 'codarts@codarts.nl', '+31102171100', '1', '+31102171100', 'NL', 'https://www.codarts.nl/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Codarts', 'institutions/1616513007_codarts.JPG', '2021-03-23 21:23:27', '2021-03-23 21:23:27'),
(140, 'Miami City Ballet', 'Miami City Ballet School fosters artistry, love of dance and respect for one another, while preparing students to be versatile 21st century dancers with the necessary technique and physical strength to perform ballets in the Balanchine repertory as well as other choreographic styles. Through the School’s affiliation to the world-renowned Miami City ballet, students are offered unique performance opportunities alongside Miami City Ballet dancers and more.', 'Ballet', 'Ophelia & Juan Js. Roca Center\r\n2200 Liberty Avenue\r\nMiami Beach, FL 33139', 'School@miamicityballet.org', '3059297007', '1', '3059297007', 'US', 'https://www.miamicityballet.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/miamicityballet', 'institutions/1616513136_mcb.png', '2021-03-23 21:25:36', '2021-03-23 21:25:36'),
(141, 'The Harid Conservatory', 'The HARID Conservatory, in Boca Raton, Florida, was established in 1987 to provide superior professional training for gifted young dancers. Students from across the United States and from other countries are selected for enrollment through audition.', 'Ballet', '2285 Potomac Rd\r\nBoca Raton, FL', 'info@harid.edu', '+15619972677', '1', '+15619972677', 'US', 'http://harid.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/TheHaridConservatory', 'institutions/1616513350_harid.jpg', '2021-03-23 21:29:10', '2021-03-23 21:29:10'),
(142, 'Gelsey Kirkland Academy of Classical Ballet', 'The Gelsey Kirkland Academy of Classical Ballet offers year-round, comprehensive training aimed at the full cultural development of the young artist. The Studio Company comprises trainees from the year-round program and professional dancers.', 'Ballet', '29 Jay St\r\nBrooklyn, NY', 'jillc@gelseykirklandballet.org', '+1 212-600-0047', '1', '+1 212-600-0047', 'US', 'http://gelseykirklandacademy.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/GKACB1/about/?ref=page_internal', 'institutions/1616513722_gka.jpg', '2021-03-23 21:35:22', '2021-03-23 21:35:22'),
(143, 'Sharon Lawrence Academy of Dance', 'Welcome to The Sharon Lawrence Academy of Dance.', 'Ballet', '6B 148 Chesterville Rd\r\nCheltenham. Vic   3192', 'sldance@outlook.com', '0416 145 217', '1', '0416 145 217', 'AU', 'http://sldance.com.au/', 'https://www.facebook.com/sharonlawrencedancers/', 'institutions/1616513933_sharon.jpg', '2021-03-23 21:38:53', '2021-03-23 21:38:53'),
(144, 'Béjart Ballet Lausanne', 'Since its inception in 1987, BBL is a reference in the choreographic world. Chosen as his successor by Maurice Béjart, Gil Roman is leading the company and preserving its artistic excellence since the dissappearance of the master in 2007.', 'Ballet', 'Chemin du Presbytère 12\r\nLausanne, Switzerland', 'communication@bejart.ch', '+41 21 641 64 64', '1', '+41 21 641 64 64', 'CH', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/Bejart.Ballet.Lausanne', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/Bejart.Ballet.Lausanne', 'institutions/1616514134_bejart.png', '2021-03-23 21:42:14', '2021-03-23 21:42:14'),
(145, 'The Brookline Ballet School', 'conveniently located at 1431 Beacon Street, Brookline MA, in the Coolidge Corner area.\r\n\r\nThe Green C-Line T stop Winchester/Summit is right at our door. For directions by public transportation visit HopStop.com or Google Maps, click on “Get Directions” and select “By public transit”.', 'Ballet', 'The Brookline Ballet School\r\n1431 Beacon Street\r\nBrookline MA, 02446', 'info@brooklineballet.com', '617.879.9988', '1', '617.879.9988', 'US', 'http://www.brooklineballet.com/', 'www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1616514459_brookline.JPG', '2021-03-23 21:47:39', '2021-03-23 21:47:39'),
(146, 'Metropolitan Ballet Academy', 'Metropolitan Ballet Company is a 501(c) 3 non-profit organization providing scholarships, performance training for pre-professional dancers and outreach programs designed to promote a love and appreciation of dance in our community.', 'Ballet', 'Metropolitan Ballet Academy\r\n700 N. Cedar Road\r\nJenkintown, Pennsylvania 19046 USA', 'info@metropolitanballetacademy.com', '215.663.1665', '1', '215.663.1665', 'US', 'https://metropolitanballetacademy.com/contact/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/MetBalletPA/about/?ref=page_internal', 'institutions/1616515068_metropolitian.JPG', '2021-03-23 21:57:48', '2021-03-23 21:57:48'),
(147, 'Mystic Ballet', 'School of Mystic Ballet and Performing Arts with Mystic Ballet Company, and its venue Mystic Dark Room brings renowned national/international dance artists, and choreographers to our studios right here in Mystic, Connecticut.\r\n\r\nFor 27 years, providing our community with dynamic recreational, enrichment classes for preschoolers to adults, as well as pre-professional and professional training.\r\n\r\nThere is a place for everyone here at School of Mystic Ballet.', 'Ballet', '325 Mistuxet Ave.\r\nStonington CT 06378 – USA', 'info@mysticdarkroom.org', '+ (860) 536 3671', '1', '+ (860) 536 3671', 'US', 'https://mysticballet.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pg/mysticdarkroom', 'institutions/1616515726_mystic.JPG', '2021-03-23 22:08:46', '2021-03-23 22:08:46'),
(148, 'Julie Bromage Dance Academy', 'JBDA is situated in Bedworth Warwickshire and has been established since 1988.Training is offered in a wide range of disciplines for all ages.', 'Ballet', 'Chapel Street\r\nBedworth, UK', 'jbda.information@gmail.com', '+44 7770 631777', '1', '+44 7770 631777', 'GB', 'https://www.facebook.com/Julie-Bromage-Dance-Academy-284306871755641/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Julie-Bromage-Dance-Academy-284306871755641/', 'institutions/1616516011_julie.jpg', '2021-03-23 22:13:31', '2021-03-23 22:13:31'),
(149, 'Swansboro Dance Studio', 'rhythm” and at Swansboro Dance Studio & Emerald Isle Dance Studio we strive to help each dancer find their own rhythm. We believe that a child should be exposed to a variety of activities and encouraged to pursue those that they truly enjoy.', 'Ballet', 'Swansboro Dance Studio\r\nPO Box 1653\r\nSwansboro, NC  28584', 'swansborodance@gmail.com', '910-326-1152', '1', '910-326-1152', 'US', 'http://www.swansborodancestudio.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1616516692_swansboro.png', '2021-03-23 22:24:52', '2021-03-23 22:24:52'),
(150, 'Jason Coleman\'s Ministry of Dance', 'In the spirit of reconciliation The Ministry of Dance acknowledges the Traditional Custodians of country throughout Australia and their connections to land, sea and community. We pay our respect to their elders past and present and extend that respect to all Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples today.', 'Ballet', 'Level 1, 64 Sutton st North Melbourne 3105 VIC, AUS', 'admin@theministryofdance.com.au', '+61 (03) 93296770', '1', '+61 (03) 93296770', 'AU', 'https://www.theministryofdance.com.au/', 'https://www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1616516846_mod.JPG', '2021-03-23 22:27:26', '2021-03-23 22:27:26'),
(151, 'Springfield Ballet', 'pringfield Ballet is a not-for-profit organization dedicated to advancing the art of ballet through premier education, performance, outreach and collaboration. Our home is in The Creamery Arts Center, offering state of the art dance facilities including Harlequin sprung floors. Our classes are not recital driven; all classroom time is spent on dance instruction. Performance opportunities are offered each semester, and all performances take place at the historic Landers Theatre.', 'Ballet', '411 N. Sherman Pkwy.\r\nSpringfield, MO 65802', 'info@springfieldballet.org', '417-862-1343', '1', '417-862-1343', 'US', 'https://springfieldballet.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/SpringfieldBallet', 'institutions/1616517150_springfield.jpg', '2021-03-23 22:32:30', '2021-03-23 22:32:30'),
(152, 'Marat Daukayev School of Ballet', 'Our school teaches Russian style classical ballet that places emphasis on discipline, respect, and self-improvement. We believe practicing ballet routinely is the only way to gain benefit from it, which is why we require signing up for full semesters and encourage students attend multiple classes a week (depending on level).', 'Ballet', '731 S La Brea Ave\r\nLos Angeles, CA', 'admin@maratdaukayev.com', '(323) 965-0333', '1', '(323) 965-0333', 'US', 'https://maratdaukayev.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/maratdaukayevballet', 'institutions/1616517717_maratdaukayew.JPG', '2021-03-23 22:41:57', '2021-03-23 22:41:57'),
(153, 'Intensity Dancers\' Studio', 'Here at Intensity Dancers’ Studio our goal is to inspire, motivate, and enrich our students through the art of dance. We offer only the finest in all styles of dance training. We always have our dancers’ best interests at heart, taking the time to work with each of our students to develop current dancers and encourage new ones. No matter your skill level or goals with dance, you will find a place here at Intensity Dancers Studio!', 'Ballet', '15507 Bull Run Rd\r\nMiami Lakes, FL 33014\r\n786.313.7600', 'info@intensitydancerstudio.com', '786.313.7600', '1', '786.313.7600', 'US', 'http://intensitydancersstudio.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/IntensityDancersStudio', 'institutions/1616517818_intensity.jpg', '2021-03-23 22:43:38', '2021-03-23 22:43:38'),
(154, 'Inland Pacific Ballet', 'Inland Pacific Ballet\'s Founder/Artistic Directors are Victoria Koenig and Kevin Myers. Both are southern California natives and bring a wealth of experience to their visionary leadership of this young Company.', 'Ballet', '9061 Central Avenue\r\nMontclair, CA', 'admin@ipballet.org', '909-482-1590', '1', '909-482-1590', 'US', 'http://www.ipballet.org/index.php', 'https://www.facebook.com/inlandpacificballet/', 'institutions/1616517960_inland.jpg', '2021-03-23 22:46:00', '2021-03-23 22:46:00');
