(155, 'Alicia Extreme Dance Academy', 'Alicia Extreme Dance Academy, Corp. is an educational institution for the development of the arts, established in 2007 , with the purpose of offering the community a varied, fun and educational extracurricular activity.', 'Ballet', 'THE OUTLET MALL, 2do nivel Edif. Caribbean Cinemas, Canovanas\r\nCanóvanas, Puerto Rico', 'info@axdapr.com', '+1 787-256-7717', '1', '+1 787-256-7717', 'US', 'https://aliciaextremedanceacademy.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/axdapr/', 'institutions/1616518215_alicia.JPG', '2021-03-23 22:50:15', '2021-03-23 22:50:15'),
(156, 'Koltun Ballet Academy', 'Koltun Ballet Boston offers the finest dance training in the New England area. Our Academy has won the Youth America Grand Prix Outstanding School Award for the years 2018, 2019 and 2020, as well as many top prizes at other major competitions. We offer a Children’s Ballet Program (ages 3-9) which encourages creativity and cooperation and promotes social interaction and collaboration by providing positive role models in a structured environment.', 'Ballet', '23 Main St (6,515.61 mi)\r\nWatertown, MA, MA 02472', 'info@KoltunBalletBoston.com', '617-901-3792', '1', '617-901-3792', 'US', 'https://koltunballetboston.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/koltunballetboston/', 'institutions/1616518445_koltun.png', '2021-03-23 22:54:05', '2021-03-23 22:54:05'),
(157, 'Alexandra\'s School of Ballet', 'The Alexandra School of Ballet was established in 1949 to provide professional ballet training for students. Over the years classes in modern and variations have been added. The goal of the school has been to develop a sound technique and cultivate an appreciation of dance in every student whether hopes are for a professional career or for cultural enrichment and enjoyment.', 'Ballet', 'Alexandra Ballet\r\n68E Four Seasons Center\r\nChesterfield, Missouri 63017', 'alexandraballet@msn.com', '314.469.6222', '1', '314.469.6222', 'US', 'http://www.alexandraballet.com/', 'www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1616518643_alexandra.JPG', '2021-03-23 22:57:23', '2021-03-23 22:57:23'),
(158, 'University of Arts', 'The University of Arts, (UART), is a public institution of higher education with artistic character in Albania, which offers Bachelor Degree for the first cycle of studies, “Master of Science”/ “Master of Art”, “Professional Master Degree”, “Integrated Master Degree”, in Music, Fine Arts, and Scenic Art.', 'Music', 'Sheshi \"Nënë Tereza\", Nr. 2\r\nTirana, Albania', 'kontakt@uart.edu.al', '+355 4 222 5488', '1', '+355 4 222 5488', 'AL', 'http://www.uart.edu.al/index.php?lang=2', 'https://www.facebook.com/akademiaearteve', 'institutions/1616566703_uoa.jpg', '2021-03-24 12:18:23', '2021-03-24 12:18:23'),
(159, 'Pontifical Catholic University of Argentina', '\"The Catholic University, as a university, is an academic community which, in a rigorous and critical fashion, assists in the protection and development of human dignity and cultural heritage through research, teaching and various services offered to local, national and international communities.', 'Music', 'Av. Alicia Moreau de Justo 1300 (C1107AAZ). C.A.B.A.', 'posder@uca.edu.ar', '0810-2200-822', '1', '0810-2200-822', 'AR', 'http://uca.edu.ar/es', 'https://www.facebook.com/universidad.catolica.argentina', 'institutions/1616567100_uca.JPG', '2021-03-24 12:25:00', '2021-03-24 12:25:00'),
(160, 'National University of Villa María', 'UNVM was born as a community project. The processes for its creation involved collective work. Over the years it was consolidated as an educational, social, cultural and political project that boosted the growth of a city and a region. We invite you to explore its history in a dynamic, interactive and collaborative way, such as the Uni and its community.', 'Music', 'Arturo Jauretche 1555\r\nVilla María, Córdoba, Argentina', 'comunicacion@unvm.edu.ar', '+54 353 453-9100', '1', '+54 353 453-9100', 'AR', 'https://www.unvm.edu.ar/', 'https://www.facebook.com/unvm.edu.ar/', 'institutions/1616567361_nuvm.jpg', '2021-03-24 12:29:21', '2021-03-24 12:29:21'),
(161, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música Astor Piazzolla', 'Its main objective is the training of professional and creative teachers and musicians who have a comprehensive and reflective vision about the field of music as a whole, in accordance with the processes of language transformation and technological development.', 'Music', 'Sarmiento 3401', 'alumnosciudad@gmail.com', '4865-9000', '1', '4865-9000', 'AR', 'https://www.buenosaires.gob.ar/', 'https://www.facebook.com/GCBA/', 'institutions/1616567545_conservatorio.png', '2021-03-24 12:32:25', '2021-03-24 12:32:25'),
(162, 'Escuela de Música Popular de Avellaneda', 'The School of Popular Music of Avellaneda, unique in Argentina and Latin America, counts among its students young people from different countries (Chile, Peru, Mexico, Uruguay, Colombia, Ecuador, Bolivia, France, Holland, Germany) and the interior of our country, a fact that highlights its importance given the high and specific academic level of its teachers , closely related to the institutional objectives of the school.', 'Music', 'Vélez Sársfield 680 -Avellaneda', 'empa@empa.edu.ar', '4203-5772', '1', '4203-5772', 'AR', 'http://www.empa.edu.ar/', 'https://www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1616567664_escuela.JPG', '2021-03-24 12:34:24', '2021-03-24 12:34:24'),
