(187, 'Royal Conservatory of Ghent', 'he Royal Academy of Fine Arts (KASK) and the Royal Conservatoire together form the school or doctor of HOGENT and Howest. The school connects talented and motivated students with excellent pedagogues, active artists, designers and theorists of art and design. The development of the arts, education and research within an international perspective are her main tasks.', 'Music', 'Jozef Kluyskensstraat 2 (3,074.33 mi)\r\nGhent, Belgium, 9000', 'schoolofarts@hogent.be', '+32 9 243 36 00', '1', '+32 9 243 36 00', 'BE', 'https://schoolofartsgent.be/2021/', 'https://www.facebook.com/schoolofartsgent', 'institutions/1616591476_kask.png', '2021-03-24 19:11:16', '2021-03-24 19:11:16'),
