(189, 'Royal Conservatory of Brussels', 'Founded in 1832, the Royal Conservatoire of Brussels is an Arts College run by the Federation Wallonia-Brussels. It is one of the oldest institutions for arts education in Belgium. While building on its prestigious past, the current work of the Conservatoire looks to the future, with a focus on delivering high quality education.', 'Music', 'Rue De La Regence 30, 1000 Brussels, Belgium', 'info@conservatoire.be', '0032 (0)2 511 04 27', '1', '0032 (0)2 511 04 27', 'BE', 'http://www.conservatoire.be/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CRBruxelles', 'institutions/1617608087_crdb.png', '2021-04-05 13:34:47', '2021-04-05 13:34:47'),
(190, 'Muda Institute', 'Het MUDA is een secundaire school voor muziek en dans. Je behaalt er je diploma secundair onderwijs in combinatie met een opleiding in muziek of dans op topniveau. In het MUDA kan je kiezen voor de opleiding hedendaagse dans, klassieke muziek, jazz/pop, songwriting, productie of muziektheater/musical.', 'Music', 'Hofbilkstraat 21, Evergem, Belgium', 'info@muda.be', '+32 9 394 30 80', '1', '+32 9 394 30 80', 'BE', 'http://www.muda.be/', 'https://www.facebook.com/muda.be/', 'institutions/1617608454_muda.png', '2021-04-05 13:40:54', '2021-04-05 13:40:54'),
(191, 'Luca School of Arts', 'LUCA School of Arts is the only university college in Flanders exclusively dedicated to art and design, making it unique in the region. The art school combines the strengths and expertise of five renowned Flemish higher education institutions for art and design, spread across Brussels, Genk, Ghent and Leuven.', 'Music', 'Paleizenstraat 70, 1030 Brussel', 'artoffice@luca-arts.be', '+32 2 447 10 00', '1', '+32 2 447 10 00', 'BE', 'https://www.luca-arts.be/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/LucaSchoolOfArts/', 'institutions/1617608761_luca.png', '2021-04-05 13:46:01', '2021-04-05 13:46:01'),
(192, 'Royal Conservatory of Liège', 'The Royal Conservatory of Liège is a Higher School of Arts of the Wallonia-Brussels Federation that offers higher level artistic training (Bacheliers, Masters and Aggregations) in the field of music and theatre.', 'Music', 'Rue Forgeur 14, Liège, Belgium', 'info@crlg.be', '+32 4 222 03 06', '1', '+32 4 222 03 06', 'BE', 'https://www.crlg.be/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConservatoireLiege', 'institutions/1617608959_ConservatoireLiege.png', '2021-04-05 13:49:19', '2021-04-05 13:49:19'),
(193, 'Institut Supérieur de Musique et Pédagogie', 'Mesdames et Messieurs, Chers amies et amis, Chères étudiantes, chers étudiants,\r\n\r\nBienvenue à l’IMEP, Institut supérieur de Musique et de Pédagogie…. Royal !\r\n\r\nMoi qui pensais, comme le premier Directeur de l’IMEP, Paul Léonard, avoir « tout vu à l’IMEP », j’étais loin du compte ! Pour la première fois depuis sa création, l’Institut ferma les portes de ses bâtiments en pleine année académique, le 18 mars 2020.', 'Music', 'Rue Henri Blès, 33A\r\n5000 Namur\r\nBelgique', 'info@imep.be', '+32 (0)81 73 64 37', '1', '+32 (0)81 28 02 61', 'BE', 'http://www.imep.be', 'https://www.facebook.com/imepnamur/', 'institutions/1617612778_imep.png', '2021-04-05 14:52:58', '2021-04-05 14:52:58'),
(194, 'Institut Jaques-Dalcroze (Brussels)', 'La Rythmique Dalcroze s’adresse aux personnes de tout âge (à partir de 3 ans) et de tout niveau (des amateurs aux professionnels). Elle est une base de formation pour toutes les disciplines artistiques et valorise la confiance, la sociabilité, l’écoute, la connaissance de soi et de l’autre.', 'Music', 'Rue Henri Wafelaerts 53, 1060', 'officedalcroze@gmail.com', '02 537 47 93', '1', '02 537 47 93', 'BE', 'http://dalcroze.eu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/institut.dalcroze', 'institutions/1617613466_rthmique.png', '2021-04-05 15:04:26', '2021-04-05 15:04:26'),
(195, 'Conservatório Brasileiro de Música', 'Na trajetória dos 80 anos de existência do Conservatório Brasileiro de Música - Centro Universitário Brasileiro de Educação, dois princípios sempre foram a marca da Instituição: a Renovação e a Tradição. Durante oito décadas a tradição se mantém na formação dos músicos em áreas performáticas, instrumentos e canto, na composição, regência, licenciatura, musicoterapia e música e tecnologia.', 'Music', 'Avenida Graça Aranha, nº. 57, 12º andar, Castelo, Rio de Janeiro, RJ.', 'contato@cbmmusica.edu.br', '(21) 3478-7600', '1', '(21) 3478-7600', 'BR', 'http://www.cbmmusica.edu.br/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CBM.CEU/', 'institutions/1617614002_cbm.jpg', '2021-04-05 15:13:22', '2021-04-05 15:13:22'),
(196, 'Conservatório de Tatuí', 'A seleção de novos alunos aos cursos de música ocorre no início de cada semestre, de acordo com a demanda dos cursos, ou a qualquer tempo em caso de existência de vagas remanescentes. Para os cursos de artes cênicas e luteria as seleções são anuais, acontecendo no início de cada ano letivo.\r\n\r\nPodem se inscrever aos cursos qualquer interessado – com ou sem conhecimento musical – respeitando a idade mínima indicada a cada curso.', 'Music', 'Rua São Bento, 415 - Centro - 18.270-820 - Tatuí/SP', 'secretaria@conservatoriodetatui.org.br', '+55 11 2193-8000', '1', '+55 11 2193-8000', 'BR', 'http://www.conservatoriodetatui.org.br/', 'https://www.facebook.com/governosp/', 'institutions/1617614766_logo-cdmcc-padrao.jpg', '2021-04-05 15:26:06', '2021-04-05 15:26:06'),
(197, 'Escola de Música da Universidade Federal do Rio de Janeiro', 'A ESCOLA DE MÚSICA se origina do Imperial Conservatório de Música, fundado em 13 de agosto de 1848. Ao longo do tempo recebeu várias denominações - entre elas Instituto Nacional de Música e Escola Nacional de Música. A atual data dos anos 1960.', 'Music', 'Escola de Música da UFRJ\r\n Edifício Ventura Corporate Towers\r\nAv. República do Chile, 330\r\n21o andar, Torre Leste\r\nCentro - Rio de Janeiro, RJ', 'administracao@musica.ufrj.br', '+55 21 2240-1391', '1', '+55 21 2240-1391', 'BR', 'http://www.musica.ufrj.br/', 'https://www.facebook.com/musicaufrj/?ref=ts&fref=ts', 'institutions/1617615134_logonovoc.png', '2021-04-05 15:32:14', '2021-04-05 15:32:14'),
(198, 'Escola de Música do Estado de São Paulo - Universidade Livre  de Música', 'The Sao Paulo State Music School – EMESP Tom Jobim provides education for children and young adults on classical and popular music, and further development for musicians who have finished their education and wish to evolve their training. More than 1300 students dispose of a range of 40 programmes.', 'Music', 'Largo General Osório, 147 - Luz\r\n01213-010 - São Paulo/SP', 'sau@santamarcelinacultura.org.br', '(11) 98888-9868', '1', '(11) 98888-9868', 'BR', 'http://emesp.org.br/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/tomjobimemesp/', 'institutions/1617615413_logo-emesp.png', '2021-04-05 15:36:53', '2021-04-05 15:36:53'),
(199, 'Escola Municipal de Música de São Paulo', 'A Fundação Theatro Municipal de São Paulo foi instituída pela Lei 15.380 de 27 de maio de 2011 e regulamentada pelo decreto nº 53.225, de 19 de junho.\r\n\r\nO Estatuto traz um novo formato administrativo: uma Fundação de Direito Público vinculada à Secretaria Municipal de Cultura, que apresenta órgãos de Direção, Conselho Deliberativo e Conselho Fiscal em sua estrutura organizacional.', 'Music', 'Avenida São João, 281\r\nSé - São Paulo, SP', 'escutamunicipal@santamarcelinacultura.org.br', '55 11 4571 0401', '1', '55 11 4571 0401', 'BR', 'https://theatromunicipal.org.br/pt-br/formacao/escola-municipal-de-musica/', 'https://www.facebook.com/theatromunicipalsp', 'institutions/1617615724_logo-tmsp.png', '2021-04-05 15:42:04', '2021-04-05 15:42:04'),
(200, 'Conservatorio Municipal de Arte de Guarulhos', 'O público alvo do Conservatório Musical de Guarulhos está inserido em todas as faixas etárias. A música pode estar presente e ser assimilada por crianças,adolescentes, jovens, adultos e até pela terceira idade. Nossos objetivos são o de capacitar o aluno a exercer uma atividade profissional ou para própria satisfação. Incentivar as manifestações artísticas, promover iniciação para o trabalho de carácter artístico.', 'Music', 'Rua João Gonçalves, 52 – 2º andar Centro Guarulhos – SP', 'conservatoriomg@gmail.com', '(11) 2409-5830', '1', '(11) 2409-5830', 'BR', 'http://conservatorioguarulhos.com.br/', 'https://www.facebook.com/cmusical.gru/', 'institutions/1617615901_conservatorio-musical-guarulhos.png', '2021-04-05 15:45:01', '2021-04-05 15:45:01'),
(201, 'Federal University of Rio Grande do Sul', 'The Universidade Federal do Rio Grande do Sul, UFRGS (Federal University of Rio Grande do Sul) is a century-old educational institution nationally and internationally recognized. It is centered in Porto Alegre – the capital city of the State of Rio Grande do Sul – and it offers academic programs from all different fields of knowledge, for all stages of education, ranging from elementary to graduate school.', 'Music', 'v. Paulo Gama, 110 - Bairro Farroupilha - Porto Alegre - Rio Grande do Sul', 'imprensa@ufrgs.br', '+55 51 33086000', '1', '+55 51 33086000', 'BR', 'http://www.ufrgs.br/ufrgs/inicial', 'https://www.facebook.com/ufrgsnoticias/', 'institutions/1617616365_ufrgs.jpg', '2021-04-05 15:52:45', '2021-04-05 15:52:45'),
(202, 'Faculdade de Música do Espírito Santo \"Maurício de Oliveira\"', 'A Faculdade de Música Maurício de Oliveira (Fames), é uma Instituição de Ensino Superior Isolada (IES), de caráter autárquico, mantida pelo Governo do Estado do Espírito Santo, vinculada à Secretaria de Estado de Educação (Sedu) e ao Sistema Estadual de Ensino, através do Conselho Estadual de Educação(CEE), e por este inspecionado', 'Music', 'Praça Américo Poli Monjardim, 60 - Centro\r\nCEP: 29010-640 - Vitória / ES', 'ouvidoria@fames.es.gov.br', '(27) 3636-3600', '1', '(27) 3636-3600', 'BR', 'https://fames.es.gov.br/', 'https://www.facebook.com/faculdadedemusica.es', 'institutions/1617616695_fames.png', '2021-04-05 15:58:15', '2021-04-05 15:58:15'),
(203, 'Academy of Music, Dance, and Fine Arts (Plovdiv)', 'The Academy of Music, Dance and Fine Arts in Plovdiv is organizing the First International Conference on \"Science, Education and Innovation in the Field of Arts\". This forum is a vivid expression of the endeavor and the strong motivation of leading Bulgarian and foreign academics in the field of music, choreography, art and pedagogy.', 'Music', '2, Todor Samodumov Str\r\nP.O. Box 783\r\n4000 Plovdiv\r\nBulgaria', 'office@artacademyplovdiv.com', '+359 32 601 441', '1', '+359 32 601 441', 'BG', 'http://www.artacademyplovdiv.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/artacademyplovdiv.amtii/', 'institutions/1617617018_artacademy.png', '2021-04-05 16:03:39', '2021-04-05 16:03:39'),
(204, 'National Academy of Music (Sofia)', 'National academy of Music is the most authoritative higher education music school in Bulgaria with the oldest, best established and most efficient professional traditions, which focuses the potential and achievements of the most significant, renowned artists in this area in the same amount today, as it has done in the past. Its graduates win top prizes in prestigious international competitions and take part in international music initiatives.', 'Music', 'Bulgaria 1505 Sofia, bul. \"Evlogi i Hristo Georgievi\" № 94', 'info@nma.bg', '+359 2 4409 740', '1', '+359 2 4409 740', 'BG', 'http://nma.bg/en/', '-', 'institutions/1617617432_nma.png', '2021-04-05 16:10:32', '2021-04-05 16:10:32'),
(205, 'Banff Centre', 'Founded in 1933 by the University of Alberta, Department of Extension, with a grant from the U.S.-based Carnegie Foundation, Banff Centre for Arts and Creativity began with a single course in drama. Its success generated additional arts programs and the Centre became known as The Banff School of Fine Arts in 1935. While arts programming continued to grow and flourish, conferences were introduced in 1953 and management programs in 1954.', 'Music', '107 Tunnel Mountain Drive\r\nPO Box 1020 Banff, Alberta\r\nCanada', 'reservations@banffcentre.ca', '403.762.6100', '1', '403.762.6100', 'CA', 'https://www.banffcentre.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/BanffCentre/', 'institutions/1617622601_banff.jpg', '2021-04-05 17:36:41', '2021-04-05 17:36:41'),
(206, 'MacEwan University', 'MacEwan University provides a transformative education in a collaborative and supportive learning environment. Creativity thrives here—through research and innovation that engage students, faculty and the community.', 'Music', '10700 104 Ave NW\r\nEdmonton, AB T5J 4S2', 'info@macewan.ca', '780-497-5000', '1', '780-497-5000', 'CA', 'https://www.macewan.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/MacEwanUniversity/', 'institutions/1617622958_macewan-logo-color.png', '2021-04-05 17:42:38', '2021-04-05 17:42:38'),
(207, 'University of Alberta', 'The University of Alberta in Edmonton is one of Canada\'s top teaching and research universities, with an international reputation for excellence across the humanities, sciences, creative arts, business, engineering and health sciences.', 'Music', '116 St. and 85 Ave.\r\nEdmonton, Alberta T6G 2R3', 'chat@ualberta.ca', '+1 780-492-3111', '1', '+1 780-492-3111', 'CA', 'www.ualberta.ca', 'https://www.facebook.com/ualberta', 'institutions/1617632323_ualberta-logo-reverse.png', '2021-04-05 20:18:43', '2021-04-05 20:18:43'),
