(209, 'University of Lethbridge', 'Our main campus is located in the city of Lethbridge, and combines breathtaking natural beauty with cutting edge learning and research facilities. With seven faculties and schools, the Lethbridge Campus offers a range of undergraduate and graduate programs for all types of students.', 'Music', '4401 University Drive\r\nLethbridge, Alberta\r\nT1K 3M4\r\nCanada', 'inquiries@uleth.ca', '403-329-2111', '1', '403-329-2111', 'CA', 'https://www.ulethbridge.ca/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ulethbridge.ca', 'institutions/1617632840_ulethbridge.png', '2021-04-05 20:27:20', '2021-04-05 20:27:20'),
