(257, 'Music Academy Zagreb', 'The Music Academy of the University of Zagreb is the largest and oldest higher education music institution in the Republic of Croatia. She is a direct successor to the Music School of the Croatian Music Institute founded in 1829, under the auspices of which she started acting as a higher education music institution in 1921. Since 1979, the Music Academy has been a constituent of the University of Zagreb.', 'Music', 'Trg Republike Hrvatske 12\r\n10000 Zagreb\r\nEU CROATIA', 'prodekan.nastava@muza.hr', '+385 (01) 4810 200', '1', '+385 (01) 4810 200', 'AF', 'http://www.muza.unizg.hr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Academy-of-Music-University-of-Zagreb/120317044706311?rf=193857650629267', 'institutions/1618837187_MAZ.JPG', '2021-04-19 18:59:47', '2021-04-19 18:59:47'),
