(260, 'Juraj Dobrila University of Pula', 'National identities and their cultural riches greatly contribute to the development of Pula as a multicultural and multiethnic city oriented towards the European way of life. The murmur of all the world\'s languages and numerous cultural events - festivals, concerts, exhibitions, theatres and cultural centres will complete your life in a city that has always kept its doors wide open to all. Therefore, come to Pula, get to know the beauty and cordiality of the 3000-year-old city.', 'Music', 'A: Zagrebačka 30\r\n52100 Pula\r\nCroatia', 'ured@unipu.hr', '+385 52 377', '1', '+385 52 377', 'HR', 'https://www.unipu.hr/search?sq=+index.php', 'https://www.facebook.com/unipu.hr', 'institutions/1618917568_puli.jpg', '2021-04-20 17:19:28', '2021-04-20 17:19:28'),
(261, 'Arte Music Academy', 'The Arte Music Academy started its operation in September 2002 filling a long existing gap in Cyprus and laying the foundation for a substantial progress in music. The Academy is the first Institution of higher music education in Cyprus and it\'s staff consists of eminent musicians and scholars.', 'Music', 'Leonidou 34-36 , Nicosia 1097 , Cyprus', 'artechno@spidernet.com.cy', '+357 22 676 823', '1', '+357 22 676 823', 'CY', 'https://www.cyprus-college.com/arte-music-academy', 'www.facebook.com', 'institutions/1618917789_cyprus.JPG', '2021-04-20 17:23:09', '2021-04-20 17:23:09'),
