(271, 'Conservatoire national supérieur de musique et de danse de  Lyon', 'A major international school of musical and choreographic arts, the National Conservatory of Music and Dance in Lyon trains with demand and passion the performers, creators, researchers and teachers of tomorrow, building on an innovative pedagogical dynamic carried by leading teachers, attentive to the evolution of the contemporary scene and promoting the aesthetic, intellectual and societal openness of its students.', 'Music', '3 quai chauveau\r\nLyon, France', 'communication@cnsmd-lyon.fr', '+33 4 72 19 26 26', '1', '+33 4 72 19 26 26', 'FR', 'http://www.cnsmd-lyon.fr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CNSMDLyon/', 'institutions/1618922154_cns.jpg', '2021-04-20 18:35:54', '2021-04-20 18:35:54'),
