(283, 'Lawrence Conservatory of Music, Lawrence University', 'Lawrence is a supportive and welcoming academic community of 1,500 intellectually curious, diverse, multi-interested students from nearly every state and 50 countries—all committed to a rigorous and challenging educational experience.', 'Music', '711 E. Boldt Way\r\nAppleton, WI 54911\r\n(920) 832-7000', 'communications@lawrence.edu', '+1 920-832-7000', '1', '+1 920-832-7000', 'US', 'www.lawrence.edu/conservatory', 'https://www.facebook.com/lawrenceuni', 'institutions/1618995834_lawrence.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:03:54', '2021-04-21 15:03:54'),
(284, 'West Virginia University', 'As a land-grant institution, the faculty, staff and students at West Virginia University commit to creating a diverse and inclusive culture that advances education, healthcare and prosperity for all by providing access and opportunity; by advancing high-impact research; and by leading transformation in West Virginia and the world through local, state and global engagement.', 'Music', 'West Virginia University\r\nPO Box 6201\r\nMorgantown, West Virginia 26506', 'web_services@mail.wvu.edu', '+1 304-293-0111', '1', '+1 304-293-0111', 'US', 'https://www.wvu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/wvumountaineers', 'institutions/1618995986_west virgina.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:06:26', '2021-04-21 15:06:26'),
(285, 'University of Washington', 'The UW is one of the world’s preeminent public universities. Our impact on individuals, our region and the world is profound — whether we are launching young people into a boundless future or confronting the grand challenges of our time through undaunted research and scholarship. Ranked No. 14 in the world on the 2018 Academic Ranking of World Universities, the UW educates more than 54,000 students annually.', 'Music', 'Seattle, WA 98105', 'uwsocial@uw.edu', '+1 206-543-2100', '1', '+1 206-543-2100', 'US', 'https://www.washington.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/UofWA', 'institutions/1618996102_washington.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:08:22', '2021-04-21 15:08:22'),
(286, 'University of Puget Sound School of Music', 'Founded in 1888 in a vibrant port city in the Pacific Northwest, the University of Puget Sound is an independent, residential, and predominantly undergraduate liberal arts college, with graduate programs in education and health sciences. Our beautiful 97-acre campus supports connection with the world it serves, from the tide flats of Tacoma to the Pacific Rim and beyond.', 'Music', 'University of Puget Sound\r\n1500 N. Warner St.\r\nTacoma, WA 98416', 'communications@pugetsound.edu', '+1 253-879-3100', '1', '+1 253-879-3100', 'US', 'http://www.pugetsound.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/univpugetsound/', 'institutions/1618997192_puget sound.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:26:32', '2021-04-21 15:26:32'),
(287, 'Pacific Lutheran University Department of Music', 'Founded in 1888 in a vibrant port city in the Pacific Northwest, the University of Puget Sound is an independent, residential, and predominantly undergraduate liberal arts college, with graduate programs in education and health sciences. Our beautiful 97-acre campus supports connection with the world it serves, from the tide flats of Tacoma to the Pacific Rim and beyond.', 'Music', '12180 Park Avenue S.\r\nTacoma, WA 98447', 'events@plu.edu', '253-535-7411', '1', '253-535-7411', 'US', 'https://www.plu.edu/music', 'https://www.facebook.com/Pacific.Lutheran.University', 'institutions/1618997908_plu.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:38:28', '2021-04-21 15:38:28'),
(288, 'Cornish College of Arts', 'Cornish College of the Arts is the premier accredited arts college in the Northwest, inspiring the highest standards of artistic and academic excellence.', 'Music', 'Cornish College of the Arts\r\n1000 Lenora St.,\r\nSeattle, WA 98121', 'communications@cornish.edu', '+1 206-726-5016', '1', '+1 206-726-5016', 'US', 'https://www.cornish.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CornishCollegeOfTheArts', 'institutions/1618998042_cornish.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:40:42', '2021-04-21 15:40:42'),
(289, 'Virginia Wesleyan University', 'Virginia Wesleyan University is Coastal Virginia\'s premier university of the liberal arts and sciences. Situated on a 300-acre park-like campus in Virginia Beach, the University annually enrolls approximately 1,600 students in undergraduate, graduate, and online programs.', 'Music', '5817 Wesleyan Drive\r\nVirginia Beach, Virginia 23455', 'virginiawesleyan@vwu.edu', '+1 757-455-3200', '1', '+1 757-455-3200', 'US', 'www.vwu.edu', 'https://www.facebook.com/vawesleyan', 'institutions/1618998178_virginia.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:42:58', '2021-04-21 15:42:58'),
(290, 'Hampton University', 'Hampton University is nestled along the banks of the Virginia Peninsula, near the mouth of the Chesapeake Bay. The surrounding city of Hampton features a wide array of business and industrial enterprises, retail and residential areas, historical sites, and miles of waterfront and beaches.', 'Music', '130 William R. Harvey Way\r\nHampton, VA 23668', 'ucadmissions@hamptonu.edu', '+1 757-788-8968', '1', '+1 757-728-4829', 'US', 'www.hamptonu.edu', 'https://www.facebook.com/huonline', 'institutions/1618998458_hampton.PNG', '2021-04-21 15:47:38', '2021-04-21 15:48:02'),
(291, 'Shenandoah University', 'Shenandoah University educates and inspires individuals to be critical, reflective thinkers; lifelong learners; and ethical, compassionate citizens who are committed to making responsible contributions within a community, a nation and the world.', 'Music', '1460 University Drive, Winchester, VA 22601', 'Admit@su.edu', '540-665-4500', '1', '540-665-4500', 'US', 'https://www.su.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ShenandoahUniversity', 'institutions/1618999582_shenandoah.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:06:22', '2021-04-21 16:06:22'),
(292, 'Old Dominion University', 'We have history together. Our region. Our city. Our university. All of us. At Old Dominion University, we are first-generation students, fourth-generation veterans and the next generation of risk-taking entrepreneurs who will invent our own tables instead of waiting for a seat at another\'s.', 'Music', 'Old Dominion University\r\nNorfolk, VA 23529', 'admissions@odu.edu', '+1 757-683-3000', '1', '+1 757-683-3000', 'US', 'http://www.odu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Old.Dominion.University/', 'institutions/1618999770_dominion.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:09:30', '2021-04-21 16:09:30'),
(293, 'Norfolk State University', 'Norfolk State University, a comprehensive urban public institution, is committed to transforming students\' lives through exemplary teaching, research and service.', 'Music', '700 Park Avenue Norfolk VA 23504', 'admissions@nsu.edu', '757-823-8600', '1', '757-823-8600', 'US', 'http://www.nsu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/norfolkstateuniversity/', 'institutions/1618999888_norfolk.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:11:28', '2021-04-21 16:11:28'),
(294, 'Christopher Newport University', 'Christopher Newport University -- Lead a life of significance. Leadership • Service • Honor • Excellence', 'Music', 'One Avenue of the Arts | Newport News, VA 23606', 'admit@cnu.edu', '+1 757-594-7000', '1', '+1 757-594-7000', 'US', 'https://cnu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/christophernewportuniversity', 'institutions/1619000324_christopher.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:18:44', '2021-04-21 16:18:44'),
(295, 'Virginia Commonwealth University', 'Our tenacity.\r\nOur love of the city.\r\nOur commitment to \r\ndiversity and access.\r\nThese are the things that drive us and make us one of America’s premier research universities. They are what set us apart from your average college. They are how we make it real.', 'Music', 'Virginia Commonwealth University\r\nRichmond, Virginia 23284', 'homepage@vcu.edu', '(804) 828-0100', '1', '(804) 828-0100', 'US', 'https://vcu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/virginiacommonwealthuniversity', 'institutions/1619000457_vcu.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:20:57', '2021-04-21 16:20:57'),
(296, 'James Madison University', 'Founded in 1908, James Madison University is a public university located in Virginia’s Shenandoah Valley. JMU is fast becoming one of the nation’s leading lights in higher education because students enjoy unusually engaged relationships with world-class faculty who are here because they want to pursue knowledge and make teaching their No. 1 priority.', 'Music', '800 SOUTH MAIN STREET\r\nHARRISONBURG, VA 22807', 'publicaffairs@jmu.edu', '+1 540-568-6211', '1', '+1 540-568-6211', 'US', 'https://www.jmu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/jamesmadisonuniversity', 'institutions/1619000631_jmu.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:23:51', '2021-04-21 16:23:51'),
(297, 'George Mason University', 'George Mason University is the largest public research university in Virginia, serving more than 37,000 students. We are an open campus, and we welcome news media to visit and learn more about the exciting work that takes place here.', 'Music', 'George Mason University\r\n4400 University Drive\r\nFairfax, Virginia 22030', 'social@gmu.edu', '+1 703-993-1000', '1', '+1(703)993-1000', 'US', 'https://www2.gmu.edu', 'https://www.facebook.com/georgemason', 'institutions/1619000778_georgemason.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:26:18', '2021-04-21 16:26:18'),
(298, 'University of Utah School of Music', 'Over the past five years, few public research universities have risen in stature as quickly for both academic excellence and the creation of life-changing technological and medical innovation than the University of Utah. With the urban and cultural advantages of Salt Lake City out its front door, and the majestic Wasatch Mountains and some of the best outdoor recreational opportunities in the world in its backyard,', 'Music', 'School of Music\r\nThe University of Utah\r\n1375 East Presidents Circle\r\n204 David P. Gardner Hall\r\nSalt Lake City, Utah 84112-0030', 'recruit@music.utah.edu', '801.581.6762', '1', '801.581.6762', 'US', 'http://www.music.utah.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/uofumusic', 'institutions/1619001477_utah.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:37:57', '2021-04-21 16:37:57'),
(299, 'Brigham Young University School of Music', 'One of the lasting traditions of Brigham Young University is its strong cultural emphasis and support of the fine arts. Historically, the music department has been one of BYU’s academic stars, and today the BYU School of Music continues this tradition as it leads toward a bright future.', 'Music', 'School of Music\r\nBrigham Young University\r\nC-550 Harris Fine Arts Center\r\nProvo, UT 84602', 'music@byu.edu', '+18014228903', '1', '+18014228903', 'US', 'http://www.music.utah.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/schoolofmusicbyu', 'institutions/1619001656_byu.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:40:56', '2021-04-21 16:40:56'),
(300, 'Houston Baptist University School of Music (SoM)', 'The mission of Houston Baptist University is to provide a learning experience that instills in students a passion for academic, spiritual and professional excellence as a result of our central confession, “Jesus Christ is Lord.”\r\nHouston Baptist University offers an intimate college environment in the heart of one of the most vibrant and diverse cities in the United States: Houston, Texas. Coming to HBU as a student is about more than books, tests and lectures.', 'Music', 'Houston Baptist University\r\n7502 Fondren Rd\r\nHouston, TX 77074', 'OnlineAdmissions@HBU.edu', '(281) 649-3000', '1', '(281) 649-3000', 'US', 'https://hbu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/HoustonBaptistUniversity', 'institutions/1619002080_hbu.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:48:00', '2021-04-21 16:48:45'),
(301, 'Baylor University The School of Music', 'The Baylor University School of Music provides transformational experiences that prepare students for careers in music. Our students thrive in a Christian environment characterized by a nurturing resident faculty, an unwavering pursuit of musical excellence, a global perspective, dedication to service, and devotion to faith.', 'Music', 'School of Music\r\nBaylor University\r\nOne Bear Place #97408\r\nWaco, TX 76798-7408', 'Ruth_Tucker@baylor.edu', '+1 800-229-5678', '1', '1-800-229-5678', 'US', 'www.baylor.edu/music', 'https://www.facebook.com/BaylorUniversity1845/', 'institutions/1619002314_baylor.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:51:54', '2021-04-21 16:51:54'),
(302, 'University of Texas Sarah and Ernest Butler School of Music', 'Music has been a critical part of life at UT Austin since 1914. The Sarah and Ernest Butler School of Music is where students full of potential find their mentors and guides in a faculty comprised of extraordinary performers, composers, and scholars. Days and nights at the Butler School are charged with the energy of new opportunities, new challenges and new contributions to the art form.', 'Music', 'Sarah and Ernest Butler School of Music\r\n2406 Robert Dedman Dr.\r\nStop E3100\r\nAustin, TX 78712-1555', 'generalinfo@mail.music.utexas.edu', '(512) 471-7764', '1', '(512) 471-7764', 'US', 'http://music.utexas.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ButlerSOM', 'institutions/1619002764_butler.PNG', '2021-04-21 16:59:24', '2021-04-21 16:59:24'),
(303, 'University of North Texas College of Music', 'The College of Music is the largest public university music program in the United States and one of the most globally respected. We offer fully accredited degrees from the bachelor to doctoral levels and is home to the world’s first jazz studies degree program. Faculty include internationally acclaimed artists and scholars in composition, conducting, ethnomusicology, music education, music entrepreneurship, music history, music theory and performance.', 'Music', '1155 Union Circle #311367\r\nDenton, Texas', 'music.marketing@unt.edu', '+1 940-565-2791', '1', '940-565-2000', 'US', 'https://music.unt.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/untcollegeofmusic', 'institutions/1619002953_northtexas.PNG', '2021-04-21 17:02:33', '2021-04-21 17:02:33'),
(304, 'Texas Tech University School of Music', 'Welcome to the School of Music here at Texas Tech University\'s J.T.& Margaret Talkington College of the Visual and Performing Arts.\r\nWe are delighted to share with you the talent and dynamic verve that make our School of Music a destination of choice for all music educators.', 'Music', '18th and Boston Avenue Box 42033, Lubbock TX 79409-2033', 'schoolofmusic@ttu.edu', '806.742.2270', '1', '806.742.2270', 'US', 'www.depts.ttu.edu/music', 'https://www.facebook.com/TTUSchoolOfMusic', 'institutions/1619003053_texas tech.PNG', '2021-04-21 17:04:13', '2021-04-21 17:04:13'),
(305, 'West Texas A&M University School of Music', 'West Texas A&M University is committed to providing a technology-rich education, constantly improving its academically challenging educational experience, and engaging students through effective teaching and practical experiences involving inquiry, discussion, research, creative activities, experiential learning and service', 'Music', 'WTAMU Box 60907\r\nCanyon, TX\r\n79016-0001\r\n1-800-99-WTAMU', 'admissions@wtamu.edu', '+1 806-651-0000', '1', '+1 806-651-0000', 'US', 'https://www.wtamu.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/wtamu', 'institutions/1619004107_west texas.PNG', '2021-04-21 17:21:47', '2021-04-21 17:21:47'),
(306, 'Haute école des arts du Rhin', 'La Haute école des arts du Rhin propose une exposition en plein air de sculptures. Une quinzaine d’artistes, de générations et d’esthétiques différentes, investissent le jardin de l’école à Strasbourg.', 'Music', 'Strasbourg\r\nPlastic Arts Site 1 Rue de\r\nl\'Académie CS 10032\r\n67082 Strasbourg cedex\r\n-33 (0)3 69 06 37 77', 'prenom-compose.nom-compose@hear.fr', '+ 33 (0)3 69 76 61 06', '1', '-', 'FR', 'http://www.hear.fr/', 'https://fr-fr.facebook.com/HEAR.fr/', 'institutions/1619522486_HEAR FR.JPG', '2021-04-27 17:21:26', '2021-04-27 17:21:26'),
(307, 'Hochschule für Musik und Tanz Köln', 'The University of Music and Dance Cologne has a wide range of courses with different bachelor and master degrees as well as the possibility of a doctorate and the concert exam. You can find an overview of the undergraduate and postgraduate courses at the university under range of courses .', 'Music', 'Theodor-Heuss-Ring 38-40\r\n50668 Cologne', 'tudiensekretariat@hfmt-koeln.de', '+49 (221) 28380 0', '1', '+49 (221) 28380 0', 'DE', 'https://www.hfmt-koeln.de/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Hochschule-f%FCr-Musik-und-Tanz-K%F6ln-952375948177730', 'institutions/1619522907_hfmt.JPG', '2021-04-27 17:28:27', '2021-04-27 17:28:27'),
(308, 'Leopold-Mozart-Zentrum Augsburg', 'The University of Augsburg is a comparatively young university. It was only founded in 1970 by the Free State of Bavaria as a reform university. She successfully used the associated opportunities to develop dynamically and to orient her own profile to the challenges of the present and the future.\r\n\r\nInitially focused on law, economics, social sciences and humanities, the University of Augsburg has continuously developed promising fields of natural and technical sciences.', 'Music', 'Central postal address:\r\nUniversity of Augsburg\r\nUniversitätsstrasse 2\r\n86159 Augsburg', 'florian.hummel@phil.uni-augsburg.de', '+49 821 598-0', '1', '+49 821 598-0', 'DE', 'https://www.uni-augsburg.de/de/fakultaet/philsoz/lmz/', 'https://www.facebook.com/uni.augsburg/', 'institutions/1619523120_una.JPG', '2021-04-27 17:32:00', '2021-04-27 17:32:00');
