(309, 'Hochschule für Musik \"Hanns Eisler\"', 'We look forward to welcoming you to the Hanns Eisler University of Music! If you are starting your studies soon, you are at the right place.\r\n\r\nBelow you will find important information about enrollment as well as the program of our Welcome Weeks.', 'Music', 'Hanns Eisler University of Music Berlin\r\nCharlottenstr. 55\r\n10117 Berlin', 'rektorat@hfm-berlin.de', '+4930688305700', '1', '+4930688305700', 'DE', 'http://www.hfm-berlin.de/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Hochschule-f%C3%BCr-Musik-Hanns-Eisler-Berlin-449922482010251', 'institutions/1619523308_hfm.JPG', '2021-04-27 17:35:08', '2021-04-27 17:39:37'),
(310, 'Berlin University of the Arts', 'The start of lectures in the summer semester is April 12, 2021 .\r\n\r\nDue to the current situation, the summer semester 2021 at the UdK Berlin will also take place as a \"hybrid semester\", ie, there are, if possible, both face-to-face teaching and digital formats. This can also be different in the various degree programs at the UdK.', 'Music', 'University of the Arts\r\nEinstein 43-53\r\nD- 10587 Berlin', 'studyguide@udk-berlin.de', '(030) 3185-0', '1', '(030) 3185-0', 'DE', 'https://www.udk-berlin.de/startseite/', 'http://www.facebook.com/udkberlin', 'institutions/1619523535_udk.JPG', '2021-04-27 17:38:55', '2021-04-27 17:38:55'),
(311, 'University of the Arts Bremen', 'Sustainable ideas to strengthen the digitization skills of the retail trade in Bremen - that is the aim of the “Digital Retail Consulting for Bremen” project at the University of Bremen.', 'Music', 'University of Bremen\r\nBibliothekstrasse 1\r\n28359 Bremen', 'zsb@uni-bremen.de', '+49 421 218-1', '1', '+49 421 218-1', 'DE', 'http://www.hfk-bremen.de/en/', '-', 'institutions/1619551079_hfk.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:17:59', '2021-04-28 01:17:59'),
(312, 'Hochschule für Musik Detmold', 'The members and relatives from the study, teaching and administration of the Hochschule für Musik Detmold have developed this concept together. It is based on the agreement to take responsibility for living and working at the university and for maintaining its resources.', 'Music', 'Neustadt 22, 32756 Detmold, Germany', 'info@hfm-detmold.de', '+49 5231 9755', '1', '+49 5231 9755', 'DE', 'http://www.hfm-detmold.de/', 'https://de-de.facebook.com/HfMDetmold', 'institutions/1619551296_hfm-detmold.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:21:36', '2021-04-28 01:21:36'),
(313, 'Hochschule für Musik Carl Maria von Weber', 'The Dresden University of Music sees itself as a place for cultivating music culture, where art, science and teaching intertwine in theory and practice. Tradition and renewal, continuity and experiment are in lively exchange. Freedom for experiments, new ways of working and artistic research are part of everyday university life.', 'Music', 'University of Music Carl Maria von Weber Dresden\r\nWettiner Platz 13\r\n01067 Dresden', 'rektorat@hfmdd.de', '+49 351 4923–600', '1', '+49 351 4923–600', 'DE', 'https://www.hfmdd.de/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hfmdd/', 'institutions/1619551426_hfmdd.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:23:46', '2021-04-28 01:23:46'),
(314, 'Robert Schumann Hochschule', 'The bachelor\'s degree in  Music and Media  combines a broad spectrum of content and enables media perspectives to be artistically and scientifically examined, questioned, reinvented and conveyed.', 'Music', 'Robert Schumann University of Applied Sciences Düsseldorf\r\nFischerstraße 110\r\n40476 Düsseldorf \r\nTelephone switchboard: +49 211 49 18 0\r\nFax: +49 211 4 91 16 18', 'patrick.arnold@rsh-duesseldorf.de', '+49 163 309 11 73', '1', '+49 163 309 11 73', 'DE', 'http://www.rsh-duesseldorf.de/', 'https://www.facebook.com/RSH.Duesseldorf', 'institutions/1619551572_rsh.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:26:12', '2021-04-28 01:26:12'),
(315, 'Frankfurt University of Music and Performing Arts', 'Bachelor of Music. Four years. Studies include performance (classical, jazz/pop, opera, early music), composition, musicology, instrumental pedagogy, music education (for teaching at all school levels), Protestant or Catholic church music.', 'Music', 'Frankfurt University of Music and Performing Arts\r\n\r\nEschersheimer Landstrasse 29–39\r\nD 60322 Frankfurt am Main', 'manfred.gerhardt@hfmdk-frankfurt.de', '+ 49.69.154.007-0', '1', '+ 49.69.154.007-0', 'DE', 'http://www.hfmdk-frankfurt.info/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hfmdkfrankfurt', 'institutions/1619552754_hfmdk.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:45:54', '2021-04-28 01:45:54'),
(316, 'Hochschule für Musik Freiburg', 'This university-level institution was founded in 1946. There are Institutes for New Music, Music Theatre, Historic Performance Practice and Music Medicine. Facilities include a well-equipped electronic music studio.', 'Music', 'Schwarzwaldstraße 141, 79102 Freiburg im Breisgau, Germany', 'info@mh-freiburg.de', '+49 761 319 15-42', '1', '+49 761 319 15-42', 'DE', 'https://www.mh-freiburg.de/start/', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Hochschule-f%C3%BCr-Musik-Freiburg/201955966516388', 'institutions/1619553251_mh-freiburg.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:54:11', '2021-04-28 01:54:11'),
(317, 'Martin Luther University of Halle-Wittenberg', 'Bachelor of Arts. Music studies include performance, musicology, ethnomusicology, choral conducting, pedagogy, church music, music education. Preparation for teaching music in schools but needs to be followed by the two-year Master program to gain the qualification.', 'Music', 'Musicology: Universitätsring 4, 06108 Halle (Saale), Germany', 'dekan@philfak2.uni-halle.de', '+49 345 55 27232', '1', '+49 345 55 27232', 'DE', 'http://www.uni-halle.de/?lang=en', 'https://www.facebook.com/unihalle', 'institutions/1619553414_uni halle.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:56:54', '2021-04-28 01:56:54'),
(318, 'Hochschule für Musik und Theater Hamburg', 'Bachelor of Arts. Studies in pedagogy, music education, arts management. Bachelor of Music. Studies include performance (classical, jazz/pop, opera, music theatre, early music), composition, theory, musicology, choral and orchestral conducting, church music.', 'Music', 'Harvestehuder Weg 12, 20148 Hamburg, Germany', 'info@hfmt.hamburg.de', '+49 40 428 482-666', '1', '+49 40 428 482-666', 'DE', 'https://www.hfmt-hamburg.de/', '-', 'institutions/1619553576_hfmt-hamburg.JPG', '2021-04-28 01:59:36', '2021-04-28 01:59:36'),
(319, 'Hochschule für Musik, Theater und Medien Hannover', 'Band Conducting, Choral Conducting, Church Music/Religious Music, Early Music Performance, Ethnomusicology/World Music, Jazz/Popular Music Performance, Library Collections, Music Theatre Performance, Opera Performance, Orchestral Conducting, Repetiteur Training/Coaching, Sound Archives, Wellness for Musicians', 'Music', 'Neues Haus, Emmichplatz 1, 30175 Hannover, Germany', 'hmtm@hmtm-hannover.de', '+49 (0) 511 3100-200', '1', '+49 (0) 511 3100-200', 'DE', 'https://www.hmtm-hannover.de/de/start/', 'http://www.facebook.com/HMTMH', 'institutions/1619553830_hmtm.JPG', '2021-04-28 02:03:50', '2021-04-28 02:03:50'),
(320, 'Hochschule für Musik Karlsruhe', 'Bachelor of Arts. Studies include performance (classical, opera, early music), choral and orchestral conducting, composition, musicology, school music, church music, music journalism.', 'Music', 'Am Schloss Gottesaue 7, 76131 Karlsruhe, Germany', 'info@hfm-karlsruhe.de', '+49 721 66 29-266', '1', '+49 721 66 29-266', 'DE', 'http://www.hfm-karlsruhe.de/', '-', 'institutions/1619605452_hfm-karlsruhe.JPG', '2021-04-28 16:24:12', '2021-04-28 16:24:12'),
(321, 'University of Music and Theatre Leipzig', 'Bachelor of Music. Four years. Studies include performance (classical, jazz/pop, early music, opera, music theatre), choral and orchestral conducting, repetiteur training, composition, harmony and counterpoint, theory, musicology, church music, piano pedagogy, music education (preparation for teaching music in schools but needs to be followed by a two-year Master program in education to gain the qualification. .', 'Music', 'Grassistraße 8, 04107 Leipzig, Germany', 'studienangelegenheiten@hmt-leipzig.de', '+49 341 2144 503', '1', '+49 341 2144 503', 'DE', 'https://web.archive.org/web/20100119022822/http:/www.hmt-leipzig.de/index.php?english', 'https://web.archive.org/web/20100119022822/http:/www.hmt-leipzig.de/index.php?english#', 'institutions/1619605604_music and theatre leipzig.JPG', '2021-04-28 16:26:44', '2021-04-28 16:26:44'),
(322, 'Lübeck Academy of Music', 'This Academy of Music was founded in 1911 as a music conservatoire and gained its current name and status in 1973. It is the only music university-level institution in Schleswig-Holstein. The University houses the Brahms Institute with original manuscripts, letters, photographs and other memorabilia of Brahms and his circle.', 'Music', 'Große Petersgrube 21, 23552 Lübeck, Germany', 'info@mh-luebeck.de', '+49 451 1505 300', '1', '+49 451 1505 300', 'DE', 'https://www.mh-luebeck.de/start/', 'https://www.mh-luebeck.de/facebook/', 'institutions/1619605713_mh-luebeck.JPG', '2021-04-28 16:28:33', '2021-04-28 16:28:33'),
(323, 'Hochschule für Musik Mainz', 'The University was founded in 1477, and as such, is one of the oldest universities in Germany. There is a small collection of Thai instruments and a number of recordings of tribal music of the region. There is co-operation with the Peter Cornelius Conservatorium in Mainz and a number of other institutions.', 'Music', 'Jacob-Welder-Weg 28, 55128 Mainz, Germany', 'veranstaltungen-musik@uni-mainz.de', '+49 6131 393 0140', '1', '+49 6131 393 0140', 'DE', 'http://www.musik.uni-mainz.de/', 'http://www.facebook.com/hfm.mainz', 'institutions/1619605816_musik.uni-mainz.JPG', '2021-04-28 16:30:16', '2021-04-28 16:30:16'),
(324, 'Hochschule für Musik und Darstellende Kunst Mannheim', 'The Hochschule can trace its history back to 1909. It was granted its current name and status in 1931. There is a preliminary program for those wishing to enter the professional program. The Hochschule has a collaboration with the Hochschule für Musik und Darstellende Kunst Mannheim in a program linking church music with school music teaching. A further collaboration with the Popakademie Baden-Württemberg leads to the degree of Master Popularkirchenmusik.', 'Music', 'Hildastraße 8, 69115 Heidelberg, Germany', 'sekretariat@hfk-heidelberg.de', '+49 62 212 1876', '1', '+49 62 212 1876', 'DE', 'https://www.muho-mannheim.de/', 'https://de-de.facebook.com/pages/Staatliche-Hochschule-f%C3%BCr-Musik-und-Darstellende-Kunst-Mannheim/458310530862629', 'institutions/1619605985_muho.JPG', '2021-04-28 16:33:05', '2021-04-28 16:33:05'),
(325, 'Hochschule für Musik und Theater München', 'This State Academy, founded in 1993, operates from the Prinzregenten Theatre in München which is also the home of the Bavarian State Opera.', 'Music', 'Prinzregentenplatz 12, 81675 München, Germany', 'musiktheater@theaterakademie.de', '+49 89 2185 2813', '1', '+49 89 2185 2813', 'DE', 'https://website.musikhochschule-muenchen.de/de/', '-', 'institutions/1619610037_Hochschule fur Musik.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:40:37', '2021-04-28 17:40:37'),
(326, 'Bayerische Theaterakademie August Everding', 'This State Academy, founded in 1993, operates from the Prinzregenten Theatre in München which is also the home of the Bavarian State Opera. It is the largest institution for stage professions in Germany, offering programs for singers, actors, directors, stage designers, costumiers and make-up artists.', 'Music', 'Prinzregentenplatz 12, 81675 München, Germany', 'musiktheater@theaterakademie.de', '+49 (0) 89 2185 02', '1', '+49 (0) 89 2185 02', 'DE', 'https://www.theaterakademie.de/studium.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.theaterakademie.de/studium.html', 'institutions/1619610195_theatreakademie.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:43:15', '2021-04-28 17:43:15'),
(327, 'University of Münster', 'The Hochschule, founded in 1946, has branches in Dortmund and Münster. It was formerly known as the Northwest German Music Academy. The University comprises ten music-specific buildings in and around the Palais Gardens.', 'Music', 'Neustadt 22, 32756 Detmold, Germany', 'info@hfm-detmold.de', '+49 251 83-0', '1', '+49 251 83-0', 'DE', 'https://www.uni-muenster.de/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/wwumuenster', 'institutions/1619610335_uni-muenster.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:45:35', '2021-04-28 17:45:35'),
(328, 'University of Osnabrück', 'The Conservatorium was founded in 1931. It offers courses for teachers of piano accordion and harmonica. There is an accordion orchestra. The Conservatorium organises workshops and concerts as well as classes in kindergartens and for seniors groups. A co-operative link with the University of Osnabrück enables graduates of the Hohner Conservatorium to continue for two further years to complete a bachelor\'s degree in jazz or classic accordion.', 'Music', 'Hohnerstraße 4/1, 78647 Trossingen, Germany', 'info@hohner-konservatorium.de', '+49 541 969 0', '1', '+49 541 969 0', 'DE', 'https://www.uni-osnabrueck.de/en/home.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/uniosnabrueck', 'institutions/1619610455_osnabrueck.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:47:35', '2021-04-28 17:47:35'),
(329, 'Rostock University of Music and Theatre', 'This University was originally founded in 1946 and was established under its present title in 1994. It currently enrols around 500 students in its departments of music and drama. The music department consists of an Institut für Musik and an Institut für Musikwissenschaft und Musikpädagogik.', 'Music', 'Beim St.-Katharinenstift 8, 18055 Rostock, Germany', 'jeanett.heine@hmt-rostock.de', '+49 381 5108-0', '1', '+49 381 5108-0', 'DE', 'https://www.hmt-rostock.de/?L=1', '-', 'institutions/1619610582_hmt.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:49:42', '2021-04-28 17:49:42'),
(330, 'Hochschule für Musik Saar', 'The University was founded in 1947 and has co-operation agreements with the conservatories of Luxembourg and Lorraine (France). The three institutions have formed the ‘Saar-Lor-Lux Orchester’ to present an annual concert tour.', 'Music', 'Saar University of Music\r\nBismarckstrasse 1\r\n66111 Saarbrücken', 'info@hfm.saarland.de', '0681 967310', '1', '0681 967310', 'DE', 'http://www.hfm.saarland.de/', '-', 'institutions/1619610737_hfm saarland.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:52:17', '2021-04-28 17:52:17'),
(331, 'State University of Music and Performing Arts Stuttgart', 'This State University of Music and Performing Arts was founded in 1857. The opera school operates in conjunction with the Staatsoper Stuttgart. There are eleven organs. An attached music school offers music tuition to young children.', 'Music', 'Urbanstraße 25, 70182 Stuttgart, Germany', 'info@mh-stuttgart.de', '+49 711 212 4632', '1', '+49 711 212 4632', 'DE', 'https://www.hmdk-stuttgart.de/home/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Musikhochschule-Stuttgart/155450051144516?ref=sgm', 'institutions/1619610881_hmdk-stuttgart.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:54:41', '2021-04-28 17:54:41'),
(332, 'Hochschule für Musik Trossingen', 'This university-level Hochschule was founded in 1947. Particular emphasis is placed upon early music and music and movement. It includes an Early Music Institute (Institut für Alte Musik), the largest in Germany.', 'Music', 'Schultheiß-Koch-Platz 3, 78647 Trossingen, Germany', 'rektorat@mh-trossingen.de', '07425 / 9491-0', '1', '07425 / 9491-0', 'DE', 'http://www.mh-trossingen.de/home.html', 'https://de-de.facebook.com/Musikhochschule.Trossingen/', 'institutions/1619611022_mh trossingen.JPG', '2021-04-28 17:57:02', '2021-04-28 17:57:02'),
(333, 'Hochschule für Musik Franz Liszt, Weimar', 'The University of Music Franz Liszt Weimar sees itself as an international tertiary education and research institution. Deeply rooted in the tradition of European music, it is at home in the highly symbolic cultural city of Weimar.', 'Music', 'Platz der Demokratie 2/3 \r\n99423 Weimar\r\nGermany', 'signe.pribbernow@hfm-weimar.de', '+49 3643 | 555 0', '1', '+49 3643 | 555 0', 'DE', 'http://www.hfm-weimar.de/index.php?id=580&L=1', 'http://facebook.com/hfmweimar', 'institutions/1619611231_hfm-weimar.JPG', '2021-04-28 18:00:31', '2021-04-28 18:00:31'),
(334, 'Hochschule für Musik Würzburg', 'This music university can trace its history back to 1797. It was granted its current name and status in 1973. Facilities include a well-equipped digital production studio and computer music studio.', 'Music', 'Hofstallstraße 6-8, 97070 Würzburg, Germany', 'hochschule@hfm-wuerzburg.de', '+49 (0)931-32187-0', '1', '+49 (0)931-32187-0', 'DE', 'http://www.hfm-wuerzburg.de/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hfm.wuerzburg', 'institutions/1619611565_hfm-wuerzburg.JPG', '2021-04-28 18:06:05', '2021-04-28 18:06:05'),
(335, 'Hoch Conservatory', 'Dr. Hoch\'s Conservatory - Music Academy Frankfurt am Main is a state-recognized training institute with a long tradition. 1878 as a foundation of the Frankfurt citizen Dr. Founded by Joseph Hoch, it now unites under one roof the musical education from early musical development to the academic degree \"Bachelor of Music\".', 'Music', 'Sonnemannstrasse 16 60314 Frankfurt', 'info@dr-hochs.de', '0 69 - 212 - 44822', '1', '0 69 - 212 - 44822', 'DE', 'https://www.dr-hochs.de/de', 'https://www.facebook.com/drhochsKonservatorium/', 'institutions/1619611831_dr-hochs.JPG', '2021-04-28 18:10:31', '2021-04-28 18:10:31'),
(336, 'Hamburger Konservatorium', 'The Conservatorium was founded in 1908. It consists of three divisions, the professional academy, the music school (with programs in classical and jazz performance, ensembles, children’s choir, programs for the very young).', 'Music', 'Sülldorfer Landstraße 196, 22589 Hamburg, Germany', 'akademie@hamburger-konservatorium.de', '(040) 870877-0', '1', '(040) 870877-0', 'DE', 'http://www.miz.org/index.php?seite=details&id=1399&suche=16', '-', 'institutions/1619612034_miz.JPG', '2021-04-28 18:13:54', '2021-04-28 18:13:54'),
(337, 'Peter Cornelius Conservatory', 'The founding idea of ​​the Peter Cornelius Conservatory - to combine professional and lay training in music - characterizes the work of the study department as a living tradition. Here, in an institute with a unique profile in Germany, students can learn under the best conditions what is needed in professional practice.', 'Music', 'Peter-Cornelius-Conservatory\r\nBinger Str. 18\r\n55122 Mainz', 'pck@stadt.mainz.de', '06131 - 2500812', '1', '06131 - 2500812', 'DE', 'https://pck-mainz.de/', '-', 'institutions/1619612203_pck.JPG', '2021-04-28 18:16:43', '2021-04-28 18:16:43'),
(338, 'Hochschule für Musik Nürnberg', 'In 1999 the Leopold Mozart Konservatorium in Augsburg and the Meistersinger Konservatorium in Nürnberg were officially joined to become the Hochschule für Musik Nürnberg-Augsburg – the youngest Hochschule in Germany.', 'Music', 'Nürnberg: Veilhofstraße 34-40, 90489 Nürnberg, Germany', 'info@hfm-nuernberg.de', '+49 911 231 7697', '1', '+49 911 231 7697', 'DE', 'https://www.facebook.com/Hochschule-f%C3%BCr-Musik-N%C3%BCrnberg-165110576869963', 'http://www.hfm-nuernberg.de/home/', 'institutions/1619612412_hfm-nuernberg.JPG', '2021-04-28 18:20:12', '2021-04-28 18:20:12'),
(339, 'Tbilisi State Conservatoire', 'The Conservatory was founded in 1917. Courses are taught in Georgian. Facilities include two performance halls, one also being used for opera performances, a three-manual pipe organ and a well-appointed recording studio.', 'Music', 'Ul Griboedova 0108, 8/10, Tbilisi, Georgia', 'info@conservatoire.edu.ge', '+995 32 298 7187', '1', '+995 32 298 7187', 'GE', 'http://www.conservatoire.edu.ge/', '-', 'institutions/1619644854_conservatoire.edu.ge.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:20:54', '2021-04-29 03:20:54'),
(340, 'Ilia State University Music Centre', 'School of Arts and Sciences is one of the largest and most reputable faculties of ISU carrying out study programs on 4 different levels (Vocational, Bachelor\'s, Master\'s And Doctoral Studies).', 'Music', 'Kakutsa Cholokashvili Ave 3/5\r\nTbilisi 0162, Georgia', 'info@iliauni.edu.ge', '(+995 32) 222 00 09', '1', '(+995 32) 222 00 09', 'GE', 'http://iliauni.edu.ge/en/iliauni/AcademicDepartments/mecnierebata-da-xelovnebis-fakulteti-269', 'https://www.facebook.com/Iliauni/', 'institutions/1619645010_iliauni.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:23:30', '2021-04-29 03:23:30'),
(341, 'Aristotle University of Thessaloniki Department of Music', 'The Aristotle University of Thessaloniki was established in 1925. The School of Music Studies was established in 1985, being the first music studies department in a university in Greece. The emphasis is on both artistic creation and research.', 'Music', 'University campus, Aristotle University of Thessaloniki, GR-54124 Thessaloniki, Greece', 'info@mus.auth.gr', '+30 2310 991801', '1', '+30 2310 991 815', 'GR', 'http://www.auth.gr/en/mus', 'http://www.facebook.com/Aristoteleio', 'institutions/1619645201_auth.gr.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:26:41', '2021-04-29 03:26:41'),
(342, 'Ionian University', 'The university was founded in 1984 and recently has expanded its operations to several islands in the Ionian Islands Region. Its Department of Music Studies began operations in 1992. In 2013 a new Faculty of Music & Audiovisual Arts was established.', 'Music', 'Old Fortress, GR-49100 Corfu, Greece', 'music@ionio.gr', '+30 26610 26 024', '1', '+30 26610 26 024', 'GR', 'https://ionio.gr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ionio.gr', 'institutions/1619645360_ionio.gr.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:29:20', '2021-04-29 03:29:20'),
(343, 'National and Kapodistrian University of Athens', 'The University was founded in 1837, the first university in the newly-established Greek State. The Department of Music Studies is divided into three sectors: • Historical and Systematic Musicology. • Ethnomusicology and Cultural Anthropology. • Sound technology, Music Pedagogy and Byzantine Musicology.', 'Music', 'School of Philosophy, Ilissia campus, Panepistimioupoli, GR-15784 Athens, Greece', 'music@cc.uoa.gr', '+30 210 727 7302', '1', '+30 210 727 7302', 'GR', 'https://en.uoa.gr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/uoa.official', 'institutions/1619645483_kapodistrian.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:31:23', '2021-04-29 03:31:23'),
(344, 'University of Macedonia', 'The University was established in 1990, though it can trace its history back to 1948. The Department of Music Science and Art accepted its first students in 1998. It is organised in a similar way to that of European Music Academies in order to provide performance as well as theoretical studies.', 'Music', 'Egnatia 156. GR-54636 Thessaloniki, Greece', 'veconom@uom.gr', '2310 891.101', '1', '2310 891.101', 'GR', 'http://www.uom.gr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/universityofmacedonia', 'institutions/1619645610_macedonia.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:33:30', '2021-04-29 03:33:30'),
(345, 'Athens Conservatoire', 'This Conservatory, founded in 1871 by the Athens Music and Drama Society, is the oldest conservatoire in modern Greece. It receives some government financial support and has been in existence for over 120 years, producing such artists as Dimitri Mitropoulos, Maria Callas, Gina Bachauer, Nana Mouskouri and Nikos Skalkotas.', 'Music', 'Rigillis & Vas. Georgiou BD 17-19\r\nAthena\r\n106 75 GREECE', 'info@odeionathinon.gr', '210 72 40 673', '1', '210 72 40 673', 'GR', 'https://www.athensconservatoire.gr/', 'https://www.facebook.com/AthensConservatoire', 'institutions/1619645742_athens cons.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:35:42', '2021-04-29 03:35:42'),
(346, 'Franz Liszt Academy of Music', 'Established by Franz Liszt in 1875 and known in English as the Franz Liszt Academy of Music, this institution has now been officially recognised as a University. It has several buildings in Budapest, including among others, the central building, the György Ligeti building, the Ferenc Liszt Memorial and Research Centre.', 'Music', 'Liszt Ferenc tér 8, PO Box 206, 1061 Budapest, Hungary', 'info@lisztacademy.hu', '+36 1 321-0690', '1', '+36 1 321-0690', 'HU', 'https://lfze.hu/en/the-university', 'https://www.facebook.com/lisztferenczenemuveszetiegyetem/', 'institutions/1619646380_lfze.hu.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:46:20', '2021-04-29 03:46:20'),
(347, 'Hong Kong Academy for Performing Arts', 'The Academy was founded in 1984. There are schools of dance, drama, music, theatre and entertainment arts, film and television and Chinese traditional theatre. Facilities include a fine concert hall, an opera theatre and a well-equipped library which houses the Ernest Read collection of orchestral scores and the Black Watch Concert Band collection.', 'Music', '1 Gloucester Road, Wanchai, Hong Kong', 'aso@mail.hkapa.edu', '(852) 2584 8500', '1', '(852) 2584 8500', 'HK', 'https://www.hkapa.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/HKAPA.edu', 'institutions/1619646547_kkapa.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:49:07', '2021-04-29 03:49:07'),
(348, 'Iceland Academy of the Arts', 'This self-governing university awards the only university-level degrees in the arts in Iceland. It opened in 1999 and consists of departments of fine arts, theatre, music, dance, art education, and design and architecture.', 'Music', 'Þverholt ll, 5th floor, 13, 105 Reykjavík, Iceland', 'lhi@lhi.is', '+354 545 2200', '1', '+354 545 2200', 'IS', 'https://www.lhi.is/', 'https://www.facebook.com/lhi.is', 'institutions/1619646675_lhi.is.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:51:15', '2021-04-29 03:51:15'),
(349, 'Dublin Institute of Technology', 'Deeply embedded in our region, TU Dublin has campuses in Dublin City Centre, in Blanchardstown and in Tallaght, and, through our major infrastructural development plan, we are currently investing over €500 million in new, state-of-the-art, technology-enabled facilities to enhance our students\' experience.', 'Music', 'Park House, 191 N Circular Rd, Grangegorman, Dublin, D07 EWV4, Ireland', 'courses@tudublin.ie', '+353 1 885 1000', '1', '+353 1 885 1000', 'IE', 'https://www.dit.ie/', 'https://www.facebook.com/TechnologicalUniversityDublin.TUDublin/', 'institutions/1619646888_dit.ie.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:54:48', '2021-04-29 03:54:48'),
(350, 'Royal Irish Academy of Music', 'The Royal Irish Academy of Music, founded in 1848, is a College of Dublin City University which is the umbrella organisation that also includes the former independent institutions of the Mater Dei Institute of Education and St Patrick’s College.', 'Music', '36-38 Westland Row, Dublin 2, D02 WY89, Ireland', 'info@riam.ie', '+353 1 662 2798', '1', '+353 1 662 2798', 'IE', 'https://www.riam.ie/', 'https://www.facebook.com/riamdublin/', 'institutions/1619647114_RIAM.JPG', '2021-04-29 03:58:34', '2021-04-29 03:58:34'),
(351, 'Cork Institute of Technology', 'The Cork School of Music was founded in 1878 and has been a constituent school of Cork’s Institute of Technology (CIT) since 1993. A new purpose-built home for the Cork School of Music opened in September 2007, and houses the 300-seat Curtis Auditorium.', 'Music', 'Union Quay, Ballintemple, Cork, Ireland', 'noranne.elliott@cit.ie', '021 432 6100', '1', '021 432 6100', 'IE', 'http://www.cit.ie/', 'http://www.facebook.com/myMTU', 'institutions/1619647222_cit.ie.JPG', '2021-04-29 04:00:22', '2021-04-29 04:00:22'),
(352, 'Conservatorio Statale di Musica \"Giuseppe Verdi\"', 'The Conservatorio was founded in 1982 as a branch of the Milan Conservatorio and became an independent institution in 1996. There is a preparatory program for students wishing to enter the professional program.', 'Music', 'Via Luigi Cadorna 4, 22100 Como, Italy', 'conservatoriocomo@pec.como.it', '+39 011.81.78.458', '1', '+39 011.81.78.458', 'IT', 'https://www.conservatoriotorino.gov.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConservatorioTo/', 'institutions/1619647436_conservatoriotorino.JPG', '2021-04-29 04:03:56', '2021-04-29 04:03:56'),
(353, 'Istituto superiore di studi musicali Franco Vittadini', 'The Franco Vittadini Conservatory of Music is a Higher Institute of Musical Studies pursuant to art. 2, paragraph 7, letter c) of the law 21/12/1999, n. 508.', 'Music', 'Via A. Volta, 31 – 27100 Pavia', 'segreteria.vittadini@conspv.it', '+39 0382 304764', '1', '+39 0382 304764', 'IT', 'https://conspv.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/issmfrancovittadini/', 'institutions/1619647658_conspv.JPG', '2021-04-29 04:07:38', '2021-04-29 04:07:38'),
(354, 'Conservatorio Umberto Giordano', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1914. It gained its current name and status in 1977 and has a campus in Rodi Garnico. There is a preparatory program for students wishing to enter the professional program.', 'Music', 'Piazza Vincenzo Nigri 13, IT-71100 Foggia, Italy', 'info@conservatoriofoggia.it', '(+39) 0884 966580', '1', '+39 881 774 687', 'IT', 'https://www.conservatoriofoggia.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatorioUG/', 'institutions/1619647776_conservatoriofoggia.JPG', '2021-04-29 04:09:36', '2021-04-29 04:09:36'),
(355, 'Music conservatories of Naples', 'The history of the San Pietro a Majella Conservatory of music is the history of different and distinct institutions that came together - albeit in different ways and at different times - to form the current body, and it is a story marked by very specific identities, by clear vocations, through which runs, constantly, the fil rouge of training in the musical field.', 'Music', 'Via San Pietro a Majella, 35 - 80138 (Napoli)', 'ufficioprotocollo@legalmail.it', '(+39) 081.544.92.55', '1', '(+39) 081.544.92.55', 'IT', 'http://www.sanpietroamajella.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriodimusicasanpietroamajelladinapoli/', 'institutions/1619690407_sanpietromejella.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:00:07', '2021-04-29 16:00:07'),
(356, 'Accademia Nazionale di Santa Cecilia', 'The Academy was founded in 1585, thus being one of the oldest music establishments in the world. Its headquarters at the Auditorium Parco della Musica houses three concert halls. The Academy incorporates the International Centre for the study of Italian Music (Centro Internazionale di Studi per la Divulgazione della Musica Italiana) and also houses a drama school and centre for experimental cinema.', 'Music', 'Auditorium Parco della Musica, Largo Luciano Berio 3, 00196 Roma, Italy', 'info@santacecilia.it', '+39 6 8024 2300', '1', '+39 6 8024 2300', 'IT', 'http://www.santacecilia.it/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/accademiadisantacecilia/', 'institutions/1619690503_santacecilia.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:01:43', '2021-04-29 16:01:43'),
(357, 'Conservatorio Giovanni Battista Martini', 'In 1802 the Municipality of Bologna made the project of a city Music High School, to be placed in the convent of S. Giacomo next to the church of the same name: the new school was to teach composition, piano, voice, violin and viola, cello and double bass, oboe and horn English, through six teachers including the composer Stanislao Mattei.', 'Music', 'Piazza Rossini, 2 - 40126 - Bologna', 'conservatoriobologna@pec.it', '051/22.14.83', '1', '051/22.14.83', 'IT', 'https://www.consmilano.it//', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Conservatorio-di-Musica-Giovan-Battista-Martini-Bologna/588536971293128?fref=ts', 'institutions/1619690920_consbo.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:08:40', '2021-04-29 16:08:40'),
(358, 'Conservatorio Bruno Maderna', 'The Conservatorio offers a preparatory program for students wishing to enter the professional program. It also offers music tuition to children and interested members of the local community. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Corso Ubaldo Comandini 1, 47521 Cesena, Italy', 'info@conservatoriomaderna-cesena.it', '054728679', '1', '054728679', 'IT', 'https://www.conservatoriomaderna-cesena.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriob.maderna.cesena/', 'institutions/1619691052_cesana.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:10:52', '2021-04-29 16:10:52'),
(359, 'Conservatorio Luigi Cherubini', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1849. It offers programs in music, literature and arts. The MART Lab is a collaboration between the Conservatorio, the National Research Council and other similar bodies, aiming to recover and restore audio magnetic media and sound recordings.', 'Music', 'Piazza della Belle Arti 2, 50121 Firenze, Italy', 'protocol.consfi@pec.it', '+39 055 298 9311', '1', '. +39 055 298 9311', 'IT', 'https://www.consfi.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConservatorioLuigiCherubiniFirenze/', 'institutions/1619691170_consfi.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:12:50', '2021-04-29 16:12:50'),
(360, 'Conservatorio Benedetto Marcello', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1876. It gained its current name and status in 1940. In addition to the professional programs the Conservatorio offers music tuition to young people and interested members of the local community. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Conservatory of Music \"Benedetto Marcello\"\r\nSestiere di San Marco, 2810 - 30124, Venice', 'conservatorio.venezia@conservatoriovenezia.net', '+39 041 522 5604', '1', '+39 041 522 5604', 'IT', 'http://www.conservatoriovenezia.net/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriobenedettomarcello/', 'institutions/1619691320_venezia.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:15:20', '2021-04-29 16:15:20'),
(361, 'Conservatorio Giuseppe Tartini', 'This Conservatorio was established in the 1930s and was granted its current name and status in 1958. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Via Carlo Ghega 12, 34132 Trieste, Italy', 'comunicazione@conts.it', '+39 040 6724911', '1', '+39 040 6724911', 'IT', 'https://conts.it/', '-', 'institutions/1619691453_conts.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:17:33', '2021-04-29 16:17:33'),
(362, 'Conservatorio Cesare Pollini', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1577. There is a junior department offering string music tuition (\'Violinolandia\') to children from the age of five years. There is a branch office in Via Bertacchi 15, Padua. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Via Eremitani 18, 35121 Padova, Italy', 'conservatorio.pd@legalmail.it', '+39 0498750648', '1', '+39 0498750648', 'IT', 'https://www.conservatoriopollini.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Conservatorio.Pollini.Padova', 'institutions/1619691584_pollini.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:19:44', '2021-04-29 16:19:44'),
(363, 'Conservatorio Niccolò Paganini', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1829. There are laboratories for early music, sound recording and digital sound processing. Facilities include a state-of-the-art electronic studio associated with the School of Music and New Technology.', 'Music', 'Via Albaro 38, 16145 Genoa, Ital', 'info@conservatoriopaganini.org', '010.3620747 - 010.318683', '1', '010.3620747 - 010.318683', 'IT', 'https://www.conspaganini.it/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conspaganini', 'institutions/1619691718_paganin.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:21:58', '2021-04-29 16:21:58'),
(364, 'Conservatorio Statale di Musica \"Gioachino Rossini\"', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1858. It gained its current name and status in 1999. It is housed in the palazzo, the property of the \"Gioachino Rossini Foundation\" (with offices in the building), that publishes the critical editions of the works of the composer. Facilities include an electronic laboratory for experimental music and the Rossini Conservatory of Early Music \'Croma\'.', 'Music', 'Piazza Olivieri 5, 61121 Pesaro, Italy', 'segreteria@conservatoriorossini.it', '+39 0721 33671', '1', '+39 0721 33671', 'IT', 'http://www.conservatoriorossini.it/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConservatorioPS', 'institutions/1619691848_rossini.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:24:08', '2021-04-29 16:24:08'),
(365, 'Conservatorio Statale \"Domenico Cimarosa\"', 'The Conservatorio was founded in 1972. There is a preparatory program for students wishing to enter the professional program. The Conservatorio offers music tuition to children and interested members of the local community.', 'Music', 'Via Circumvallazione 156, 83100 Avellino, Italy', 'conservatoriocimarosa@pec.it', '+39 825 780 074', '1', '+39 825 780 074', 'IT', 'http://www.conservatoriocimarosa.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriodomenicocimarosa/', 'institutions/1619692021_marosa.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:27:01', '2021-04-29 16:27:01'),
(366, 'Kunitachi College of Music', 'A municipal co-educational university. Founded in 1880, it is a conservatory type institution which concentrates on Western music, though a Research Centre for Traditional Japanese Music was opened in 2000.', 'Music', '13-6 Kutsukake-cho, Oe, Nishikyo-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto 610-1197, Japan', 'www-admin@kcua.ac.jp', '+81 75 332 0709', '1', '+81 75 332 0709', 'IT', 'http://www.kcua.ac.jp/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/kcua.ac.jp', 'institutions/1619692331_kcua.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:32:11', '2021-04-29 16:32:11'),
(367, '8 Musashino Academia Musicae', 'A private co-educational music academy founded in 1929 and regarded as equivalent to a university. There are campuses in Tokyo (the Ekoda campus) for third and fourth year and graduate students, and in Iruma (in Saitama prefecture on the outskirts of Tokyo, opened in 1971) for first and second year students. In 1993 the academy opened its third campus, Parnassos (in Tama), where post-graduate instruction is given to music specialists.', 'Music', 'Ekoda campus: 1-13-1 Hazawa, Nerima-ku, Tokyo 176-8521, Japan', 'koho@musashino-music.ac.jp', '+81 3 3991 7599', '1', '+81 3 3991 7599', 'JP', 'http://www.musashino-music.ac.jp/', 'https://youtu.be/ypsgwv2Zc9Q', 'institutions/1619692436_musashino.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:33:56', '2021-04-29 16:33:56'),
(368, 'Nagoya College of Music', 'A private Buddhist co-educational music college belonging to the Doho group of educational institutions, established in its current form in 1976, and is the oldest music college in this area of Japan.', 'Music', '7 Chome-1 Inabajicho, Nakamura-ku, Nagoya-shi, Aichi 453-8540, Japan', 'stdnt_on@meion.ac.jp', '+81 52 413 2300', '1', '+81 52 413 2300', 'JP', 'https://www.meion.ac.jp/', 'https://twitter.com/meion_nyushi', 'institutions/1619692562_meion.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:36:02', '2021-04-29 16:36:02'),
(369, 'Osaka College of Music', 'A private co-educational music college founded in 1915 and was chartered as a university in 1958. The college houses a pipe organ, an opera house with resident professional chorus and orchestra, a state-of-the-art electronic music laboratory, a museum holding over 3,500 musical instruments from around the world and the largest music library in western Japan with over 188,000 reference materials and some 43,700 music scores.', 'Music', '1 Chome-1-8 Shonai-saiwai-machi, Toyonaka-shi, Ōsaka 561-8555, Japan', 'info-nyushi@daion.ac.jp', '0120-414-015', '1', '0120-414-015', 'JP', 'https://www.daion.ac.jp/', 'https://www.facebook.com/osaka.college.of.music', 'institutions/1619692703_osaka.JPG', '2021-04-29 16:38:23', '2021-04-29 16:38:23'),
(370, 'Toho Gakuen School of Music', 'A private co-educational music college founded in 1961 though it can trace its history back to 1948. It is located about five minutes’ walk from Sengawa station on the Keio Line, and about half an hour by train from Shinjuku. The College is renowned for the quality of its training in performance, particularly on piano, violin and violoncello. It concentrates exclusively on training in Western music.', 'Music', '1-41-1 Wakaba-cho, Chofu-shi, Tokyo 182-8510, Japan', 'exam@tohomusic.ac.jp', '03-3307-4101', '1', '03-3307-4101', 'JP', 'https://www.tohomusic.ac.jp/', 'https://twitter.com/tohomusic_pub', 'institutions/1619787973_tohomusic.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:06:13', '2021-04-30 19:06:13'),
(371, 'Tokyo College of Music', 'Tokyo College of Music celebrated the 100th anniversary of its founding in 2007. The oldest private music institute in Japan, TCM has been contributing significantly to the development of Western classical music at home. It created the very first symphonic orchestra in Japan which performed on Pacific Ocean steamers from 1912 to 1929.', 'Music', '1-9-1 Kami-Meguro Meguro-ku, Tokyo 153-8622, Japan', 'nyushika@tokyo-ondai.ac.jp', '+81-3-6455-2700', '1', '+81-3-6455-2700', 'JP', 'http://www.tokyo-ondai.ac.jp/en/', '-', 'institutions/1619788177_tokya ondai.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:09:37', '2021-04-30 19:09:37'),
(372, 'Tokyo University of the Arts', 'Tokyo University of the Arts was founded in May 1949 under the National School Establishment Law (Act No. 150 of 1949) through a merger of Tokyo Fine Arts School (currently the Faculty of Fine Arts) and Tokyo Music School (currently the Faculty of Music). At the time of its establishment, the university comprised ten departments in two faculties, the Faculty of Fine Arts (Departments of Painting, Sculpture, Crafts, Architecture, and Aesthetics and Art History), the Faculty of Music .', 'Music', '12-8 Ueno Park, Taito-ku, Tokyo 110-8714, Japan', 'ryugaku@ml.geidai.ac.jp', '+81 (0)50-5525-2067', '1', '+81 (0)50-5525-2067', 'JP', 'http://www.geidai.ac.jp/english/', '-', 'institutions/1619788460_geidai.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:14:20', '2021-04-30 19:14:20'),
(373, 'The Lebanese National Higher Conservatory of Music', 'The Lebanese National Conservatory was founded in the 1920s. Wadih Sabra (the composer of the Lebanese National Anthem) was the founder of the Music School which later became the Conservatory.', 'Music', '165488, Achrafieh, Beirut, Lebanon.', 'info@conservatory.gov.lb', '01-489530/1/2/3.', '1', '01-489530/1/2/3.', 'LB', 'http://www.conservatory.gov.lb/', '-', 'institutions/1619788636_conservatory gov lb.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:17:16', '2021-04-30 19:17:16'),
(374, 'Lithuanian Academy of Music and Theatre', 'The Lithuanian Academy of Music and Theatre was founded in 1918 as the Kaunas Music School. In 1949 it was merged with the Vilnius Conservatoire and became the Lithuanian State Conservatoire. In 2004 it gained its current name and status and was further enlarged in 2018 with the integration of the Academy of Arts from Klaipeda University.', 'Music', 'Building 2, Vilniaus 6-2, 01101 Vilnius, Lithuania', 'rektoratas@lmta.lt', '(8 5) 261 2691', '1', '(8 5) 261 2691', 'LT', 'https://www.usek.edu.lb/en/home', 'https://lt-lt.facebook.com/lmta.lt', 'institutions/1619788867_usek.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:21:07', '2021-04-30 19:21:07'),
(375, 'Conservatoire de Luxembourg', 'The Conservatoire can trace its history back to 1906. There are schools of dance, drama and music. The School offers courses in all aspects of music. It specialises in opera and lied, percussion and jazz.', 'Music', 'Rue Charles Martel 33, 2134 Luxembourg', 'conservatoire@vdl.lu', '352 4796-5555', '1', '352 4796-5555', 'LU', 'http://www.conservatoire.lu/', '-', 'institutions/1619789019_conservatorire lu.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:23:39', '2021-04-30 19:23:39'),
(376, 'Malaysian Institute of Art', 'The Department of Music provides an opportunity for music enthusiasts, who meet the minimum academic qualification to study music. The institute\'s 3-year fulltime course encompasses both Western classical & Eastern aspects of music. Students may choose either Western or Chinese instruments for their principal and second studies.', 'Music', '294-299, Jalan Bandar 11,\r\nTaman Melawati, 53100,\r\nKuala Lumpur, Malaysia.', 'registry@mia.edu.my', '+603-4108 8100', '1', '+603-4108 8100', 'MY', 'https://web.archive.org/web/20091128180219/http:/www.mia.edu.my/html/music.html', 'https://web.archive.org/web/20091128180219/http:/www.mia.edu.my/html/music.html#', 'institutions/1619789209_mia.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:26:49', '2021-04-30 19:26:49'),
(377, 'Institute of Music, UCSI University', 'Built on the principles of audacity, perseverance, integrity and excellence, UCSI University is a leading institution of higher learning with campuses in Kuala Lumpur, Terengganu and Sarawak, Malaysia. Our faculties, equipped with state-of-the-art facilities to meet student needs offer a wide spectrum of academic programmes, ranging from Medicine, Pharmacy, Nursing, Engineering and Architecture to Music, Multimedia, Education, Liberal Arts and Hospitality.', 'Music', 'UCSI Heights, 1, Jalan Puncak Menara Gading, Taman Connaught, 56000 Cheras, Wilayah Persekutuan Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia', 'thwa@ucsiuniversity.edu.my', '+603-9101 8882', '1', '+603-9101 8882', 'MY', 'https://www.ucsiuniversity.edu.my/contact', 'https://www.facebook.com/ucsi.university', 'institutions/1619789404_uccis.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:30:04', '2021-04-30 19:30:04'),
(378, 'International College of Music', 'International College of Music (ICOM) is Asia\'s Leading College of Contemporary Music. With fully equipped performance halls, recording studios and surround sound facilities, you will hone your talent studying with experienced faculty and industry leaders. Your music starts here. Explore!', 'Music', 'International College Of Music [DK 145(W)]\r\nManaged by KRIS Education Services Sdn Bhd (354928-X)\r\nWisma ICOM, Lot 126, Section 85A, Lorong Setapak,\r\n53000 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia', 'admissions@icom.edu.my', '603 4023 6000', '1', '603 4023 6000', 'MY', 'http://icom.edu.my/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ICOMfb/', 'institutions/1619789499_icom.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:31:39', '2021-04-30 19:31:39'),
(379, 'University of Malta', 'The University can trace its history back to 1591. The Mediterranean Institute organises the music program within the Faculty of Arts. Its Music Studies division holds an archive of folk and traditional music of the region and offers courses in ethnomusicology of the region. There is some collaboration in this area with the Università degli Studi de Bologna. Languages of instruction are Maltese and English.', 'Music', 'University of Malta Msida Campus (main campus)\r\nMsida MSD 2080\r\nMalta', 'info@um.edu.mt', '+356 2340 2340', '1', '+356 2340 2340', 'MY', 'https://www.um.edu.mt/', 'http://www.facebook.com/universityofmalta', 'institutions/1619789812_maltta.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:36:52', '2021-04-30 19:36:52'),
(380, 'Facultad de Música', 'To train interpreters, composers, musical educators and researchers of musical art with a high professional level and great social commitment, who generate new knowledge, preserve the national and international musical heritage, and promote a culture of peace, respect for human rights, and cultural diversity. and gender equity, in a changing and complex local and global context.', 'Music', 'Xicoténcatl # 126, Col. Del Carmen, Coyoacán, CP 04100 Mexico City, Federal District', 'cvaldez@fam.unam.mx', '5601 3210', '1', '5601 3210', 'MX', 'http://www.fam.unam.mx/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Escuela-Nacional-de-M%C3%BAsica-UNAM/320116767743', 'institutions/1619789996_UNAM.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:39:56', '2021-04-30 19:39:56'),
(381, 'Monterrey College of Music and Dance', 'We congratulate Valeria García, 8th year student of the Bachelor of Classical Dance, who will join the INBAL National Dance Company from March 2021! Valeria García is ready to start the next stage of her career in March, when she joins the dance corps of the National Dance Company of the National Institute of Fine Arts and Literature', 'Music', 'Father Mier 1720 Poniente, Col. Obispado, Monterrey Nuevo León, CP 64060', 'diffusion@esmdm.edu.mx', '(81) 1253 2300', '1', '(81) 8348 2319', 'MX', 'http://esmdm.edu.mx/', 'http://esmdm.edu.mx/#', 'institutions/1619790144_esmdm.JPG', '2021-04-30 19:42:24', '2021-04-30 19:42:24'),
(382, 'ArtEZ Conservatorium', 'The ArtEZ Institute of the Arts, founded in 2006, has campuses at Enschede, Arnhem and Zwolle and includes some graduate programs. It consists of schools of music, fine arts, design, architecture, fashion, dance, theatre, and education in art. The Arnhem programs concentrate on jazz and pop performance (through the Academy of Pop Music), composition, music theatre and the ArtEZ Air performance program for brass and reed players.', 'Music', 'Onderlangs 9, 6812 CE Arnhem, Arnhem, The Netherlands', 'info@artez.nl', '026 35 35 600', '1', '026 35 35 600', 'NL', 'https://www.artez.nl/dit-is-artez/academies/artez-conservatorium', 'https://www.facebook.com/artezhogeschool', 'institutions/1619806354_artez.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:12:34', '2021-05-01 00:12:34'),
(383, 'Conservatorium van Amsterdam', 'The Conservatorium van Amsterdam offers courses ranging from classical music, jazz and early music to opera, latin and popular music. Owing to the many special projects, the curriculum guarantees a strong link between theory and practice. Both in the bachelor\'s and the master\'s degree programmes students are given ample opportunity to make individual choices and go their own way.', 'Music', 'Conservatorium van Amsterdam\r\nOosterdokskade 151\r\n1011 DL Amsterdam', 'conservatorium@ahk.nl', '+31(0)20 5277550', '1', '+31(0)20 5277550', 'NL', 'https://www.conservatoriumvanamsterdam.nl/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConservatoriumVanAmsterdam', 'institutions/1619806465_amsterdam.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:14:25', '2021-05-01 00:14:25'),
(384, 'Maastricht Academy of Music', 'Meet people from around the globe as Conservatorium Maastricht is the most international conservatory in Europe. 56 countries are represented in our community. 75% of our students are international and many projects, masterclasses, and programmes are without borders.', 'Music', 'Bonnefantenstraat 15\r\n6211 KL Maastricht', 'communicatie.conservatorium@zuyd.nl', '+31(0)43-3466680', '1', '+31(0)43-3466680', 'NL', 'https://www.conservatoriummaastricht.nl/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriummaastricht/', 'institutions/1619806551_zuyd.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:15:51', '2021-05-01 00:15:51');
INSERT INTO `institutions` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `category`, `address`, `email`, `phone`, `is_active`, `land_line`, `country`, `web_url`, `social_url`, `file`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(385, 'Royal Conservatory of The Hague', 'The Royal Conservatoire was founded in 1826. Since the day it was established the link between innovation and tradition has been at the heart of the institute’s activities. Innovation does not come naturally. It is built on tradition. It is the result of establishing educated relationships between traditional views and new ideas.', 'Music', 'Juliana van Stolberglaan 1\r\n2595 CA The Hague', 'info@koncon.nl', '+31 70 315 15 15', '1', '+31 70 315 15 15', 'NL', 'http://www.koncon.nl/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/royal.conservatoire', 'institutions/1619806685_koncon.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:18:05', '2021-05-01 00:18:05'),
(386, 'Codarts University for the Arts', 'Codarts is a Rotterdam based international university providing high level professional arts education in music, dance and circus arts. The university has about 1,000 students, of 65 nationalities, and around 480 staff members.', 'Music', 'Kruisplein 26\r\n3012 CC Rotterdam\r\nThe Netherlands', 'codarts@codarts.nl', '+31 10 217 11 00', '1', '+31 10 217 11 00', 'NL', 'http://www.codarts.nl/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Codarts', 'institutions/1619806801_codarts.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:20:01', '2021-05-01 00:20:01'),
(387, 'Utrechts Conservatorium', 'HKU distinguishes itself with higher education in the arts and media. We are a driving force in courses and innovation for the creative industries, and one of the largest art universities in Europe. HKU has nine schools with a total of 4400 students: Fine Art, Design, Music and Technology, Games and Interaction, Art and Economy, Media, Utrechts Conservatorium, Theatre and HKU College.', 'Music', 'Nieuwekade 1\r\n3511 RV Utrecht', 'sz@hku.nl', '+31 (0) 30-2091509', '1', '+31 (0) 30-2091509', 'NL', 'https://www.hku.nl/web/English.htm', 'https://www.facebook.com/hku.utrecht/', 'institutions/1619806908_hku.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:21:48', '2021-05-01 00:21:48'),
(388, 'University of Auckland', 'Retaining a position in the top ten reaffirms the University of Auckland’s strong commitment to sustainability and making a positive social impact through its partnerships, research, teaching, operations, community engagement and knowledge transfer.', 'Music', 'Private Bag 92019\r\nAuckland 1142\r\nNew Zealand', 'city.security@auckland.ac.nz', '(09) 923 5025', '1', '(09) 923 5025', 'NZ', 'https://www.auckland.ac.nz/en.html', 'http://www.facebook.com/UniofAkl', 'institutions/1619807049_aukland.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:24:09', '2021-05-01 00:24:09'),
(389, 'University of Waikato', 'The University of Waikato will provide you with the foundational knowledge and experience you need to achieve your career and life goals.\r\n\r\nWith our focus on academic excellence and innovation, you will become part of a group known for making a big difference in the world around them.\r\n\r\nJoin our warm and welcoming community of students from all over New Zealand and the globe.', 'Music', 'The University of Waikato\r\nTe Whare Wananga o Waikato\r\nGate 1, Knighton Road\r\nHamilton 3240', 'info@waikato.ac.nz', '+64 7 838 4610', '1', '+64 7 838 4610', 'NZ', 'http://www.waikato.ac.nz/', 'https://www.facebook.com/WaikatoUniversity', 'institutions/1619807180_waikato.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:26:20', '2021-05-01 00:26:20'),
(390, 'University of Canterbury', 'At UC you have the opportunity to turn theory into practice. Apply and build your skills in research, analysis, writing, and presentation in real-world contexts with an internship or placement. Internships and placements are offered in many subjects including Arts, Education, Engineering, and Commerce.', 'Music', '20 Kirkwood Avenue, Upper Riccarton, Christchurch 8041, New Zealand', 'info@canterbury.ac.nz', '+64 3 364 3443', '1', '+64 3 364 3443', 'NZ', 'https://www.canterbury.ac.nz/', 'https://www.facebook.com/universitycanterbury', 'institutions/1619807340_uc.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:29:00', '2021-05-01 00:29:00'),
(391, 'University of Otago', 'At the University of Otago, you will have the option to study Science, Health Sciences, Humanities and Commerce. Most of you will study at the main Dunedin campus and live in one of the 14 well-appointed and friendly residential colleges, or in one of the many character-filled flats in surrounding streets.s', 'Music', '362 Leith Street\r\nDunedin 9016\r\nNew Zealand', 'university@otago.ac.nz', '+64 3 479 7000', '1', '+64 3 479 7000', 'AF', 'https://www.otago.ac.nz/', 'https://www.facebook.com/otagouniversity', 'institutions/1619807458_otago.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:30:58', '2021-05-01 00:30:58'),
(392, 'University of Agder', 'UiA will be an open and inclusive university, characterized by a culture of collaboration.\r\nKnowledge is co-created when employees, students and the environment challenge each other.', 'Music', 'Universitetet i Agder\r\nPostboks 422\r\n4604 Kristiansand', 'post@uia.no', '+47 38 14 10 00', '1', '+47 38 14 10 00', 'NO', 'https://www.uia.no/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/AgderUniversity/', 'institutions/1619807641_agder.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:34:01', '2021-05-01 00:34:01'),
(393, 'Grieg Academy', 'Our profile is modelled on internationally recognised performing arts environments (classical, jazz, folk music), composition, music therapy, musicology and music education. The study programme emphasises independence and reflection. Students are able to explore a wide range of expressions and practical approaches, and develop through dialogue and critical discussion.', 'Music', 'Møllendalsveien 61 /\r\n\r\nLars Hilles gate 3 for Griegakademiet\r\n\r\n5009 Bergen', 'post@kmd.uib.no', '+47 55 58 73 00', '1', '+47 55 58 73 00', 'NO', 'http://www.uib.no/en/grieg', 'https://www.facebook.com/kmdbergen/', 'institutions/1619807778_uib.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:36:18', '2021-05-01 00:36:18'),
(394, 'Tromso University College, Faculty of Art, Music Conservatory', 'UiT The Arctic University of Norway is the third largest in Norway and the northernmost university of the world. Its location on the edge of the Arctic implies a mission. The Arctic is of increasing global importance. Climate change, the exploitation of Arctic resources and environmental threats are topics of great public concern, and which the University of Tromsø takes special interest in. At UiT The Arctic University of Norway you can explore global issues from a close-up perspective.', 'Music', 'UiT Norwegian Arctic University\r\n\r\nPO Box 6050 Langnes\r\n9037 Tromsø', 'postmottak@uit.no', '77 64 40 00', '1', '77 64 40 00', 'NO', 'https://uit.no/startsida', 'https://www.facebook.com/UniTromso', 'institutions/1619807982_uit no.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:39:42', '2021-05-01 00:39:42'),
(395, 'University of Stavanger', 'We have available study places for certain instruments within performing music studies in both classical and jazz, in addition to Practical-Pedagogical Education (PPU) in performing and creative arts and Digital School Corps studies.', 'Music', 'University of Stavanger, PO Box 8600, 4036 Stavanger', 'post@uis.no', '51831000', '1', '51831000', 'NO', 'https://www.uis.no/nb', 'post@uis.no', 'institutions/1619808174_stavanger.JPG', '2021-05-01 00:42:54', '2021-05-01 00:42:54'),
(396, 'Universidad de San Martín de Porres', 'The University of San Martín de Porres, traces its origins to the Pro-Deo Institute, a house dedicated to the cultivation of philosophy and theology that was founded by the RP Dr. Vicente Sánchez Valer of the order of preachers (Dominicans). Shortly after Pope John XXIII raised Blessed Fray Martín de Porres Velásquez of the Dominican Order of Peru to the altars, the University was founded under the invocation of the new saint; on May 17, 1962.', 'Music', 'ima Headquarters: Jr. Las Calandrias N ° 151 - 291 Santa Anita, Lima - Peru', 'medicina@usmp.pe', '(511) 317-2130.', '1', '(511) 317-2130.', 'PE', 'https://www.usmp.edu.pe/', 'https://www.facebook.com/usmpoficial/', 'institutions/1619854234_usmp.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:30:34', '2021-05-01 13:30:34'),
(397, 'Pontifical Catholic University of Peru', 'It is a plural and tolerant academic community, respectful of freedom of conscience and religion, inspired by ethical, democratic and Catholic principles.\r\nIt offers a civic, humanistic, scientific and comprehensive training of excellence.\r\nIt contributes to expanding knowledge through research and innovation at the international level.', 'Music', 'Campus principal\r\nAv. Universitaria 1801, San Miguel\r\nLima 32, Perú', 'erasmus@pucp.pe', '626-2000', '1', '626-2000', 'PE', 'https://www.pucp.edu.pe/', 'https://facebook.com/pucp/', 'institutions/1619854418_pucp.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:33:38', '2021-05-01 13:33:38'),
(398, 'Universidad Peruana de Ciencias Aplicadaas', 'The Peruvian University of Applied Sciences (UPC) was born in 1994 as an educational institution based on creativity and innovation, aimed at training future professionals, who will be the protagonists of the transformation of our country.', 'Music', 'Av. Prolongación Primavera 2390, Los Álamos de Monterrico, Santiago de Surco, Lima, Peru', 'guillermo.quiroga@upc', '+51 1 6303333', '1', '+51 1 6303333', 'PE', 'https://www.upc.edu.pe/', 'https://www.facebook.com/upcedu', 'institutions/1619854596_upc.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:36:36', '2021-05-01 13:36:36'),
(399, 'Bydgoszcz : Akademia muzyczna', 'Bromberger Konservatorium der Musik (founded in 1904 by Arnold Schattschneider and Wilhelm Winterfeld), the City Conservatory of Music (founded in 1927 by Zdzisław Jahnke), the Music Society of IJ Paderewski (founded in 1922), or several singing societies, but the range of their artistic influence was primarily local. In 1938, on the initiative of the Music Society, a symphony orchestra with its director Alfons Rösler was established, but its activity ended with the outbreak of World War II.', 'Music', 'Academy of Music Feliksa Nowowiejskiego in Bydgoszcz\r\nul. Słowackiego 7, 85-008 Bydgoszcz\r\nNIP: 554-031-32-25', 'sekretariat@amfn.pl', '+48 52 321-05-82,', '1', '+48 52 321-05-82,', 'PL', 'http://www.amuz.bydgoszcz.pl/', 'https://www.facebook.com/amuzbydgoszcz/', 'institutions/1619854808_amuz.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:40:08', '2021-05-01 13:40:08'),
(400, 'Akademia muzyczna \"Stanislas Moniuzko', 'Academy of Music Stanisław Moniuszko in Gdańsk is a public academic, artistic school. It was established by the order of the Minister of Culture and Art of September 25, 1947 as the State Higher School of Music in Sopot. Then it was renamed, by the regulation of the Council of Ministers of September 30, 1966, as of September 30, 1966, the State Higher School of Music in Gdańsk, and finally, by the regulation of the Council of Ministers of December 1, 1981, as of December 1, 1981.', 'Music', 'Academy of Music Stanisław Moniuszko in Gdańsk,\r\nul. Łąkowa 1-2\r\n80-743 Gdańsk', 'rektorat@amuz.gda.pl', '(+48 58) 3009 201', '1', '(+48 58) 3009 201', 'PL', 'https://www.amuz.gda.pl/en', 'https://www.facebook.com/amuz.gdansk', 'institutions/1619854980_amuz gdansk.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:43:00', '2021-05-01 13:43:00'),
(401, 'Akademia muzyczna \"Karol Szymanowski', 'From October 1, 2004 to September 30, 2019, the unit operated under the name of the Department of Composition, Interpretation, Education and Jazz. Earlier, on April 29, 2004, by a joint decision of the Faculty Councils, the existing departments: I - Composition, Theory and Music Education, and the V Department - Jazz and Popular Music - were merged into a new organizational unit. On the same day, the Jazz Institute was initiated as part of the newly established Faculty', 'Music', 'ul. Zacisze 3 40-025 Katowice', 'Dziekanati@am.katowice.pl', '+48 32 779 22 58', '1', '+48 32 779 22 58', 'PL', 'http://www.am.katowice.pl/', '-', 'institutions/1619855197_am katowice.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:46:37', '2021-05-01 13:46:37'),
(402, 'Łódź: Akademia muzyczna', 'Academy of Music Grażyna and Kiejstut Bacewicz in Łódź was established in 1945 on the basis of the pre-war musical traditions of the Helena Kijeńska-Dobkiewiczowa Conservatory. Since its inception, it has consistently played a significant role in shaping the musical life of the city and the region. The patrons of the Academy are outstanding artists born in Łódź: the famous composer and violinist Grażyna Bacewicz and Kiejstut Bacewicz.', 'Music', 'Academy of Music\r\nthem. Grażyna and Kiejstut Bacewicz in Łódź', 'rektorat@amuz.lodz.pl', '+ 48 42 662 16 01', '1', '+ 48 42 662 16 01', 'PL', 'http://www.amuz.lodz.pl/pl/', '-', 'institutions/1619855478_am lodz.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:51:18', '2021-05-01 13:51:18'),
(403, 'Poznan: Akademia muzyczna', 'The history of the university dates back to 1920 - it was then that the State Academy and School of Music began operating, renamed the State Conservatory of Music in 1922. From 1947, it functioned as the State Higher School of Music, and from 1981 - as the Academy of Music. Ignacy Jan Paderewski in Poznań. From the beginning of our activity until today, we are proud of the teaching staff created and created by outstanding figures of the Polish music community.', 'Music', 'Academy of Music\r\nthem. Ignacego Jan Paderewski\r\nin Poznań\r\nul. Święty Marcin 87\r\n61-808 Poznań', 'amuz@amuz.edu.pl', '+48 61 856 89 00', '1', '+48 61 856 89 00', 'PL', 'http://amuz.edu.pl/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Akademia-Muzyczna-im-Ignacego-Jana-Paderewskiego-w-Poznaniu/217461635055892?fref=ts', 'institutions/1619855605_amuz edu.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:53:25', '2021-05-01 13:53:25'),
(404, 'Varsovia: Akademia muzyczna \"Fryderyk Chopin', 'The Fryderyk Chopin University of Music is the oldest and largest Polish music university, constantly expanding cooperation with the largest music centers in Poland and in the world. \r\n\r\nOur students study at nine faculties in Warsaw and at the branch of the FCUM in Białystok in the following fields: composition and theory of music, conducting, instrumental studies, vocal studies, artistic education in the field of musical art, church music, dance, jazz and stage music, sound engineering.', 'Music', 'ul. Okólnik 2,\r\n00–368 Warsaw', 'info@chopin.edu.pl', '(22) 827 72 41', '1', '(22) 827 72 41', 'PL', 'https://chopin.edu.pl', 'https://www.facebook.com/UMFChopin', 'institutions/1619855744_umfc.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:55:44', '2021-05-01 13:55:44'),
(405, 'Breslavia: Akademia muzyczna', 'Currently at the Academy of Music. Karol Lipiński in Wrocław educates nearly 700 students and doctoral students developing their talents and passions at first and second degree studies and at the Doctoral School, in almost all musical specialties, within seven fields and over thirty areas, in Polish and English. We are constantly working to ensure that our students and doctoral students learn in the best possible conditions and at the highest possible level.', 'Music', 'pl. Jana Pawła II No. 2, 50-043 Wrocław', 'kancelaria.ogolna@amkl.edu.pl', '+48 71 31 00 500', '1', '+48 71 31 00 500', 'PL', 'http://amuz.wroc.pl/', 'https://www.facebook.com/AMKLwroc', 'institutions/1619855866_amuz wroc.JPG', '2021-05-01 13:57:46', '2021-05-01 13:57:46'),
(406, 'Silliman University College of Performing and Visual Arts', 'The College of Performing and Visual Arts started out in 1912 as the Music Department of the College of Arts and Sciences. Since the beginning, however, the inspiration to create an independent college was already there, even as far back as 1906 when Dr. Walter O. MacIntire organized the Silliman Band.', 'Music', '1 Hibbard Avenue, Dumaguete City, Negros Oriental, 6200 Philippines', 'copa@su.edu.ph', '+035 4226002 loc 250', '1', '+035 4226002 loc 250', 'PH', 'https://su.edu.ph/', 'http://www.facebook.com/SillimanUniversity', 'institutions/1619856042_silliman.JPG', '2021-05-01 14:00:42', '2021-05-01 14:00:42'),
(407, 'University of Santo Tomas Conservatory of Music', 'While the University of Santo Tomas holds the distinction of being Asia’s oldest existing university, its age is coupled with its preeminence in Philippine education. Not only does it boast of several firsts in the different realms of education. It also has administrators and faculty members who are holding leadership positions in the Philippines’ policy-making bodies and professional organizations, helping influence policies for the betterment of the society in general.', 'Music', 'Albertus Magnus Building, Ruaño Drive, UST, Sampaloc, Manila', 'cb.online@ust.edu.ph', '+63-2-3406-1611', '1', '+63-2-3406-1611', 'PH', 'http://www.ust.edu.ph/', 'https://www.facebook.com/UST1611official/', 'institutions/1619856223_santo tomas.JPG', '2021-05-01 14:03:43', '2021-05-01 14:03:43'),
(408, 'University of Minho', 'We are a family owned and operated business that has been in the business for over 30 years.\r\nThe University of Minho is a public foundation with a private law regime, under the Legal Regime of Higher Education Institutions.', 'Music', 'Universidade do Minho\r\nLargo do Paço\r\n4704-553 Braga', 'gcii@reitoria.uminho.pt', '+351 253601100', '1', '+351 253601100', 'PT', 'https://www.uminho.pt/PT', 'https://www.facebook.com/Universidade-do-Minho-Oficial-111501795592752/?fref=ts', 'institutions/1619857245_minho.JPG', '2021-05-01 14:20:45', '2021-05-01 14:20:45'),
(409, 'Polytechnic Institute of Lisbon', 'We are a public higher education institution that develops its activity through six Schools and two Institutes with a diversified training offer covering the arts, business sciences, health sciences, communication, education and engineering.\r\n\r\nWe are a space of freedom and responsibility where teachers, non-teaching staff and students work with the aim of increasing scientific, technological and artistic knowledge.', 'Music', 'Instituto Politécnico de Lisboa\r\n\r\nEstrada de Benfica, 529\r\n\r\n1549-020 Lisboa', 'geral@sc.ipl.pt', '(+351) 217 101 200', '1', '(+351) 217 101 200', 'PT', 'https://www.ipl.pt/', 'https://www.facebook.com/politecnicodelisboa', 'institutions/1619857404_ipl.JPG', '2021-05-01 14:23:24', '2021-05-01 14:23:24'),
(410, 'University of Évora', 'The University of Évora was the second university to be founded in Portugal. After the founding of the University of Coimbra in 1537, the need for another university to serve the south of the country was felt. Évora, ecclesiastical metropolis and temporary residence of the Court, immediately emerged as the most suitable city. Although the original idea of ​​creating the second university of the Kingdom belonged to D. João III, it was up to Cardinal D. Henrique to put it into practice.', 'Music', 'Rua do Cardeal Rei, s / n, 7000-849 Évora\r\nLargo dos Colegiais , Nº 2, 7004-516 Évora', 'uevora@uevora.pt', '+351 266 740 800', '1', '+351 266 740 800', 'AF', 'https://www.uevora.pt/', 'https://www.facebook.com/uevora', 'institutions/1619857608_evora.JPG', '2021-05-01 14:26:48', '2021-05-01 14:26:48'),
(411, 'University of Aveiro', 'The University of Aveiro (UA) is currently attended by about 13600 undergraduate students and 3800 graduate students. They are the raison d\'être of the University of Aveiro.  Here they spend years of learning and enriching experiences until they graduate and enter the job market. The AU welcomes them, integrates them and accompanies them throughout their academic path and beyond, when they integrate the world of work as the professionals of excellence for which they are trained.', 'Music', 'Santiago University Campus\r\n3810-193 Aveiro Portugal', 'geral@ua.pt', '+351 234 370 200', '1', '+351 234 370 200', 'PT', 'https://www.ua.pt/', 'https://www.facebook.com/universidadedeaveiro/', 'institutions/1619857928_averio.JPG', '2021-05-01 14:32:08', '2021-05-01 14:32:08'),
(412, 'Moscow Conservatory', 'It is is a musical educational institution located in Moscow, Russia. It grants undergraduate and graduate degrees in musical performance and musical research. The conservatory offers various degrees including Bachelor of Music Performance, Master of Music and PhD in research.', 'Music', '13/6 Bolshaya Nikitskaya Street\r\nMoscow, 125009, Russian Federation', 'pravka@mosconsv.ru', '+7 (495) 255 1994', '1', '+7 (495) 255 1994', 'RU', 'http://www.mosconsv.ru/en/default.aspx', 'https://www.mosconsv.ru/en/page.aspx?id=130264#', 'institutions/1619858203_moscow conser.jfif', '2021-05-01 14:36:43', '2021-05-01 14:36:43'),
(413, 'Saint Petersburg Conservatory', 'The St. Petersburg State Rimsky-Korsakov Conservatory is one of the most famous music universities in the world and the first higher educational institution of professional music education in Russia. Founded in 1862 at the initiative of the Imperial Russian Musical Society.', 'Music', '190068, St. Petersburg, st. Glinka, 2, letter \"A\"', 'rectorat@conservatory.ru', '+7 (812) 644-99-88', '1', '+7 (812) 644-99-88', 'RU', 'http://www.conservatory.ru/', 'https://www.facebook.com/spb.conservatory', 'institutions/1619882036_1862.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:13:56', '2021-05-01 21:13:56'),
(414, 'Gnessin State Musical College', 'The beginning of the long history of the creation and formation of a large complex of educational institutions named after the Gnesins is February 15, 1895 - it was on this day that the first student came to the E. and M. Gnesins Music School, one of the small private music educational institutions that were actively opening at that time in Moscow.', 'Music', '21069 Moscow st. Povarskaya d. 30-36 (metro \"Arbatskaya\" or \"Barrikadnaya\")', 'priem@gnesin-academy.ru', '+7 495 691-15-54', '1', '+7 495 691-15-54', 'RU', 'http://www.gnesin-academy.ru/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Gnesinacademy/', 'institutions/1619882199_gnesin.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:16:39', '2021-05-01 21:16:39'),
(415, 'Kazan Conservatory', 'The Conservatoire was founded in 1945. It is situated in the Middle Volga region in a multi-ethnic area, and trains students from Russia, China, Korea, Japan and other countries both in Western and Tatar music cultures.', 'Music', 'Ul Bolskaya Krasnaya 38, Kazan 420015, Tatarstan, Russia', 'kgk-dekanat@mail.ru', '+7 8432 365 641', '1', '+7 8432 365 641', 'RU', 'http://kazanconservatoire.ru/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=21&Itemid=347', 'https://www.facebook.com/kazancons', 'institutions/1619882462_kazan.png', '2021-05-01 21:21:02', '2021-05-01 21:21:02'),
(416, 'Saratov Conservatory', 'The Saratov Conservatory trains professionals in the field of performing and acting, as well as musicology and composition. Here, applicants will have an interesting life and scope for creativity, where, in addition to lectures, fascinating practical classes, master classes with famous musicians and teachers are held.', 'Music', 'Saratov, prosp. them. Kirov S.M., 1', 'sgk@sarcons.ru', '8 (845 2) 39-00-29', '1', '8 (845 2) 39-00-29', 'RU', 'http://www.sarcons.ru/?fbclid=IwAR3cUQ4U5l6hdaLojwCDbSFoY02JMNmkFDg9xoJQJ0ukGOz1TeEnZxt9y0s', 'https://www.facebook.com/saratovconservatory/', 'institutions/1619882633_sarcons.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:23:53', '2021-05-01 21:23:53'),
(417, 'Ulyanovsk State University', 'In 1985, the USSR government adopted a resolution to establish the first university in Ulyanovsk, which was to open its doors to first students in 1995. The government acted on the request of the Ulyanovsk region administration, which hoped for a new academic institution to satisfy the growing demand for professionals in rapidly developing fields, such as radiophysics, electronics, mathematics, information technologies, medicine.', 'Music', '1 Tverskaya Street, GSP-3, Russia, 125993, Moscow', 'contact@ulsu.ru', '+7 495 629-70–62', '1', '+7 495 629-70–62', 'RU', 'http://www.english.ulsu.ru/1.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/UlSU.ru', 'institutions/1619882754_ulsu.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:25:54', '2021-05-01 21:25:54'),
(418, 'Urals Mussorgsky State Conservatoire', 'The Ural Conservatory was founded in 1934 and became the first music university in the entire territory of the USSR east of the Volga region. The choice of the city for the new conservatory was due to the status of Yekaterinburg, from a district city turned into the capital of the Big Urals (since 1924 - Sverdlovsk), and the presence of a music school, opened in 1916 on the basis of the classes of the Imperial Russian Musical Society.', 'Music', '620014, Yekaterinburg, prosp. Lenin, 26', 'mail@uralconsv.org', '+7 (343) 371-21-80', '1', '+7 (343) 371-21-80', 'RU', 'https://uralconsv.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/koncert.ugk', 'institutions/1619882896_ural.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:28:16', '2021-05-01 21:28:16'),
(419, 'Moscow State University of Culture and Art', 'The University was founded in 1930 as the Moscow Library Institute and gained its current name and status in 1999. Under the control of the Ministry of Culture, it offers programs in music, drama, visual arts, film, journalism, arts management and administration, among others. Foreign students are welcome to apply, and Russian language classes are held.', 'Music', 'Ul Bibliotechnaya 7, 141400 Khimki-6, Moscow region 141406, Russia', 'info@msuc.org', '+74095 570 0444', '1', '+74095 570 0444', 'RU', 'http://www.mguki.ru/?fbclid=IwAR3DtEc0HtTYQEKGZQqY8-kR5k4ff56R88tQYkD-mPQtFoR_stHXbxmjFP0', 'https://www.facebook.com/Moscow-State-University-of-Culture-and-Art-176824405688645/', 'institutions/1619883168_empty.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:32:48', '2021-05-01 21:32:48'),
(420, 'Academy of Music Ljubjana', 'The University of Ljubljana, Academy of Music (UL AG) is the only higher education university institution for the entire field of music art in the country and therefore of national importance for the development of Slovenian musical creativity, reproduction and music pedagogy.', 'Music', 'Akademija za glasbo Univerze v Ljubljani, Stari trg 34, 1000 Ljubljana', 'dekanat@ag.uni-lj.si', '+386 1 2427 300', '1', '+386 1 2427 300', 'SI', 'https://www.ag.uni-lj.si/', 'https://www.facebook.com/akademijazaglasbo', 'institutions/1619883661_ag uni.JPG', '2021-05-01 21:41:01', '2021-05-01 21:41:01'),
(421, 'University of Arts in Belgrade', 'The University of Arts in Belgrade is primarily made up of people. These are the most talented, most creative, most dedicated and most valuable individuals - his students and professors. Therefore, the vision of the university is made up of the personal and individual visions of all our students and professors - to realize their potential as artists and scientists.', 'Music', 'Kosančićev venac 29\r\n11000 Belgrade', 'rektorat@arts.bg.ac.rs', '+381 11 262 5166', '1', '+381 11 262 5166', 'RS', 'http://www.arts.bg.ac.rs/', '-', 'institutions/1619897663_arts bg ac rrs.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:34:23', '2021-05-02 01:34:23'),
(422, 'University of Novi Sad', 'The University of Novi Sad was being created in a special milieu built by generations of foremost intellectuals, as well as institutions of particular national significance, in the towns of Vojvodina. Their duration is measured in centuries. The foundations of higher education in today’s Autonomous Province of Vojvodina, and Serbia as a whole, were laid around 1740, with the establishment of the seminarynamed Collegium Vissariono – Pawlovicsianum Petrovaradinense in Novi Sad.', 'Music', 'Dr Zorana Đinđića 1\r\n21102 Novi Sad, Srbija', 'rektorat@uns.ac.rs', '+381 21 485-2000', '1', '+381 21 485-2000', 'RS', 'http://www.uns.ac.rs/index.php/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/UniverzitetuNS', 'institutions/1619897767_uns ac.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:36:07', '2021-05-02 01:36:07'),
(423, 'University of Kragujevac', 'University of Kragujevac rose from the foundations of the Lyceum of the Principality of Serbia, the first higher education institution in modern Serbia, established in Kragujevac by the decree of Prince Milos Obrenović on July 1st, 1838. Its first rector was Atanasije Nikolic (1803 – 1882). The Lyceum of the Principality of Serbia planted the seed of higher education from which first modern higher education institutions originated in the beginning of the 1960s.', 'Music', 'Jovana Cvijica bb, Kragujevac, Serbia', 'unikg@kg.ac.rs', '+381 (0)34 370270', '1', '+381 (0)34 370270', 'RS', 'https://www.kg.ac.rs/', '-', 'institutions/1619897865_kg ac rs.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:37:45', '2021-05-02 01:37:45'),
(424, 'University of Niš', 'Since the founding of the University of Nis to date, a diploma of higher education institutions have acquired  75,494  students (including 1,365 foreign nationals), master studies completed 7,429  students, master\'s degree 2,621  postgraduates and doctorates   2,653  doctoral candidates.\r\n\r\nMISSION OF THE UNIVERSITY: inclusion in the single European educational space in accordance with the highest standards of quality of educational, scientific research and professional work.', 'Music', 'University of Nis\r\nUniversity Square 2, 18106 Nis e-', 'uniuni@ni.ac.rs', '(+381) 18 257 970', '1', '(+381) 18 257 970', 'RS', 'https://www.ni.ac.rs/', 'https://www.facebook.com/studentskiparlamentnis/', 'institutions/1619897971_ni ac rs.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:39:31', '2021-05-02 01:39:31'),
(425, 'Univerzitet u Prištini', 'The university of Pristina was founded in the Socialist Autonomous Province of Kosovo, Socialist Republic of Serbia, Yugoslavia, in Pristina, the first academic year being 1969-1970, and functioning until 1999. However, because of political upheaval, war, consecutive expulsion of faculty of one ethnicity or the other, extensive differences between the ethnicities, it separated into two disjoint institutions using the same name, albeit simply to reflect ethnic identity.', 'Music', 'Филипа Вишњића бб, 38220 Косовска Митровица', 'rektorat@pr.ac.rs', '028 422 340', '1', '028 422 340', 'RS', 'https://pr.ac.rs/', 'https://www.facebook.com/univerzitetupristini/', 'institutions/1619898211_pr ac rs.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:43:31', '2021-05-02 01:43:31'),
(426, 'National University of Singapore', 'Since 2001, Singapore Raffles Music College (SRMC) has been one of Singapore’s leading schools for higher learning in music and dance, registered with the Committee for Private Education (CPE).\r\n\r\nSteeped in the tradition of excellence, SRMC possesses not only comprehensive curricula, excellent infrastructure, innovative teaching methods but also a team of highly qualified, dedicated and professional academic team.', 'Music', '456 Alexandra Road Fragrance Empire Building #09-02 Singapore 119962', 'admin@srmc.edu.sg', '(+65) 6362 5759', '1', '(+65) 6362 5759', 'SG', 'http://www.srmc.edu.sg/', 'https://www.facebook.com/SRMCsg/', 'institutions/1619898320_srmc.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:45:20', '2021-05-02 01:45:20'),
(427, 'Nanyang Academy of Fine Arts', 'The Academy was established in 1938 and the School of Performing Arts was established in 1997. It offers programs in the areas of music (Western and Chinese), design and media, fine art, fashion studies, arts management, dance, drama and education. Facilities include a recital hall, a recording studio, and an Italian harpsichord and a gamelan. A bank of instruments is available for student use. A new purpose-built building with state-of-the-art facilities is located in the Civic District.', 'Music', '80 Bencoolen Street, Singapore 189655', 'music@nafa.edu.sg', '+65 6512 1385', '1', '+65 6512 1385', 'SG', 'https://www.nafa.edu.sg/', 'https://www.facebook.com/NAFA', 'institutions/1619898459_nafa.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:47:39', '2021-05-02 01:47:39'),
(428, 'LASALLE College of the Arts', 'LASALLE College of the Arts offers 30 diploma, undergraduate and postgraduate programmes in fine arts, design communication, interior design, product design, film, animation, fashion, dance, music, theatre, arts management, arts pedagogy and practice, art therapy, Asian art histories and creative writing.', 'Music', '1 McNally Street\r\nSingapore 187940', 'contact.us@lasalle.edu.sg', '(+65) 6496 5000', '1', '(+65) 6496 5000', 'SG', 'http://www.lasalle.edu.sg/', 'https://www.facebook.com/lasalle.sg/', 'institutions/1619898733_lasale.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:52:13', '2021-05-02 01:52:13'),
(429, 'South African College of Music', 'The South African College of Music, founded by a group of musicians led by Madame Apolline Niay-Darroll, opened in 1910 in Strand Street, Cape Town, with six students. In 1912 Mr W.H. Bell was appointed Principal and, in 1914, the SACM moved to larger premises in Stal Plein.', 'Music', 'South African College of Music\r\nUniversity of Cape Town\r\nPrivate Bag\r\nRondebosch\r\n7701 South Africa', 'music@uct.ac.za', '+27 (0)21 650-2626', '1', '+27 (0)21 650-2626', 'ZA', 'http://www.sacm.uct.ac.za/', '-', 'institutions/1619899056_sacm.JPG', '2021-05-02 01:57:36', '2021-05-02 01:57:36'),
(430, 'Jeju National University', 'This institution is situated on Jeju Island, about 100 kilometers off the southern tip of the Korean Peninsula. It can trace its history back to 1952. In 2008 the Jeju National University of Education merged with the Cheju National University to form the Jeju National University as it is known today, the former Jeju National University of Education section now being know as the \'Teachers College of Jeju National University.', 'Music', '4810 Hwapuk 1-dong, Jeju-si, Jeju-do, South Korea', 'kontakt@cheju-e.ac.kr', '064754-2114', '1', '064754-2114', 'AF', 'http://www.jejunu.ac.kr/main', '-', 'institutions/1619967301_jeju.JPG', '2021-05-02 20:55:02', '2021-05-02 20:55:02'),
(431, 'Chonnam National University', '77 Yongbong-ro, Buk-gu, Gwangju 61186, South Korea', 'Music', '7, Yongbong-ro, Buk-gu, Gwangju, 61186, Korea', 'underia@jnu.ac.kr', '+82 62 530 1269', '1', '+82 62 530 1269', 'KR', 'http://global.jnu.ac.kr/jnumain.aspx', '-', 'institutions/1619968419_jnu.JPG', '2021-05-02 21:13:39', '2021-05-02 21:13:39'),
(432, 'Ewha Womans Universitity', 'This private university can trace its history back to 1886 with the establishment by the Methodist Church of Korea’s first school for women. It claims to be the world’s largest university for women and is based on Christian principles. The College of Music was founded in 1925, the Sacred Music Department in 1967, and the Korean Traditional Music Department in 1974. In 2010 the Graduate School of Performing Arts was established. There is an attached Institute of Music Research.', 'Music', 'Music Building Room #117, 11-1 Daehyeon-dong, Seodaemun-gu, Seoul, South Korea', 'music@ewha.ac.kr', '+82 2 3277 2849', '1', '+82 2 3277 2849', 'KR', 'http://eng.dima.ac.kr/main.html', '-', 'institutions/1619968588_dima.JPG', '2021-05-02 21:16:28', '2021-05-02 21:16:28'),
(433, 'Korea National University of Arts', 'Thinking that goes deeper: our artists seek to understand the world around us, and reflect society’s joys and sorrows in the works they craft.\r\nImagination that grows wider: our artists explore the infinite possibilities of art, and express their discoveries with the full spectrum of their creativity.\r\nWe believe in the power of art education. We believe the deeper art education grows, the wider it becomes; and the wider it grows, the deeper it becomes.', 'Music', 'Howon University, 64 Howondae 3gil, Impi, Gunsan city, Jeollabuk-do.Korea Zip code) 54058', 'tusarita@karts.ac.kr', '+82.2.746.9076', '1', '+82.2.746.9076', 'KR', 'http://www.karts.ac.kr/index_karts.jsp', '-', 'institutions/1619968997_k.JPG', '2021-05-02 21:23:17', '2021-05-02 21:23:17'),
(434, 'Pusan National University', 'The University was established in 1945. The College of Arts, founded in 1982, has departments of Western music, Korean music, dance, fine arts, formative arts, design, and art culture and image.', 'Music', '2 Busandaehak-ro, 63beon-gil, Jangjeon-dong, Geumjeong-gu, Busan 46241, South Korea', 'info@pusan.ac.kr', '+82 51 581 3694', '1', '+82 51 581 3694', 'KR', 'https://www.pusan.ac.kr/kor/Main.do', 'https://www.facebook.com/PusanNationalUniv', 'institutions/1619969209_pusan.JPG', '2021-05-02 21:26:49', '2021-05-02 21:26:49'),
(435, 'Seoul National University', 'This institution was established in 1946, being the first national university in Korea. The Asian Music Research Institute concentrates on Korean and Asian music, aiming to collect, organise, preserve and distribute information and materials on Korean, Asian and non-European music. The Western Music Research Institute was established in 1989, researching into all aspects of musicology.', 'Music', '1 Gwanak-ro, Gwanak-gu, Seoul 08816, South Korea', 'snuoia@snu.ac.kr', '+82 2 887 8658', '1', '+82 2 887 8658', 'KR', 'http://www.snu.ac.kr/index.html', '-', 'institutions/1619970998_snu.JPG', '2021-05-02 21:56:38', '2021-05-02 21:56:38'),
(436, 'Sookmyung Women\'s University', 'Sookmyung Women’s University is a private university in Yongsan-gu, Seoul, South Korea. Founded in 1906, Sookmyung is Korea’s first royal private educational institution for women. The university\'s name is derived from Hanja characters of sook and myung, which mean \"elegant\" and \"bright\" respectively. With its more than a century-long legacy and history, Sookmyung is renowned as one of the best women\'s universities nationwide.', 'Music', 'Cheongpa-ro,, 47-gil, 100 Cheongpa-dong 2ga, Youngsan-gu, Seoul, South Korea', 'gc9533@sookmyung.ac.kr', '+82 2 887 8658', '1', '+82 2 887 8658', 'KR', 'http://www.sookmyung.ac.kr/sookmyungkr/index.do', 'https://www.facebook.com/SookmyungUniversity', 'institutions/1619971275_sookmyyung.JPG', '2021-05-02 22:01:15', '2021-05-02 22:01:15'),
(437, 'Conservatori Superior de Música del Liceu', 'With the aim of extending musical training and its practice among the population, especially among children, agreements have been established with Schools of Music and Schools of General Regime; Through them, many students can follow the educational program and artistic activities of the Conservatori Liceu. Together, these centers form a network of linked schools, heirs of the branch centers founded in 1932 .', 'Music', 'C / Nou de la Rambla, 82-88 (access c / Estel s / n)\r\n08001 BARCELONA', 'fundacio@conservatori-liceu.es', '+34 933217200', '1', '+34 933217200', 'ES', 'https://www.conservatoriliceu.es/es/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriliceu.es', 'institutions/1619971705_conservatoriliceu.JPG', '2021-05-02 22:08:25', '2021-05-02 22:08:25'),
(438, 'Catalonia College of Music', 'The school is located at L\'Auditori, a performing arts center inaugurated in 1999 which also houses three concert halls and a museum. The school has an international faculty and student body, and includes departments for classical and contemporary music, early music, jazz and popular music, traditional music, musicology and ethnomusicology, theory and composition, music education, music business, and sonology.', 'Music', 'C/Padilla, 155 (Edifici L’Auditori)\r\n\r\n08013 Barcelona', 'acreditacio@esmuc.cat', '(+34) 93.352.30.11', '1', '(+34) 93.352.30.11', 'ES', 'http://www.esmuc.cat/', 'https://www.facebook.com/esmuccat?fref=ts', 'institutions/1619972027_esmuc.JPG', '2021-05-02 22:13:47', '2021-05-02 22:13:47'),
(439, 'Queen Sofía College of Music', 'Since December 12, 1990, when it was inaugurated in a solemn academic ceremony presided over by the then Minister of Education and Science Mr. Javier Solana Madariaga, the Royal Superior Conservatory of Music of Madrid has its headquarters in a remodeled pavilion of the century XVIII, in front of the Reina Sofía National Art Center and approximately 200 meters from Madrid\'s Atocha station. The director was then Miguel del Barco.', 'Music', 'C / Doctor Mata 2, 28012 Madrid', 'infosecre@rcsmm.eu', '+34 91 539 29 01', '1', '+34 91 539 29 01', 'ES', 'http://rcsmm.eu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Real-Conservatorio-Superior-de-M%C3%BAsica-de-Madrid-Oficial/114550645341250?notif_t=page_user_activity', 'institutions/1619972603_rcsmm.JPG', '2021-05-02 22:23:23', '2021-05-02 22:23:23'),
(440, 'Escuela de Música Joaquín Turina de Sevilla', 'Located in the heart of Seville, on Tetuán and Albareda streets, this School of Music takes its name, since 1999, from the famous Spanish and Sevillian composer Joaquín Turina , born a hundred years before a few meters from it. He has had the approval and support of his daughter, Obdulia Turina, and his grandson, José Luis Turina .', 'Music', 'Albareda, 8, 3a -41001 Sevilla - Espana', 'escuelaturina@estumusica.es', '+34954210723', '1', '+34954210723', 'ES', 'http://www.estumusica.es/', '-', 'institutions/1619976644_estumusica.JPG', '2021-05-02 23:30:44', '2021-05-02 23:30:44'),
(441, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de A Coruña', 'Higher music studies. Harp, accordion, bassoon, guitar, transverse flute, trumpet, horn, trombone, percussion, violin, viola, cello, tuba, singing, jazz, oboe, double bass, clarinet, saxophone.', 'Music', 'Rúa Manuel Murguía, 44, 15011 Coruña (A)', 'cmus.coruna@edu.xunta.es', '981.14.12.95', '1', '981.14.12.95', 'ES', 'https://www.csmcoruna.com/?lang=es', 'https://www.facebook.com/csmcoruna', 'institutions/1619976869_csm.JPG', '2021-05-02 23:34:29', '2021-05-02 23:34:29'),
(442, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de Vigo', 'This public Conservatorio was established in 1956. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Calle Manuel Olivié, 23, 36203 Vigo, Pontevedra, Spain', 'cmus.vigo@edu.xunta.es', '+34 986 481 807', '1', '+34 986 481 807', 'ES', 'http://csmvigo.com/?lang=gl', 'https://www.facebook.com/ConservatorioSuperiorDeVigo/', 'institutions/1619977052_csmvigo.JPG', '2021-05-02 23:37:32', '2021-05-02 23:37:32'),
(443, 'MUSIKENE Centro Superior de Música del País Vasco', 'This private Centre was founded in 2001. \'Musikene\' is the name of the Private Foundation for the Higher School of Music of the Basque Country that was responsible for creating it. A brand-new building was opened in 2016. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Europa Plaza 2, 20018 Donostia-San Sebastián, Spain', 'info@musikene.eus', '+34 94 302 3751', '1', '+34 94 302 3751', 'ES', 'http://musikene.eus/', 'https://www.facebook.com/musikenet', 'institutions/1619977180_msukene.JPG', '2021-05-02 23:39:40', '2021-05-02 23:39:40'),
(444, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música \"Eduardo Martínez Torner\"', 'The Conservatorium can trace its history back to 1883 and gained its current name and status in 1988. It holds summer courses for young musicians. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Plaza Corrada del Obispo s/n, 33003 Oviedo, Asturias, Spain', 'international@consmupa.com', '+34 985 203 720', '1', '+34 985 203 720', 'ES', 'http://consmupa.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/Conservatorio-Superior-de-Oviedo-420647874766638/?rf=110336118986855', 'institutions/1619977269_consmupa.JPG', '2021-05-02 23:41:09', '2021-05-02 23:41:09'),
(445, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de Castellón', 'This private Conservatorio was established in 1998. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Carrer del Marqués de la Ensenada 34-36, 12003 Castelló de la Plana, Castellón, Spain', '12005635@edu.gva.es', '964 399 455', '1', '964 399 455', 'ES', 'https://www.conservatorisuperiorcastello.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatorisuperiorcastello/', 'institutions/1619978503_csmc.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:01:43', '2021-05-03 00:01:43'),
(446, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música \"Bonifacio Gil\" de Badajoz', 'A private conservatorium founded in 1927. In addition to the professional diploma program there are programs at elementary and middle levels. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Plaza Soledad 8, 06001 Badajoz, Spain', 'conservatorio@dip-badajoz.es', '+34 924 229 778', '1', '+34 924 229 778', 'AF', 'https://csmbadajoz.es/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatorio.superiordebadajoz/', 'institutions/1619978643_csmbadajoz.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:04:03', '2021-05-03 00:04:03'),
(447, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música \"Óscar Esplá\" de Alicante', 'A center open to society as a whole to whose progress the CSMA must contribute. Essentially we intend to work to achieve a more humane Conservatory, from closeness to people; managing with and for them, fostering participation and dialogue. To achieve this, in my opinion, it is essential to promote the integration of people, groups, bodies and collectives around a common and shared project. A project in which we all feel part and of which no one feels excluded.', 'Music', 'C / Catedrátic Jaume Mas i Porcel, 2. 03005 Alicante (Spain).', '%20direccion@csmalicante.com', '966.478.665', '1', '966.478.665', 'ES', 'https://www.csmalicante.com/?fbclid=IwAR1MAS9UWr0PCHc93sEofR8JuFXt-JKfnnqt08AGIItiFvLX0KWzLVQMFKE', 'https://www.facebook.com/csmalicante/', 'institutions/1619978913_iseacv.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:08:33', '2021-05-03 00:08:33'),
(448, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de las Islas Baleares', 'The Conservatorio can trace its history back to 1881 and gained its current name and status in 1999. In addition to the professional music programs there are courses for children and interested persons from the local community. There are three campuses of the Conservatorio Superior.', 'Music', 'Carrer d’Alfons el Magnànim, 64\r\n07004 Palma,\r\nIlles Balears', 'conservatori@conservatoridemallorca.com', '971 763 444', '1', '971 763 444', 'ES', 'https://conservatorisuperior.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CSMIB/', 'institutions/1619979862_csmib.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:24:22', '2021-05-03 00:24:22'),
(449, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de Navarra', 'The Higher Conservatory of Music of Navarra is a public center, dependent on the Department of Education of the Government of Navarra, which imparts higher studies of music within the framework of the European Higher Education Area (EHEA) and whose main objective is the training of professionals qualified in the branches of interpretation, musicology, composition and musical pedagogy, providing them with high levels of technical, artistic, theoretical and humanistic training.', 'Music', 'Paseo Antonio Pérez Goyena nº 1. 31008 Pamplona-Iruña Telephone: 848 42 26 70', 'csmn.direccion@educacion.navarra.es', '848421139', '1', '848421139', 'ES', 'http://csmn.educacion.navarra.es/web1/', 'https://www.facebook.com/csmnavarra', 'institutions/1619979993_csmn navarra.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:26:33', '2021-05-03 00:26:33'),
(450, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música \"Rafael Orozco\" de Córdoba', 'The Conservatorio was founded in 1902 and gained its current name and status in 1972. It provides music tuition to advanced levels.', 'Music', 'Calle Ángel Saavedra 1, 14003 Córdoba, Spain', 'oficina@csmcordoba.com', '+34 957 379 648', '1', '+34 957 379 648', 'ES', 'http://www.csmcordoba.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/csmcordoba', 'institutions/1619980112_csm cordoba.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:28:32', '2021-05-03 00:28:32'),
(451, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música \"Victoria Eugenia\" de Granada', 'The Conservatorio was founded in 1921 and has departments of performance, composition, conducting, accompaniment, musicology and music education. There is active collaboration with the Manuel de Falla Archive and the Centre of Musical Documentation of Andalusia, both situated in Granada. Member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Calle San Jerónimo 46, 18001 Granada, Spain', 'oficina.edu@juntadeandalucia.es', '+34 95 889 3181', '1', '+34 95 889 3181', 'ES', 'http://www.conservatoriosuperiorgranada.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatorio.superiorgranada', 'institutions/1619980213_superior granda.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:30:13', '2021-05-03 00:30:13'),
(452, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de Jaén', 'The \"Andrés de Vandelvira\" Superior Music Conservatory of Jaén wants to welcome you to our website, the place from where you can get to know our center, the teachings that are taught, the activities that take place, and ultimately, live the day to day with all of us who are part of this institution.', 'Music', 'Superior Conservatory of Music \"Andrés de Vandelvira\" of Jaén\r\nCalle Compañía nº 1. 23002 Jaén', 'oficina@csmjaen.es', '+ 34 953 365 610', '1', '+ 34 953 365 610', 'ES', 'http://www.csmjaen.es/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CSMJAEN/', 'institutions/1619980373_csmjaen.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:32:53', '2021-05-03 00:32:53'),
(453, 'Conservatorio Superior de Música de Málaga', 'The Superior Conservatory of Music of Malaga was created in 1880, in the heat of the Philharmonic Society, being its first director Mr. Eduardo Ocón y Rivas. The Conservatory has been and is a first-rank musical education center in the state framework, and this importance is reflected in the fact that it was part of the group of six superior conservatories available to the Ministry of Education in the 1960s. .', 'Music', 'Plaza del Maestro Artola nº 2. 29013 - Málaga (Spain)', 'secretaria@conservatoriosuperiormalaga.com', '+34 697 95 02 95', '1', '+34 697 95 02 95', 'ES', 'https://conservatoriosuperiormalaga.com/?fbclid=IwAR0mWRJ2DejK-sG8YsI_zwMGjIKKo_14UrCbu0wevHtTjesgbLVRZbJkR10', 'https://www.facebook.com/conservatoriosuperiormalaga/', 'institutions/1619980492_superior malaga.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:34:52', '2021-05-03 00:34:52');
INSERT INTO `institutions` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `category`, `address`, `email`, `phone`, `is_active`, `land_line`, `country`, `web_url`, `social_url`, `file`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(454, 'Royal College of Music, Stockholm', 'This Royal College of Music, founded in 1771, is an independent college, financed both by private funds and the state. It is housed at the University of Stockholm. The College offers in-service training courses for professional musicians and music teachers, some by distance-mode. The Nordic Performance Master in Folk Music is offered jointly with the Carl Nielsen Academy of Music in Odense, Denmark and the Ole Bull Academy in Voss, Norway.', 'Music', 'Valhallavägen 105 SE-115 51 Stockholm, Sweden', 'info@kmh.se', '+46 8 664 1424', '1', '+46 8 664 1424', 'SE', 'http://www.kmh.se/english', 'https://www.facebook.com/kmh.stockholm', 'institutions/1619980662_royal college of music.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:37:42', '2021-05-03 00:37:42'),
(455, 'Karlstad University', 'The University was founded in 1843 as a Teacher Training College and gained its current name and status in 1999. The Ingesund College of Music was founded in 1923 and since 1978 has formed the School of Music of the University of Karlstad, located in Arvika in West Värmland, 80 kilometres north of Karlstad. It organises summer courses in orchestra, solo performance and methodology of teaching.', 'Music', 'Musikhögskolan Ingesund, 671-91 Arvika, Sweden.', 'info@imh.kau.se', '+46 5 570 385 21', '1', '+46 5 570 385 21', 'SE', 'https://www.kau.se/', 'https://www.instagram.com/', 'institutions/1619980778_kau se.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:39:38', '2021-05-03 00:39:38'),
(456, 'University of Gothenburg', 'The University Board is the university\'s highest decision-making body and the rector is the highest manager. The university also consists of a number of university-wide positions, units and bodies that support management and operations in various matters. The core business - research and education - is organized and run by eight faculties, including 38 departments, as well as the 30 or so center formations that exist within the university.', 'Music', 'University of Gothenburg\r\nBox 100\r\n405 30 Gothenburg', 'servicecenter@gu.se', '031-786 00 00', '1', '031-786 00 00', 'SE', 'https://www.gu.se/', 'https://www.facebook.com/goteborgsuniversitet', 'institutions/1619980958_gu se.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:42:38', '2021-05-03 00:42:38'),
(457, 'Örebro University', 'Örebro University offers many different opportunities for international people looking to study or research in Sweden. Every year, we receive hundreds of new students from around the world - each of them contribute to a globally-conscious campus that offers a highly-rewarding, personal study experience that helps you to find your future.', 'Music', 'Örebro University SE-701 82 Örebro', 'freemover@oru.se', '+46 19 303000', '1', '+46 19 30 30 00', 'SE', 'https://www.oru.se/english', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/International-Students-at-%C3%96rebro-University/261923733848348', 'institutions/1619981065_orebro.JPG', '2021-05-03 00:44:25', '2021-05-03 00:44:25'),
(458, 'Luleå University of Technolog', 'Luleå University of Technology was founded in the 1970s. Piteå is situated about 45 kilometers south of Luleå (the main university campus). The Department of Music and Media has two sections - Media and Experience Production, and the School of Music. Several courses are offered in English. Member of the University of the Arctic. An active member of the Association Européenne des Conservatoires, Académies de Musique et Musikhochschulen.', 'Music', 'Piteå campus: Snickargatan 20, SE-941 63 Piteå, Sweden', 'muh-registrator@ltu.se', '+46 911 72 610', '1', '+46 911 72 610', 'SE', 'https://www.ltu.se/', '-', 'institutions/1620025387_itu se.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:03:07', '2021-05-03 13:03:07'),
(459, 'Lund University', 'Lund University was founded in 1666. There are no tuition fees and no scholarships are available from the university. The emphasis is on research in historical musicology and music analysis. The Faculty of Fine and Performing Arts consists of three institutions - Malmö Art Academy, Malmö Academy of Music and Malmö Theatre Academy. The major departments within the Music Academy are performance, composition, music education and church music.', 'Music', 'Box 117, 221 00 Lund, Sweden', 'info@mhm.lu.se', '+46 (0)46 222 0000', '1', '+46 (0)46 222 0000', 'SE', 'http://www.lunduniversity.lu.se/', 'https://www.facebook.com/lunduniversity', 'institutions/1620025566_lund.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:06:06', '2021-05-03 13:06:06'),
(460, 'Lucerne University of Applied Sciences and Arts', 'In 2013 the Lucerne School of Music (Hochschule Luzern - Musik) was incorporated into the recently-established (2007) Lucerne University of Applied Sciences and Arts as its music school. The earlier Swiss Jazz School forms the jazz department of the School of Music. In addition to the professional programs the School offers preparatory courses as well as a non-professional program for children and interested adults. An elective program in Alexander technique is offered.', 'Music', 'Werftestrasse 4, 6002 Lucerne, Switzerland', 'info@hslu.ch', '+41 41 228 42 42', '1', '+41 41 228 42 42', 'CH', 'https://www.hslu.ch/de-ch/', '-', 'institutions/1620025711_hslu.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:08:32', '2021-05-03 13:08:32'),
(461, 'Hochschule der Künste Bern', 'In October 1999 the University of the Arts (Hochschule der Kunste Bern) was formed from an amalgamation of the former Conservatorium of Music in Berne, the Conservatorium of Music and Theatre in Biel/Bienne, the Swiss Jazz School, and the School of Drama. There are three departments: College of Music (Hochschule für Musik), College of Theatre (Hochschule für Theater), and Music School (Musikschule). The Swiss Jazz School is now the Department of Jazz of the Hochschule für Musik Bern.', 'Music', 'Fellerstrasse 11, CH-3027 Berne 22, Switzerland', 'musik@hkb.bfh.ch', '+41 31 848 3998', '1', '+41 31 848 3998', 'CH', 'http://www.hkb.bfh.ch/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hkb.bern', 'institutions/1620025888_hkb.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:11:28', '2021-05-03 13:11:28'),
(462, 'Zurich University of Applied Sciences/ZHAW', 'Graduates of the ZHAW Zurich University of Applied Sciences possess reflective, professional, research and practice-based competences which can be applied in demanding professional fields in our knowledge-based society. The dual emphasis of higher education is guaranteed by the programmatic coupling of studying with research and development, as well as with practical application.', 'Music', 'Gertrudstrasse 15\r\n8401 Winterthur', 'info@zhaw.ch', '+41 (0) 58 934 71 71', '1', '+41 (0) 58 934 71 71', 'CH', 'https://www.zhaw.ch/en/university/', '-', 'institutions/1620026001_zhaw.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:13:21', '2021-05-03 13:13:21'),
(463, 'EJMA Lausanne', 'The EJMA offers students of all ages and all levels appropriate musical training. For students from the age of 4 and up to 20 years, subsidized education is part of a complete training course, leading to the obtaining of a non-professional end of studies certificate or a certificate from the Pre-HEM section . Up to the age of 25, students can also benefit from grants, as long as they prove student or apprentice status and enroll in a certifying or Pre-HEM course.', 'Music', 'ECOLE DE JAZZ ET DE MUSIQUE ACTUELLE\r\nRue des Côtes-de-Montbenon 26\r\n\r\n1003 Lausanne', 'info@ejma.ch', '+41 21 341 72 00', '1', '+41 21 341 72 00', 'CH', 'http://ejma.ch/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/EJMA-Ecole-de-Jazz-et-de-Musique-Actuelle/492716574117865?ref=hl', 'institutions/1620026401_ejma.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:20:01', '2021-05-03 13:20:01'),
(464, 'Geneva University of Music', 'The Geneva - Neuchâtel High School of Music (HEM) covers a historical and stylistic field ranging from medieval music to contemporary creation, without forgetting extra-European music. It comes from the professional classes of the two institutions: on the one hand the Geneva Conservatory of Music, founded in 1835, the oldest musical education institution in Switzerland; and on the other hand the Jaques-Dalcroze Institute, founded in 1915.', 'Music', 'Rue de l\'Arquebuse 12\r\nCH 1204 Genève', 'info.hem@hesge.ch', '+41 22 327 31 00', '1', '+41 22 327 31 00', 'CH', 'https://www.hesge.ch/hem/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hemgeneve', 'institutions/1620026753_hem.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:25:53', '2021-05-03 13:25:53'),
(465, 'Fu Jen Catholic University', 'A Catholic university founded originally in Beijing in 1925, and re-established in Taiwan in 1961. The music department, established in 1983, forms part of the College of Fine Arts which includes music, applied arts and architecture. The Master’s program was established in 1995. Facilities include an Experimental Music Studio and several recital venues, including the 500-seat Hwai-Jen auditorium.', 'Music', 'Zhongzheng Road 510, Xinzhuang District, New Taipei City 24205, Taiwan, Republic of China', 'pubwww@mail.fju.edu.tw', '(02) 29052000', '1', '(02) 29052000', 'TW', 'https://www.fju.edu.tw/', '-', 'institutions/1620026979_fu jen.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:29:39', '2021-05-03 13:29:39'),
(466, 'National Taiwan Normal University', 'This institution was founded in 1946 and gained its current name and status in 1994. The College of Music, established in 2007, consists of the Department of Music, the Graduate Institute of Ethnomusicology and the Graduate Institute of Performing Arts (which concentrates on three areas - theatre, marketing and industry, and collaborative performance).', 'Music', 'No.31, Shida Rd, Da’an Dist, Taipei City, Taiwan, Republic of China', 'musictnu@deps.ntnu.edu.tw', '+886 2 2364 7057', '1', '+886 2 2364 7057', 'TW', 'http://www.ntnu.edu.tw/', '-', 'institutions/1620027093_ntnu.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:31:33', '2021-05-03 13:31:33'),
(467, 'National Taiwan University of Arts', 'The last half a century of development at NTUA developed in parallel with Modern Taiwan Art History. Our institution now has the longest history of any art institution in Taiwan, as well as the most specialized fields of study.', 'Music', '59,Sec. 1, Daguan Rd., Banqiao Dist., New Taipei City 22058, Taiwan', 'pr@ntua.edu.tw', '886-2-22722181', '1', '886-2-22722181', 'TW', 'http://m.ntua.edu.tw/ntuaen/index.htm', '-', 'institutions/1620027486_ta.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:38:06', '2021-05-03 13:38:06'),
(468, 'Shepherd School of Music, Rice University', 'Shepherd School alumni include Pulitzer Prize and Grammy Award winners; they have debuted on the stages of Carnegie Hall and have appeared with the Chamber Music Society of Lincoln Center and the Metropolitan Opera. They hold positions in prestigious orchestras across the globe, including the Boston Symphony Orchestra, the Chicago Symphony Orchestra, the Philadelphia and Cleveland orchestras, the Los Angeles Philharmonic, and the Metropolitan Opera Orchestra.', 'Music', 'Rice University\r\nShepherd School of Music - MS 532\r\nP.O. Box 1892\r\nHouston, TX 77251-1892', 'musi@rice.edu', '+1 713-348-4854', '1', '+1 713-348-4854', 'US', 'https://music.rice.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ShepherdSchool?fref=ts', 'institutions/1620027500_shepherd school.PNG', '2021-05-03 13:38:20', '2021-05-03 13:38:20'),
(469, 'Shih Chien University', 'A private university founded in 1958 as the Shih Chien College of Home Economics. It gained its current name and status in 1997. The music department was founded in 1969 and the Graduate School of Music was established in 2007. There is a second campus in Kaohsiung.', 'Music', 'No.70, Dazhi St., Zhongshan Dist., Taipei City, 10462 Taiwan, Republic of China', 'mus_dept@mail.usc.edu.tw', '+886 2 2532 1125', '1', '+886 2 2532 1125', 'TW', 'https://www.usc.edu.tw/', '-', 'institutions/1620027698_usc.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:41:38', '2021-05-03 13:41:38'),
(470, 'Rangsit Conservatory of Music', 'Rangsit University is a higher education institution. That has been assessed by the Office for Education Standards and Quality Assessment (ONESQA) as the only private university that has been rated as \"very good\" among institutions that focus on graduate production.Rangsit University Located on an area of ​​292 rai, Lak Hok Subdistrict, Phahonyothin Road, Muang District, Pathum Thani Province.', 'Music', 'No. 52/347, Muang Ek Village, Phaholyothin Road, Lak Hok Subdistrict, Muang District, Pathum Thani 12000', '%20info@rsu.ac.th', '02-791-6000', '1', '02-791-6000', 'TH', 'https://www2.rsu.ac.th/home', 'https://www.facebook.com/rangsituniversity', 'institutions/1620027941_rsu.JPG', '2021-05-03 13:45:41', '2021-05-03 13:45:41'),
(471, 'College of Music, Mahidol University', 'The College of Music, Mahidol University was the first music institute in Thailand offering comprehensive degree programs, including Pre-College, Undergraduate, Master’s and Doctoral programs in many areas of music.  In 1987 Mahidol University initiated the Academic Development Project with Dr. Sugree Charoensook as project head, marking the first time that music courses were opened as electives for undergraduate students in Mahidol University.', 'Music', '25/25 Phutthamonthon Sai 4 Road Salaya,\r\nPhutthamonthon Nakhonpathom, 73170 Thailand', 'musicmupr@gmail.com', '(662) 800-2525-34', '1', '(662) 800-2525-34', 'TH', 'https://www.music.mahidol.ac.th/', 'https://www.facebook.com/mahidolmusic', 'institutions/1620050429_mahidol.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:00:30', '2021-05-03 20:00:30'),
(472, 'Payap University', 'A private liberal arts university founded in 1974 by the Church of Christ in Thailand. The Christian Communication Institute is a centre for dance, drama, music and Christian outreach. The university also has a Centre for Arts and Culture, aiming to study and preserve traditional North Thailand (Lanna) dance and music, and offering lessons on playing traditional instruments to students and staff.', 'Music', 'Kaew-Nawarat campus: 131 Kaew-Nawarat Road, T. Watket, A.Muang, Chiangmai 50000, Thailand', 'duriyasilp@payap.ac.th', '+66 053 241255', '1', '+66 053 241255', 'TH', 'https://www.payap.ac.th/home/', 'https://www.facebook.com/pyuofficial', 'institutions/1620050540_payap.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:02:20', '2021-05-03 20:02:20'),
(473, 'Silpakorn University', 'The Silpakorn University was founded in 1943 - the first university in Thailand devoted to fine arts, with its first students being admitted in 1999. The Faculty of Music was opened in 1999. It organises a summer music school and a jazz camp. A Music Plus Academy offers music tuition to interested members of the local community. Language of instruction is Thai.', 'Music', '22 Barommarachachonnani Road, Talingchan District, Bangkok 10170, Thailand', 'pongsin@su.ac.th', '+66 2 424 5618', '1', '+66 2 424 5618', 'TH', 'https://www.su.ac.th/th/index.php', '-', 'institutions/1620050683_su ac.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:04:43', '2021-05-03 20:04:43'),
(474, 'Burapha University', 'This institution was formerly a branch campus of Srinakharinwirot University. It became an autonomous university in 1990. The Faculty of Fine and Applied Arts offers programs in visual arts, music, theatre, dance, design and graphic arts. The University\'s Siam Ruby Project offers special places in its first year programs to year 12 students with specialised talents in sports, Thai music and arts.', 'Music', '169 Long-Haad Bangsaen Road, Tambon Saensook, Amphur Muang, Chonburi 20131, Thailand', 'pr@buu.ac.th', '+66 3839 0351', '1', '+66 3839 0351', 'TH', 'http://www.buu.ac.th/2016/', 'https://www.facebook.com/buu.ac.th/?__mref=message_bubble', 'institutions/1620050778_burapha.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:06:18', '2021-05-03 20:06:18'),
(475, 'Assumption University', 'Assumption University was initially originated from Assumption Commercial College in 1969 as an autonomous higher education institution under the name of Assumption School of Business. In 1972, with the approval of the Ministry of Education, it was officially established as \"Assumption Business Administration College\" or ABAC. In May 1975, it was accredited by the Ministry of University Affairs. In 1990, it was granted new status as “Assumption University” by the Ministry of University Affairs.', 'Music', '592/3 Soi Ramkhamhaeng 24,\r\nRamkhamhaeng Rd., Hua Mak,\r\nBang Kapi, \r\nBangkok 10240,\r\nThailand', 'abac@au.edu', '(66) 0-2300-4543-62', '1', '(66) 0-2300-4543-62', 'TH', 'https://www.au.edu/', 'http://www.facebook.com/assumptionuniversity', 'institutions/1620050912_assumption univeristy.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:08:32', '2021-05-03 20:08:32'),
(476, 'Lviv Conservatory', 'The Department of Postgraduate and Doctoral Studies is a structural subdivision of the Academy, its main tasks and functions include:\r\n\r\nplanning, organization and control of training and certification of higher education candidates for the degree of Doctor of Philosophy, Doctor of Arts and Doctor of Science;\r\nplanning, organization and control of training and certification of assistant trainees.', 'Music', 'Kyiv 01001, street Architect Gorodetsky 1-3 / 11', 'cancelyariya@knmau.com.ua', '+38 (044) 278-42-20', '1', '+38 (044) 278-42-20', 'UA', 'https://knmau.com.ua/?fbclid=IwAR0gK1aH0Ny4dFdO9mCHFgmxEKZZvS6tj6iAKvuIvp-NbWFePyUfaCQ8tqE', 'https://www.facebook.com/petro.tchaikovsky.92', 'institutions/1620051069_lviv.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:11:09', '2021-05-03 20:11:09'),
(477, 'Odessa Conservatoire', 'About our academy/ History\r\nThe Odessa conservatoire (for the time being – the Odessa national A. V. Nezhdanova academy of music) was created on donations of V. A. Orlov, the chairman of Management of the Odessa branch of IRMS(the Imperial Russian Musical Society), and those of other members of this branch, as well as due to the decision of the Main Management of the Russian musical society on the basis of the Odessa musical school (founded in 1897) on the 8-th of September, 1913.', 'Music', 'Novoselskogo, 63\r\nOdessa\r\nUkraine\r\n65023', 'muse@odma.edu.ua', '(048) 726-78-76', '1', '(048) 726-78-76', 'UA', 'http://odma.edu.ua/eng/about', 'https://www.facebook.com/odessa.nma.nezhdanova/', 'institutions/1620051235_odma.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:13:55', '2021-05-03 20:13:55'),
(478, 'Kharkov Institute of Art', 'IP Kotlyarevsky Kharkiv National University of Arts is one of the leading and oldest universities in Ukraine, a creative, scientific and methodological center of music and theater education in Slobozhanshchyna.\r\n\r\nThe website \"About the University\" is not aimed at a traditional report on the achievements of the university, but an essay of his \"creative self-portrait\", which is based on the need to see ourselves as we are today, because for each of us the university is Alma Mater.', 'Music', 'Constitution Square, 11/13\r\n\r\nKharkiv, 61003, Ukraine', 'num.kharkiv@i.ua', '+38 (057) 731-10-95', '1', '+38 (057) 731-10-95', 'UA', 'http://num.kharkiv.ua/index-e.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/HNUM-Kotlyarevsky-101345511960603/', 'institutions/1620051422_num.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:17:02', '2021-05-03 20:17:02'),
(479, 'Academy of Contemporary Music', 'Access Creative College has been delivering creative education for over twenty-five years. Operating as England’s largest private training provider, the college delivers creative education at campuses in seven cities, from Bristol in the south-west to York in the north-east.\r\n\r\nNow offering courses in Games, Media, Music and Events, the college started life as Access to Music', 'Music', 'The Rodboro Buildings, Bridge Street, Guildford, GU1 4SB', 'admissions@accesscreative.ac.uk', '0161 247 8090', '1', '0161 247 8090', 'GB', 'http://www.accesstomusic.co.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/accesscreativecollege/', 'institutions/1620051828_accesto muwic.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:23:48', '2021-05-03 20:23:48'),
(480, 'Birmingham Conservatoire', 'The Birmingham Conservatoire can trace its history back to 1843. It became the music department of Birmingham City University in 1989 and later became the Royal Birmingham Conservatoire. There are departments of performance, composition, early music, jazz, vocal and operatic performance, orchestral and choral conducting, chamber music performing ensembles, pedagogy and music technology.', 'Music', '200 Jennens Road, Birmingham B4 7XR, UK', 'conservatoire@bcu.ac.uk', '+44 121 331 5906', '1', '+44 121 331 5906', 'GB', 'http://www.bcu.ac.uk/conservatoire', 'https://www.facebook.com/royalbirmcons', 'institutions/1620051987_bcu.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:26:27', '2021-05-03 20:26:27'),
(481, 'British and Irish Modern Music Institute', 'We’re Europe’s largest, most connected music institute with eight colleges based in vibrant musical cities across the UK and Europe. Our creative space not only nurtures talent; it also enables future generations to find their place within the music industry.\r\n\r\nFor over 35 years, we’ve equipped our students with the knowledge and skills they need to meet the demands of the music business – and graduate feeling industry-ready.', 'Music', '38-42 Brunswick St W, Hove BN3 1EL, United Kingdom', 'admissions@bimm.ac.uk', '0344 2 646 666', '1', '0344 2 646 666', 'GB', 'http://www.bimm.co.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/BIMMInstitute', 'institutions/1620052107_bmm.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:28:27', '2021-05-03 20:28:27'),
(482, 'Guildhall School of Music and Drama', 'Guildhall School is a vibrant, international community of musicians, actors and production artists in the heart of the City of London.\r\n\r\nRanked as the top UK conservatoire in the Guardian music and drama league tables, we deliver world-class professional training in partnership with distinguished artists, companies and ensembles.', 'Music', 'Silk Street, Barbican, EC2Y 8DT', 'accommodation@gsmd.ac.uk', '+44 (0) 20 7628 2571', '1', '+44 (0) 20 7628 2571', 'GB', 'http://www.gsmd.ac.uk/', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/London-United-Kingdom/Guildhall-School-of-Music-Drama/116436691364', 'institutions/1620052233_guild.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:30:33', '2021-05-03 20:30:33'),
(483, 'The Institute of Contemporary Music Performance', 'ICMP, based in London, has been developing and delivering music education and training to students of contemporary music for over 30 years, longer than any other UK school. We pride ourselves first and foremost on the continuing success of our alumni – within 6 months of graduating over  94% of our graduates are in employment or further education*.', 'Music', '1B Dyne Road, London, NW6 7XG', 'enquiries@icmp.co.uk', '020 3805 9385', '1', '020 3805 9385', 'GB', 'http://www.icmp.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ICMPLondon', 'institutions/1620052401_icmp.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:33:21', '2021-05-03 20:33:21'),
(484, 'London College of Music', 'London College of Music (LCM) is the largest specialist music and performing arts institution in the UK and in 2017 we celebrated our 130-year anniversary. \r\nAs an all-Steinway school with one of Europe\'s largest studio complexes, we offer an impressive range of innovative courses, which are respected worldwide and delivered with creativity and passion by our expert staff.', 'Music', 'St Mary\'s Rd, London W5 5RF, UK', 'LCM.exams@uwl.ac.uk', '08000368888', '1', '08000368888', 'GB', 'http://www.uwl.ac.uk/academic-schools/music', 'http://www.facebook.com/UniversityWestLondon', 'institutions/1620052637_uwl.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:37:17', '2021-05-03 20:37:17'),
(485, 'Leeds College of Music', 'Leeds Conservatoire is a specialist conservatoire in the UK, delivering expert music and performing arts education to a community of over 1200 students. Our broad offering spans undergraduate and postgraduate degree courses, numerous short courses and Leeds Junior Conservatoire for young musicians and performers.', 'Fine Art', '3 Quarry Hill (5,217.31 mi) Leeds, UK, LS2 7PD', 'hello@lcm.ac.uk', '+44 113 222 3400', '1', '+44 113 222 3400', 'GB', 'http://www.lcm.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/leedsconservatoire', 'institutions/1620052828_leeds con.JPG', '2021-05-03 20:40:28', '2021-05-03 20:40:28'),
(486, 'Royal Academy of Music', 'The Royal Academy, founded in 1822, is the oldest institution for advanced music training in the United Kingdom. It is a full member of the University of London and all graduates are awarded University of London degrees. The Centre for Advanced Performance Studies is run jointly by the Royal Academy and King’s College, University of London.', 'Music', 'York Gate, Marylebone Road, London NW1 5HT, UK', 'registry@ram.ac.uk', '02078737373', '1', '02078737373', 'GB', 'http://www.ram.ac.uk/', '-', 'institutions/1620070022_royal acedymy of music.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:27:02', '2021-05-04 01:27:02'),
(487, 'Royal College of Music', 'The Royal College of Music was founded in 1882. It houses some fine performing spaces. Students in years three and four of the Bachelor of Music program have the opportunity to study abroad for an extended period. The College has a valuable and growing collection of historic musical instruments (Western, Asian, African), as well as a large collection of early printed music, manuscripts, portraits and ephemera associated with the music profession as well as autograph manuscripts.', 'Music', 'Prince Consort Road, London SW7 2BS, England', 'info@rcm.ac.uk', '+44 (0)20 7591 4300', '1', '+44 (0)20 7591 4300', 'GB', 'https://www.rcm.ac.uk/', 'http://www.facebook.com/royalcollegeofmusic', 'institutions/1620070214_rcm.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:30:14', '2021-05-04 01:30:14'),
(488, 'Royal Northern College of Music', 'The Royal Northern College of Music was established in 1973 following the merger of the Royal Manchester College of Music and the Northern School of Music. The College is organised into schools of study: academic, composition and contemporary music, keyboard, strings, wind, brass and percussion, vocal and opera, as well as a graduate school.', 'Music', '124 Oxford Road, Manchester M13 9RD, UK', 'info@rncm.ac.uk', '0161 907 5200', '1', '0161 907 5200', 'GB', 'https://www.rncm.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/RNCMLIVE', 'institutions/1620070353_rncm.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:32:33', '2021-05-04 01:32:33'),
(489, 'Tech Music School', 'With more than 27 years experience in music education, Tech Music School (TMS) delivers professional, real world training for serious minded musicians.\r\n\r\nStriving for musical innovation and originality, TMS’s ethos reflects the values of an idealistic conservatoire for today’s thriving musician.\r\n\r\nProviding the optimum learning environment for students of all abilities, TMS prides itself on high quality teaching from the professionals.', 'Music', 'Effie Road, Fulham, England, United Kingdom', 'info@techmusicschool.co.uk', '+448442646666', '1', '+448442646666', 'GB', 'http://www.techmusicschool.co.uk/', '-', 'institutions/1620070551_tech music school.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:35:51', '2021-05-04 01:35:51'),
(490, 'Trinity Laban Conservatoire of Music and Dance', 'Trinity Laban is a pioneering force in music education, influential in the training of musicians for classroom teaching, 1-2-1 teaching and community music-making. We believe that students should develop the skills to work across multiple contexts, blending pedagogies as required. Our approach combines both performance and education training, focusing on the practical over the academic.', 'Music', 'King Charles Court\r\nOld Royal Naval College\r\nGreenwich\r\nLondon', 'admissions@trinitylaban.ac.uk', '44 (0)20 8305 4444', '1', '44 (0)20 8305 4444', 'GB', 'https://www.trinitylaban.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/trinity.laban/', 'institutions/1620070764_trinity.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:39:24', '2021-05-04 01:39:24'),
(491, 'Royal Conservatoire of Scotland', 'The Royal Conservatoire of Scotland was, until 1 September 2011, known as the Royal Scottish Academy of Music and Drama. It can trace its history back to the creation of the Glasgow Athenaeum in 1847. Facilities include the Stevenson Hall seating 360 people, a recital hall, many practice and rehearsal rooms, an organ room, the Groves recording studio and electronic music workshop.', 'Music', '100 Renfrew Street, Glasgow G2 3DB, Scotland, UK', 'principal@rcs.ac.uk', '+44 141 332 8901', '1', '+44 141 332 8901', 'GB', 'https://www.rcs.ac.uk/', 'http://www.facebook.com/rcsofficial', 'institutions/1620071368_royal.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:49:28', '2021-05-04 01:49:28'),
(492, 'Royal Welsh College of Music & Drama', 'The Royal Welsh College of Music & Drama is part of the University of South Wales Group and a member of Conservatoires UK, Federation of Drama Schools and the European Association of Conservatoires.', 'Music', 'Royal Welsh College of Music & Drama\r\nCastle Grounds\r\nCathays Park\r\nCardiff\r\nCF10 3ER', 'info@rwcmd.ac.uk', '029 2034 2854', '1', '029 2034 2854', 'GB', 'https://www.rwcmd.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/rwcmd', 'institutions/1620071502_rwcmd.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:51:42', '2021-05-04 01:51:42'),
(493, 'Cardiff University School of Music', 'The University was founded in 1883. The Department of Music is active in the fields of publishing and concert presentation. The Library at the University of Wales in Cardiff houses the Welsh Music Information Centre, concerned with the promotion and dissemination of Welsh music.', 'Music', 'University College, 31 Corbett Road, Cathays, Cardiff CF10 3EB, Wales, UK', 'musicschool@cardiff.ac.uk', '+44 29 2087 4379', '1', '+44 29 2087 4379', 'GB', 'http://www.cardiff.ac.uk/music', 'https://www.facebook.com/cardiffuni', 'institutions/1620071810_cardiff.JPG', '2021-05-04 01:56:50', '2021-05-04 01:56:50'),
(494, 'Bangor University', 'The University of Wales in Bangor can trace its history back to 1885. The activities of the School of Music cover the areas of performance, composition, technology, media and popular culture, and history, culture and society. Facilities include four state-of-the-art electronic composition studios, two concert halls and two rehearsal rooms.', 'Music', 'College Road, Bangor, Gwynedd LL57 2DG, Wales, UK', 'music@bangor.ac.uk', '+44 1248 351 151', '1', '+44 1248 351 151', 'GB', 'https://www.bangor.ac.uk/', 'https://www.facebook.com/BangorUniversity', 'institutions/1620072061_bangor.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:01:01', '2021-05-04 02:01:01'),
(495, 'Wrexham Glyndŵr University', 'The Royal Conservatoire of Scotland was, until 1 September 2011, known as the Royal Scottish Academy of Music and Drama. It can trace its history back to the creation of the Glasgow Athenaeum in 1847. Facilities include the Stevenson Hall seating 360 people, a recital hall, many practice and rehearsal rooms, an organ room, the Groves recording studio and electronic music workshop.', 'Music', 'Wrexham Glyndwr University,\r\nMold Road,\r\nWrexham,\r\nLL11 2AW', 'ASK@glyndwr.ac.uk', '01978290666', '1', '01978290666', 'GB', 'https://www.glyndwr.ac.uk/en/', 'https://www.facebook.com/glyndwruni/', 'institutions/1620072250_glyndwr.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:04:10', '2021-05-04 02:04:10'),
(496, 'California Institute of the Arts', 'California Institute of the Arts is renowned internationally as a game-changer in the education of professional artists. The transformative cultural impact of our alumni shows why: We bring out visionary creative talent unlike any other university, school or conservatory. An all-inclusive community for a diversity of authentic voices, CalArts today offers more than 70 comprehensive degree programs in the visual, performing, media and literary arts.\r\n661-255-1050', 'Music', 'California Institute of the Arts\r\n24700 McBean Pkwy.\r\nValencia, CA 91355\r\n661-255-1050', 'communications@calarts.edu', '661-222-2782', '1', '661-222-2782', 'US', 'https://calarts.edu/', 'http://www.facebook.com/CalArts', 'institutions/1620072357_calarts.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:05:57', '2021-05-04 02:05:57'),
(497, 'California State University, Long Beach Bob Cole Conservatory of Music', 'Originally founded in 1949 as Los Angeles-Orange County State College, this institution gained its current name and status in 1971. The College of the Arts offers programs in art, dance, design, film and electronic arts, theatre arts and music. It houses the University Art Museum and the Carpenter Performing Arts Center. Member of the California State University system. Member of the National Association of Schools of Music.', 'Music', 'Room C306, University Music Center, 1250 Bellflower Boulevard, Long Beach, California 90840, USA', 'music@csulb.edu', '+1 562 985 2490', '1', '+1 562 985 2490', 'US', 'http://web.csulb.edu/depts/music/', 'http://www.facebook.com/coleconservatory', 'institutions/1620072434_bob.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:07:14', '2021-05-04 02:07:14'),
(498, 'California State University, Northridge', 'The University was founded in 1958 and gained its current name and status in 1972. The College of Arts, Media and Communication offers programs in art, cinema and television arts, communication studies, journalism, music and theatre. The Music Department is housed in Cypress Hall with several fine performance spaces.', 'Music', 'Room 116, Cypress Hall, 18111 Nordhoff Street, Northridge, California 91330, USA', 'music@csun.edu', '+1 818 677 6828', '1', '+1 818 677 6828', 'US', 'https://www.csun.edu/', '-', 'institutions/1620072527_csun.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:08:47', '2021-05-04 02:08:47'),
(499, 'San Francisco Conservatory of Music', 'This private conservatory was founded in 1917 and gained its current name and status in 1923. The Conservatory has strengths in chamber music, the production and performance of new music, and opera performance. Facilities include a number of fine performance spaces, a computer centre, a baroque studio and the state-of-the-art Wiegand Electronic Composition Studio.', 'Music', '50 Oak Street, San Francisco, California 94102, USA', 'apply@sfcm.edu', '415-503-6271', '1', '415-503-6271', 'US', 'https://sfcm.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/SanFranciscoConservatoryOfMusic', 'institutions/1620072660_sfcm.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:11:00', '2021-05-04 02:11:00'),
(500, 'Colburn School', 'The Colburn School, established in 1950, offers training in music, dance and drama to students from pre-school to adult. The professional music program is offered through the Conservatory of Music, established in 2003, while the community music arm is the School of Performing Arts. The Conservatory provides full financial support to all students, covering tuition, room and board.', 'Music', '200 South Grand Avenue, Los Angeles, California 90012, USA', 'musicacademy@colburnschool.edu', '+1 213-621-2200', '1', '+1 213-621-2200', 'US', 'https://www.colburnschool.edu/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ColburnSchool', 'institutions/1620072824_colburn.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:13:44', '2021-05-04 02:13:44'),
(501, 'University of California Berkeley School of Music', 'From a group of academic pioneers in 1868 to the Free Speech Movement in 1964, Berkeley is a place where the brightest minds from across the globe come together to explore, ask questions and improve the world.', 'Music', '104 Morrison Hall #1200, Berkeley, CA 94720, USA', 'musicgradadvisor@berkeley.edu', '642-2623', '1', '642-2623', 'US', 'https://www.berkeley.edu/', 'http://www.facebook.com/UCBerkeley', 'institutions/1620072957_berkely.JPG', '2021-05-04 02:15:57', '2021-05-04 02:15:57');
